      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0f176c0685a21ac2f59f992f552b9d1a88965fd9.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=6baf3a5f25d0171c8172bd5d077a72db"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f076cc864bcc38dbb44c7e7469c63d6540f2c5c9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=12fe23ef1a7fa8cfe15f1a25ebf8e2a6"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;This one’s for the dungeon crawlers&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you’re an avid follower of Dungeon Craft or simply want to test your mettle on a new adventure, you’ll want to snag this bundle of TTRPG rulebooks, adventures, inspiration manuals, and more presented by the one, the only Professor DM! In this library of over 100 ebooks and PDFs, you’ll find Dungeon Crawl Classics adventures like &lt;em&gt;The Croaking Fane&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;Intrigue at the Court of Chaos&lt;/em&gt;, eldritch alphabets, how-to manuals, horror and romance tales, and a lot more—even hard copies of four random adventures with your purchase! This bundle has everything you need and more to kick off your next campaign, so get it now at the price of your choice, and support St. Jude Children’s Hospital! &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;a style="color: #EF9741;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;The titles in this bundle are available through DTRPG.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;span style="color: #ef9741;"&gt;Keys expire. Please redeem your digital tier keys before June 29th, 2027, and your physical tier key before December 31st, 2026.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $2 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#dccrpgcorerulebook"&gt;DCC RPG Core Rulebook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#dungeoncrawlclassics_issue79_frozenintime"&gt;Dungeon Crawl Classics #79: Frozen in Time&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#goodmangames2022yearbook"&gt;2022 Yearbook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#freerpgday2024_acrosstheveiloftime"&gt;