      <title>Let's Go Gambling!...aw dang it.</title>
      <author>Publishers</author>
      <link>https://humblebundle.com//games/lets-go-gamblingaw-dang-it</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">caaf86b72ebfd3b69869aa13ae8c53be1758e5d0</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 18:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9bab30b2e7934a7dafaa374dc5ee86878a1c36d6.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=3ec411275a78dfcfa3b1ae8b9fdb5165"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/65b017777edc2a4dc6b304ed4cac06c514ddd1a0.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=4523463d79fcea45fbf795ee57a4bde6"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Put it all on 23, baby! &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Spin the wheel, chuck the dice, and win big in our latest bundle focused on tipping the odds in your favor. Combine strategy and chaos as best you can while you navigate through Dicealot’s risky engagements, build multiple winning hands in &lt;em&gt;This Ain’t Even Poker&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Ya Joker&lt;/em&gt;, or even alter probability itself in &lt;em&gt;Pip My Dice&lt;/em&gt;. These tempting tales, plus five more await you, and you’ll be supporting Movember with your purchase. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ef9741;"&gt;Keys expire. Please redeem before July 22nd, 2027. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $7 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#thisaintevenpokeryajoker"&gt;This Ain't Even Poker, Ya Joker&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#diceofkalma"&gt;Dice of Kalma&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#explosiveodds"&gt;Explosive Odds&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#treasuretiger"&gt;Treasure Tiger&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#supertaxcity"&gt;SuperTaxCity&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt12"&gt;Pay $12 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#dicealtot"&gt;Dicealot&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#pipmydice"&gt;Pip My Dice&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#diceydungeons"&gt;Dicey Dungeons&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $7 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="thisaintevenpokeryajoker"&gt;&lt;a id="thisaintevenpokeryajoker" href="https://youtu.be/pS9eOIPJ-sk"&gt;This Ain't Even Poker, Ya Joker&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3829fbbad804f3d85143100d02f401ad387ebbf7.png?auto=compress,format&amp;w=300&amp;s=7a81b405f51c11e07e57aba8825d3549"&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;GROW YOUR HAND&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Buy new cards to increase your odds of hitting good hands. If you're rich enough, you can even break the rules and get over 5 cards.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;GO ON EXPEDITIONS&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Once unlocked, you can send your minions on expeditions to discover new otherworldy cards with powerful benefits. Upgrade these missions to provide even more powerful benefits as you progress. You can even unlock missions to destroy cards from your deck that you don't want, to ensure every hand is exactly how you want it.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;GET UPGRADED&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Buy powerful upgrades using your hard earned coins, enabling you to progress quicker, open up new avenues, and take on the evil Jester!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;ESTABLISH DOMINANCE&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Even though the Jester doesn't like it, you can buy new decks of cards in order to play more hands at once. Use this to your advantage to grow those numbers even faster!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;ASCEND TO GREATNESS&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Make a deal with Mary the Fairy to start over in exchange for Poker Chips (poker chips? ...but this ain't even poker...?), use those chips to buy even more powerful upgrades.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;ESCAPE THE HOUSE OF CARDS&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;You're trapped in the Jester's domain, can you manage to defeat him and escape? Or will he keep you there, trapped forever in an endless cycle?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="diceofkalma"&gt;&lt;a id="diceofkalma" href="https://youtu.be/KhM76qZpLZw"&gt;Dice of Kalma&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WELCOME TO THE UNDERWORLD'S DEADLIEST GAME OF DICE POKER!&lt;/strong&gt;  Dice of Kalma is an unholy deckbuilding roguelike game where every roll matters. Collect game-breaking skulls, play poker-style dice hands, and challenge the grim guardian of the Underworld. How far can you push your luck to master the chaos?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; BUILD POKER HANDS TO SCORE POINTS&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collect skulls that transform bad rolls into game breaking combos&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Upgrade your favorite poker hands for massive multipliers&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Push your luck or play it safe, the choice is yours&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt; BUILD A DECK OF SKULLS&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;70+ unique skulls with game-breaking abilities &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;8 upgradeable poker hands&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dark, atmospheric pixel art&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Endless replayability&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Leaderboards and achievements&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;NUMBERS GO UP&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Activate as many skulls as possible with every hand and use your rerolls to gain every advantage you can. Upgrade chosen poker hands to increase their value and complement your deck of skulls to meet increasingly difficult challenges.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;FAIL AND TRY AGAIN&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you run out of hands, it is game over for you. Don’t worry, though. Persistence is rewarded, and the guardian of the Underworld seems to grow fond of you coming back to challenge him for just one more round.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="explosiveodds"&gt;&lt;a id="explosiveodds" href="https://youtu.be/YZLE9fmZkhM"&gt;Explosive Odds&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Be the last bot sitting in head to head matches with 2-4 players.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Experience tense PvP matches with 2, 3 or 4 players. Defuse a bomb with your friends and be the last bot sitting to win big! Use emotes, gestures, and in game voice comms to rub it in when their head explodes.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Clear wires to get cash, the richest player at the end of the 3 rounds wins!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The BombSlot device houses 3 wheels with 8 wires each. On your turn choose and cut one wire. Cutting a wire can earn you cash, abilities or, if your unlucky, detonate.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;Use a variety of abilities to gain an edge over chance.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scan&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;- to narrow down which wires may be detonators.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Spin&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;- each wheel to a new random position.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skip&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;- your turn, sometimes its best to let another player cut a suspicious looking wire.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reverse&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;- the turn order and send it right back to the previous bot.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lock&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;- to limit another players choice to just one wheel.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overload&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;- the bomb to make the next player cut an additional wire (Yes it stacks!).&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Turn, Detect, Plant, Obscure, And more!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;And more!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Auctions!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Minigames!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Face drawing!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customizable match settings!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;And more!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="treasuretiger"&gt;&lt;a id="treasuretiger" href="https://youtu.be/dQusG-zQ5x4"&gt;Treasure Tiger&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Treasure Tiger&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;— A Deadly Game of Luck While your wife is away on a trip, you stumble across a mysterious betting app that promises instant riches — all from the comfort of your home. Desperate for a way out of financial ruin, you start spinning. But this game isn’t just about money. It’s about survival. &lt;strong&gt;Treasure Tiger&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is a first-person horror game where every spin brings you closer to fortune… or to something far worse.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Spin to Survive&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Your only tool is your phone — and the cursed roulette app installed on it. Use the mouse to spin and earn cash through randomized outcomes:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Double or nothing&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Partial refunds&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Complete losses&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Sudden anomalies in your environment&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Each result affects your surroundings. Power outages. Sudden darkness. Unnatural sounds. And the Tiger… getting closer.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Keep Treasure Tiger Out&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;As the nights go on, the odds become increasingly stacked against you. A sinister creature known only as Treasure Tiger begins to appear — tapping at windows, lurking in shadows, and waiting for a chance to strike. You'll need to:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Monitor your environment carefully&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Close windows quickly using the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;E key&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Conserve flashlight power&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;React fast when danger hits&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Fail, and he’ll enter your home. Game over.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Five Nights. One Shot at Salvation.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The game unfolds across five increasingly intense nights. Each night escalates the tension with new challenges, harder odds, and deeper revelations. Clues begin to appear — messages on walls, distorted phone calls, and strange figures in the dark. What starts as a gambling app slowly reveals a much darker truth.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;A unique blend of gambling mechanics and survival horror&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;First-person gameplay&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Dynamic environment changes based on spin results&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Reactive AI: Treasure Tiger adapts to your behavior&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Atmospheric storytelling with escalating psychological horror&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Multiple endings depending on your performance&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Short-session design — easy to pick up, hard to master&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Will you get rich — or get devoured? &lt;strong&gt;Treasure Tiger&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is watching.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="supertaxcity"&gt;&lt;a id="supertaxcity" href="https://youtu.be/2AkyVnOGmgA"&gt;SuperTaxCity&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A new sensation!? City-building × Roguelike game *Super Tax City*.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Choose and place your favorite facilities from randomly drawn options!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The combinations are endless! Create a profitable city that's uniquely yours!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rules&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Choose a facility from three options and place it on the map!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;When randomly moving residents enter a facility, they perform tasks and earn rewards!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;When the time limit expires, it's tax time.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Pay your taxes with the money you've earned!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Facilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Over 100 types of unique facilities with distinctive effects are featured!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the items&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Enhance your city even further with over 100 different items!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The combinations are endless!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Create a profitable city that's uniquely yours!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Streaming Guidelines&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;1) You are free to stream and upload gameplay videos without prior notice, regardless of whether you are an individual or corporation, and regardless of whether your activities are for profit or not.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;2) If possible, please include the URL of the Steam page in the description.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;3) We take no responsibility for any damages that may occur as a result of streaming this game. Additionally, the content of these guidelines may be changed without prior notice.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt12"&gt;Pay $12 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="dicealtot"&gt;&lt;a id="dicealtot" href="https://youtu.be/LJ2ZKylytY4"&gt;Dicealot&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7c92b3c647e5492d88dffee0c46caafb29caaf4d.png?auto=compress,format&amp;w=300&amp;s=a05756db9daa050346498fb772009530"&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Every roll is a risk. Every risk is a thrill.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dicealot is a high-stakes roguelike dice-builder where every roll is a risk, every risk is a thrill, and every thrill teeters between triumph and disaster. Roll in search of devastating strikes, gamble in the hunt for nail-biting payoffs, and push your luck to its very limits as you battle to conquer your foes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Set in the charmingly chaotic realm of Camelot, chance collides with strategy, mastery dances with madness, and one single roll can rewrite your fate. The twist? Keep rolling to stack bigger combos and score more points, but push too far, and you’ll lose everything you’ve gained that turn.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Every roll matters. Every choice could be your last. Do you dare to keep rolling when the Kingdom itself hangs in the balance?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Dice. Your Strategy. Your Skill.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You’ll begin each run with a simple set of dice, but between battles you’ll stop at shops to expand and refine your collection. Some dice tilt the odds in your favour, others amplify your scores, and a few can backfire entirely, unless you’ve saved enough re-rolls to turn the tide. It’s up to you to experiment and discover the perfect combinations to save King Arthur and smite his foes!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Wield one of 10 distinct weapons that fundamentally transform the way you play. Maybe you favour steady, smaller, but consistent hits, or perhaps you thrive on the thrill of chasing the biggest rolls? Every choice unlocks a unique playstyle and demands a new strategy, putting your fate in your own hands as you forge your path to victory.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Master the Madness to Save the King.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A strange and sinister fate has befallen King Arthur, cursed by a spell that threatens all of Camelot. Now Queen Guinevere must rally the loyal Knights of the Round Table and lead them through a medieval kingdom that’s both charmingly unhinged and dangerously unpredictable.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master the mayhem on your own terms in this roguelike, where Farkle-inspired combat meets deck-building depth. Every decision you make will shape your fate, and victory belongs to those bold enough to embrace the chaos and risk it all for the perfect combination.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;High-risk, high-reward, high-stakes gameplay&lt;/strong&gt;, where every decision matters&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;100+ unique dice to encounter&lt;/strong&gt; for progressive dice-building&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;10 distinct weapons&lt;/strong&gt; with their own unique abilities to tweak your playstyle&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;30+ wicked foes&lt;/strong&gt; for you to take on within the chaotic Camelot realm&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7 difficulty levels&lt;/strong&gt; for endless replayability and to test your mettle&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Push-your-luck Farkle-inspired combat&lt;/strong&gt; will keep you on the edge of your seat&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Push Your Luck, Hold Your Nerve, Save the Kingdom.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Face over 30 eclectic enemies, each with varied abilities and unique dice that will test your dice-building skills and strategy. From irate maidens to mystical creatures, your journey will be challenged at every turn. Will you persevere and save your King? Do you have the nerve to keep rolling when everything's on the line?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Push your luck! Master the Madness! Hold Your Nerve! Save the Kingdom!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wishlist&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/u&gt; Dicealot now to be the first to roll into the kingdom.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Inspirations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fans of Balatro, Monster Train, Slay the Spire, Inscryption, and Dicey Dungeons will feel right at home - with a dice-driven twist that’s all Dicealot’s own.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="pipmydice"&gt;&lt;a id="pipmydice" href="https://youtu.be/n1yyp60ibno"&gt;Pip My Dice&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3ec1f5d853af3b134451741673eecfb83e8daad6.png?auto=compress,format&amp;w=300&amp;s=15e6b8b178051af646cc0e51b8e66c71"&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the game&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Pip My Dice is a roguelike deck builder inspired by Balatro and the Yahtzee game. Customize different dice and use them together with powerful relics to break high scores and climb the leaderboard. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collect powerful relics to create synergies with your dice and upgrade your combination slots. Take your time and make wise decisions about what you buy in the shop and how you use it. Don't be greedy, you never know if you are going to roll what you are expecting... Unless you customize your dice so much that all faces are the same!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Enjoy endless replayability with the guarantee that every run will be different from the previous one, and save your favorite seeds to replay and share those you like the most.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Customize all faces of your dice individually to make the most of your relics and create game-breaking combos! Rig the odds by modifying the value of the dice faces, and make sure that there is no room for chance. Hold on to precious consumables to get you out of trouble.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;130 Relics to create various builds and synergies with your dice&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Climb the leaderboard with seeded or random runs to compete with the world or your friends!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Select from 15+ different starting dice cups&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;50+ Different dice modifiers with unique effects&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;20+ Different bosses to defeat&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Daily runs&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Stats and Run History&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;25 Consumables to give you some extra help when you need it the most&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Level up your combination slots as the run goes on&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="diceydungeons"&gt;&lt;a id="diceydungeons" href="https://youtu.be/E2AdLWsRuHg"&gt;Dicey Dungeons&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c6771dd2d677bc6dc133a184dd4d86455f6c907d.png?auto=compress,format&amp;w=300&amp;s=e4691544cc92491354132d45ab209b1b"&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Become a giant walking dice and battle to the end of an ever-changing dungeon! Can you escape the cruel whims of Lady Luck? Now featuring ""Dicey Dungeons: Reunion"", a free DLC with six brand-new episodes! (Check out the Reunion OST on Bandcamp!)  In this fast-paced deckbuilding roguelike from Terry Cavanagh (Super Hexagon, VVVVVV), Chipzel, and Marlowe Dobbe, you'll fight monsters, find better loot, level up your heroes, and maybe even take down the Goddess of Fortune, Lady Luck herself. Balance your carefully planned strategies against the unknown of a dice roll.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MEET THE CONTESTANTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Play as six different characters, each with their own unique play styles and abilities.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;The Thief, who steals random enemy equipment every turn!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The Robot, who gains dice by playing a push-your-luck blackjack game!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The Inventor, overcome with inspiration, who must destroy their own equipment after each fight to get parts for powerful new gadgets!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;and more!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master each class and figure out which one best fits your style in this charming world filled with a growing array of twists and secrets.  Can you make it out alive? Maybe, but luck is definitely not on your side.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Six wildly different playable classes: Warrior, Thief, Robot, Jester, Inventor and Witch.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dozens of enemies, ranging from Vacuum Cleaners that want to suck your blood, to creatures from Irish mythology, to suave malevolent snowmen.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A catchy, upbeat and energetic soundtrack by Chipzel (previously, the musician from Super Hexagon).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Beautiful and adorable artwork by Marlowe Dobbe.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Procedurally generated for endless play-throughs.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
