      <title>Dungeon Defenders II Complete DLC Chest</title>
      <author>Chromatic Games</author>
      <link>https://humblebundle.com//games/dungeon-defenders-ii-complete-dlc-chest</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">ed5662b81d2d9374b1d94cc570555dfacb092a26</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 18:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/12a78dbd824234d566a0f886884dba9ce64d81da.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=ede7f5dbb43662b23497a108066c5e1f"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5528d8023ba503db6eea4a539a943fed83d93289.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=4f895ec1baac97db0243036d323c3c84"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Defend your friends and loot your enemies!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Are you ready to join the fight for Etheria? If you’re enjoying the free-to-play &lt;em&gt;Dungeon Defenders II&lt;/em&gt; and want to level up your game, we’ve got all of the DLC in one bundle at a great discount! Take to the stars with the Celestial Vault Pack, bask in the eldritch glow of the Ethereal Trove Pack, equip your heroes with the Adventurer’s Arsenal Pack, and more! This bundle even includes a Golden Headless Horseman Premium Pet that will plague your enemies with tormented thoughts! Grab this bundle while you can to level up your forces and save your lands from evil, pay whatever price you want, and support coral reef ecosystem nonprofit Coral Guardian with your purchase!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ef9741;"&gt;Keys expire. Please redeem before July 8th, 2027. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#adventurersarsenalpack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Adventurer's Arsenal Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#burningsoulspack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Burning Souls Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#500gembundle_dungeondefendersii"&gt;500 Gem Bundle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt12"&gt;Pay $12 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#imperialcachepack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Imperial Cache Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bundleofthebeast_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Bundle of the Beast&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#treasuretrovepack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Treasure Trove Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#1000gembundle_dungeondefendersii"&gt;1000 Gem Bundle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt20"&gt;Pay $20 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#goldenheadlesshorsemanpet_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Golden Headless Horseman Pet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#celestialvaultpack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Celestial Vault Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#etherealtrovepack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Ethereal Trove Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="adventurersarsenalpack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;&lt;a id="adventurersarsenalpack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Adventurer's Arsenal Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e147873fa982b6ebfdffdf1ba3a885d174b463ab.png?auto=compress,format&amp;w=300&amp;s=ebc5a9ca9a57e67c3ca486942a7b3e86"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/b2c646cf18dd3c96eaf09e72c43c48dbfa196d6f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e941698157b28c1984bc4d32103e3525"&gt;&lt;br&gt;Prepare for the ultimate expedition with the Adventurer’s Arsenal Pack for Dungeon Defenders II! This comprehensive pack comes with gems that allow you to buy cosmetic enhancements to adorn your heroes with, a selection of strategic Shards to bolster your defenses, and the practical additions of an extra bag and an expanded bank vault for all of your storage needs. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; To redeem the items contained in the pack, visit and interact with the Mailbox in the Heroes Marketplace or Private Tavern. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; This pack contains: &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  1,650 Gems &lt;/strong&gt; to purchase Heroes, Flairs, Costumes, and more. (1,500 + 150 Extra Gems!) &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  1 Inventory Bag &lt;/strong&gt; to carry more loot (up to a max of 8 bags). &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  1 Bank Vault &lt;/strong&gt; to store more items in town (up to a max of 12 vaults). &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  Five Campaign Shard Packs &lt;/strong&gt; to equip unique bonuses to your heroes and defenses.&lt;h3 id="burningsoulspack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;&lt;a id="burningsoulspack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Burning Souls Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7fe3f448825c8234689f0cdc001c4ab5c29d6d86.png?auto=compress,format&amp;w=300&amp;s=309c558af8e75423d2781fce2bc69f5f"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7ae01cec88d59095efd1805d94247bb8396b7a63.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=eb0ca56639f1d9ae5ee1ebbf7d6afa83"&gt;&lt;br&gt;Celebrate Halloween with our new Burning Souls Pack. Set up some fireworks, popcorn, and put on some Halloween masks to throw your own in-game party! Pick up the Burning Souls Pack now: &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; - 4 Burning Soul skins for the Original Heroes (Squire, Huntress, Apprentice, Monk) &lt;br&gt; - 50 Consumable Masks to spice up the party &lt;br&gt; - 10 Fireworks Launchers &lt;br&gt; - 10 Popcorn Machines to give you and your party some sweet combat buffs!&lt;h3 id="500gembundle_dungeondefendersii"&gt;&lt;a id="500gembundle_dungeondefendersii"&gt;500 Gem Bundle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c8fa6bb5c60a3a00039e09630ab57c7fb1cb8738.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=889d4cadaf0436176c85617b37eb9f9b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A respectable pouch of premium gems. Perfect for funding your next inventory tab or upgrading your fashion.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt12"&gt;Pay $12 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="imperialcachepack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;&lt;a id="imperialcachepack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Imperial Cache Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/52702b0363a183ea15202cacfc84a7f735b870db.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6d6f541eb48d2d6a17de015fd1291443"&gt;&lt;br&gt;Step into the realm of royalty with the Imperial Cache Pack for Dungeon Defenders II! This regal pack bestows upon your heroes cosmetic finery fit for kings and queens, along with a treasury of gems and Shards that will let you command respect and power across Etheria! &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; This pack may only be purchased once per account. To redeem the items contained in the pack, visit and interact with the Mailbox in the Heroes Marketplace or Private Tavern. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; This pack contains: &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  4,800 Gems &lt;/strong&gt; to purchase Heroes, Flair, Costumes, and more. (4,000 + 800 Extra Gems!) &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  5 Mythical Defender Packs &lt;/strong&gt; to gain any number of cosmetic rewards to look your best! &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  Two Shard Packs from Campaign and every level of Chaos (22 total!) &lt;/strong&gt; to equip unique bonuses to your heroes and defenses. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  Legendary Autumeow Pet &lt;/strong&gt; to wreck your enemies with natural power.&lt;h3 id="bundleofthebeast_dungeondefendersii"&gt;&lt;a id="bundleofthebeast_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Bundle of the Beast&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a627c5bec775251c75f71c4bcc843cbf22329c31.png?auto=compress,format&amp;w=300&amp;s=d7eeaed6948925d3a30bef88246c1c57"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8e03ca149c7b4aadff2ecd0d2313b3a3e2ac91f4.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=b2a728dc9b3cdf3f00e153d8d8ea0343"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;  &lt;i&gt;Dungeon Defenders II - Bundle of the Beast&lt;/i&gt; &lt;/strong&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; Embrace the Demon Lord with a set of accessories that can be equipped on any hero and four unique helmets for the original four heroes! This bundle contains: &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;u&gt;  The Hellion’s Mask, Wings, Tail and Fire Ember Trail &lt;/u&gt; accessories that can be equipped on any hero! &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;u&gt;  The Purrnicorn Mask &lt;/u&gt; helmet for the Huntress. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;u&gt;  The Bag ‘O’ Boogey &lt;/u&gt; helmet for the Monk. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;u&gt;  The Pumpkin Head Folly &lt;/u&gt; helmet for the Apprentice. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;u&gt;  The Dread Knight Casque &lt;/u&gt; helmet for the Squire. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;u&gt;  2,000,000 Gold &lt;/u&gt; for a quick boost in leveling your loot.&lt;h3 id="treasuretrovepack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;&lt;a id="treasuretrovepack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Treasure Trove Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6b515f9ef2d0c0f4af5d59a4e081d6cf7f82135c.png?auto=compress,format&amp;w=300&amp;s=8e9ca79cedd63f3f9e652f6ef1c5b7b2"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4a55f11cc9676161fa528a27c808610c91c611ef.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2d0491bf56013b3339020a25a5909f66"&gt;&lt;br&gt;Embark on an epic journey with the Treasure Trove Pack for Dungeon Defenders II! This pack is a collector’s dream, brimming with cosmetic treasures that will dazzle your allies and intimidate your foes. Unearth a wealth of Shards that promise to fortify your defenses and amplify your offense, as well as a chest full of gems to unlock even more cosmetic enhancements! &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; This pack may only be purchased once per account. To redeem the items contained in the pack, visit and interact with the Mailbox in the Heroes Marketplace or Private Tavern. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; This pack contains: &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  2,850 Gems &lt;/strong&gt; to purchase Heroes, Flair, Costumes, and more. (2,500 +  350 Extra Gems!) &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  2 Mythical Defender Packs &lt;/strong&gt; to gain any number of cosmetic rewards to look your best! &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  One Shard Pack from Campaign and every level of Chaos (11 total!) &lt;/strong&gt; to equip unique bonuses to your heroes and defenses. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  Legendary Terror Dragolich Pet &lt;/strong&gt; to strike fear into the hearts of your enemies.&lt;h3 id="1000gembundle_dungeondefendersii"&gt;&lt;a id="1000gembundle_dungeondefendersii"&gt;1000 Gem Bundle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2567eaa0085130c862c66e363e31d034e682cb4d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4d922c389c9c269c110fd776f0f50763"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A hefty helmet-full of premium gems. Perfect for funding your next inventory tab or upgrading your fashion.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt20"&gt;Pay $20 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="goldenheadlesshorsemanpet_dungeondefendersii"&gt;&lt;a id="goldenheadlesshorsemanpet_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Golden Headless Horseman Pet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/fb8e3893a2e2b12f45ab8985e13c67d74066ed1c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c111e50610bc31d088d6d38ec33b314f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;He may have lost his head, but he definitely kept his bling. A terrifyingly shiny companion to spook the old one's hoards.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="celestialvaultpack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;&lt;a id="celestialvaultpack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Celestial Vault Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/54416084ad883f1dd6adb8508b29d0c873d4a408.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=32b66f13315d80d37b8066d3597b5cf2"&gt;&lt;br&gt;Elevate your Dungeon Defenders II experience to the stars with the Celestial Vault Pack!  By acquiring this pack, you’ll not only show your support for the game but also gain our cosmic gratitude and celestial commendation. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; This pack may only be purchased once per account. To redeem the items contained in the pack, visit and interact with the Mailbox in the Heroes Marketplace or Private Tavern. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; This pack contains: &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  13000 Gems &lt;/strong&gt; to purchase Heroes, Flair, Costumes, and more. (10,000 + 3,000 Extra Gems!) &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  10 Mythical Defender Packs &lt;/strong&gt; to gain any number of cosmetic rewards to look your best! &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  Three Shard Packs from Campaign and every level of Chaos (33 total!) &lt;/strong&gt; to equip unique bonuses to your heroes and defenses. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  Legendary Katkarot Pet &lt;/strong&gt; to achieve ultimate levels of power! &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  Legendary Autumeow Pet &lt;/strong&gt; to wreck your enemies with natural power.&lt;h3 id="etherealtrovepack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;&lt;a id="etherealtrovepack_dungeondefendersii"&gt;Ethereal Trove Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f1948ac977daff3070091a871bf7085595bcbb79.png?auto=compress,format&amp;w=300&amp;s=4692638a0610ed729b07495844c59d05"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/74665b898713d065f44b9d06268b2d3e90f3c8bc.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5961e0d75696ff0d4ad165b12836eb96"&gt;&lt;br&gt;Unlock the mysteries of the arcane with the Ethereal Trove Pack for Dungeon Defenders II! This pack is a treasure chest of otherworldly delights that shimmer with an ethereal glow, and a cornucopia of gems and Shards to unlock ultimate mystical powers! &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; This pack may only be purchased once per account. To redeem the items contained in the pack, visit and interact with the Mailbox in the Heroes Marketplace or Private Tavern. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; This pack contains: &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  8100 Gems &lt;/strong&gt; to purchase Heroes, Flair, Costumes, and more. (6,500 + 1,600 Extra Gems!) &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  5 Mythical Defender Packs &lt;/strong&gt; to gain any number of cosmetic rewards to look your best! &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  Two Shard Packs from Campaign and every level of Chaos (22 total!) &lt;/strong&gt; to equip unique bonuses to your heroes and defenses. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;strong&gt;  Legendary Katkarot Pet &lt;/strong&gt; to achieve ultimate levels of power!&lt;/div&gt;</description>
