      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/336ef5e7a2dd29da4b0c0601c88db41c71b8ca13.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=8386a3106211d293f0152db294e68dc8"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/dfbd7e16996f197919e46224a4eac349054a05f1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=46919761bbc5bc93d766df748d929f40"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Create a slice of American life&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Celebrate the 250th birthday of the United States by adding a massive collection of A1 game assets to your personal library! Pay what you want for the World Builders: Americana Bundle and drop your players into a sinisterly simple suburban hellscape or a haunting hospital perfect for high-stakes sieges. Unlock 75+ themed asset packs like &lt;em&gt;Meridian 1988: Captain Jimmy's Seafood - Modular Environment (VOL 6)&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;Meridian 1988: Genie Service Station - Modular Environment (VOL 16)&lt;/em&gt;, and add detailed retro realism to your next project! As always, a portion of your purchase helps support the Forest School Foundation. &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ef9741;"&gt;Keys Expire. Please redeem before December 21, 2027.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#meridian1988_captainjimmysseafood_modularenvironmentvol6"&gt;Meridian 1988: Captain Jimmy's Seafood - Modular Environment (VOL 6)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#meridian1988_communitycenter_modularenvironmentvol10"&gt;Meridian 1988: Community Center - Modular Environment (VOL 10)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#boatyard_vol2_oldboatsnanite"&gt;Boatyard VOL.2 - Old Boats (Nanite)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#boatyard_vol4_boatsnanite"&gt;Boatyard VOL.4 - Boats (Nanite)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#boatyard_vol5_tugboatnanite"&gt;Boatyard VOL.5 - Tugboat (Nanite)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#fenc