      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 18:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4ce2b536ec2bc18a187ea13eacf5b26a72880367.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=1f48328b5cbaf2a29902cb943edbf831"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ab06dad2c6924a1006038975ad4de6f69ed7dfc2.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=d09c1f0e0e3b5ef0cea24b6dc6116355"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Master modern staples of game development&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Curious about game design? Then you need the Premium Sci-Fi Design Training Bundle by Learn Squared! Go from game lover to developer when you study under the best—learn how to bring your artistic side into the digital world with &lt;em&gt;Concepting in ZBrush&lt;/em&gt;, jump into your own vessel of the stars with &lt;em&gt;Starship Design&lt;/em&gt;, create original protagonists with &lt;em&gt;Futuristic Character Design&lt;/em&gt;, and more. Get the expert instruction and knowledge you seek, and help support Girls Who Code with your purchase! &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ef9741;"&gt;Keys Expire. Please redeem before July 7th, 2027. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#designingfuturisticvisuals"&gt;Designing Futuristic Visuals&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#fusionbasics"&gt;Fusion Basics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt18"&gt;Pay $18 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#armadaconceptart"&gt;Armada Concept Art&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#cinematicconceptdesign"&gt;Cinematic Concept Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#conceptarchitecture"&gt;Concept Architecture&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#hardsurfacemodeling"&gt;Hard Surface Modeling&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#industrialdesignfoundations"&gt;Industrial Design Foundations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#conceptinginzbrush"&gt;Concepting in ZBrush&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#dynamicconceptarti"&gt;Dynamic Concept Art I&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#futuristiccharacterdesign"&gt;Futuristic Character Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#hardsurfacedesign"&gt;Hard Surface Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#masteringfilmui"&gt;Mastering Film UI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#rethinkingweapondesign"&gt;Rethinking Weapon Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#starshipdesign"&gt;Starship Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#uianddatadesignforfilm"&gt;UI and Data Design for Film&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vehicleconceptart"&gt;Vehicle Concept Art&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="designingfuturisticvisuals"&gt;&lt;a id="designingfuturisticvisuals" href="https://youtu.be/wmS3RsxKHZU"&gt;Designing Futuristic Visuals&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create striking futuristic visuals with Toros Kose as you design assets, build compelling styleframes, and add animation for extra impact. This Director’s Cut edition delivers an expanded, updated look at his full professional workflow.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="fusionbasics"&gt;&lt;a id="fusionbasics" href="https://youtu.be/fZe-SLaSte8"&gt;Fusion Basics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn to use Autodesk Fusion with simple hands-on training. Rather than asking you to watch and memorize, this beginner-focused course guides you through core tools and workflows by having you create something new in each lesson.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt18"&gt;Pay $18 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="armadaconceptart"&gt;&lt;a id="armadaconceptart" href="https://youtu.be/H7Va7bl1tWQ"&gt;Armada Concept Art&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Experience a streamlined, production-level concept art workflow with Aaron Limonick. Using 3D-Coat, Blender, Octane and Photoshop, you’ll go from early ship sculpt to final cinematic render with clarity, efficiency and creative power.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cinematicconceptdesign"&gt;&lt;a id="cinematicconceptdesign" href="https://youtu.be/4v_oXw-5Mmc"&gt;Cinematic Concept Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create stunning works of art by implementing the powerful language of film. Follow along as concept artist John Sweeney teaches you to create a cinematic image from start to finish. Covering everything from film analysis, to photoshoots, to 2D/3D workflows, this course should prove invaluable for both beginners and experts alike.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="conceptarchitecture"&gt;&lt;a id="conceptarchitecture" href="https://youtu.be/Cf-Fg1X-0WE"&gt;Concept Architecture&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Explore a more artistic style of architectural concept design with Maxim Zhestkov. Learn his Cinema 4D, Arnold, and Photoshop techniques to craft striking images, including your own immersive 360° render.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="hardsurfacemodeling"&gt;&lt;a id="hardsurfacemodeling" href="https://youtu.be/gQW3OGtFSDA"&gt;Hard Surface Modeling&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Design functional, production-ready concepts in Fusion 360 with Kirill Chepizhko. Learn a streamlined 3D workflow that brings purpose to your ideas and equips you with the techniques needed to land your first gig.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="industrialdesignfoundations"&gt;&lt;a id="industrialdesignfoundations" href="https://youtu.be/89wM7z-XxZY"&gt;Industrial Design Foundations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Design real-world products with Tim Zarki as you learn industrial design fundamentals and Fusion 360 workflows. Move from thoughtful sketches to polished forms and finish with photoreal Keyshot renders that showcase your craftsmanship.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="conceptinginzbrush"&gt;&lt;a id="conceptinginzbrush" href="https://youtu.be/roRXk43yeNU"&gt;Concepting in ZBrush&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master ZBrush without the overwhelm as Alex Figini guides you through his full concepting workflow. Learn core principles, advanced sculpting, and how to build complex characters and props using ZBrush, Marvelous Designer, and Keyshot.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="dynamicconceptarti"&gt;&lt;a id="dynamicconceptarti" href="https://youtu.be/-f1Gumzdyzg"&gt;Dynamic Concept Art I&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock new creative possibilities with Louis Laurent’s fluid mix of 2D and 3D techniques. Learn to embrace happy accidents and build unique, expressive artworks with a process that keeps experimentation at the center.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="futuristiccharacterdesign"&gt;&lt;a id="futuristiccharacterdesign" href="https://youtu.be/wjhbrXOpK6Y"&gt;Futuristic Character Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn Maciej Kuciara’s full futuristic character design workflow from loose sketches to polished renders. Build speed, consistency, and clear design thinking as you tackle creative challenges alongside his professional process.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="hardsurfacedesign"&gt;&lt;a id="hardsurfacedesign" href="https://youtu.be/-Q6R3TTva1w"&gt;Hard Surface Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build hard-surface props of any size with Lars Sowig as he takes you through blocking, modeling, texturing, and rendering. Learn a full production workflow, right down to custom decals, and create props ready for films, games, and beyond.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="masteringfilmui"&gt;&lt;a id="masteringfilmui" href="https://youtu.be/76D8BjNRnZs"&gt;Mastering Film UI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn to design and animate incredible, film-ready UI for your next project with Kris Brady's comprehensive new course. Master the art of creating stunning interfaces that seamlessly integrate into any film project, and take your design skills to the next level.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="rethinkingweapondesign"&gt;&lt;a id="rethinkingweapondesign" href="https://youtu.be/_4hbX_bXqTE"&gt;Rethinking Weapon Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Reimagine weapon designs with confidence as Luis Carrasco guides you through creative workflows that do not require advanced drawing or 3D skills. Unlock your imagination, elevate your process, and design bold, inventive weapons at any level.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="starshipdesign"&gt;&lt;a id="starshipdesign" href="https://youtu.be/dlY3rCwwVBk"&gt;Starship Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Design cinematic spacecraft as you explore ideation, modeling, texturing, and presentation workflows. Create scientifically grounded ships and polished keyframes using Blender, Photoshop, and Octane.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="uianddatadesignforfilm"&gt;&lt;a id="uianddatadesignforfilm" href="https://youtu.be/rqAJaEdIFgs"&gt;UI and Data Design for Film&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;From thumbnail sketch to final render, visionary designer Ash Thorp will show you how to create production-ready UI and data elements for Hollywood films.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vehicleconceptart"&gt;&lt;a id="vehicleconceptart" href="https://youtu.be/Fpmb7ITjJUw"&gt;Vehicle Concept Art&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Boost your concept art workflow with Pablo Dominguez as you generate simple 3D assets, build dynamic compositions, and paint over them to create detailed, cinematic artwork for your projects or portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
