href="https://youtu.be/jj8QqEiihvg"&gt;Tech Trailer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Watch &lt;a href="https://www.wwiiwalkthrough.meshingunstudio.com/"&gt;Walkthrough Video&lt;/a&gt; (Coming soon)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Watch &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zfIAudEaHBA"&gt;SmartPoly's Review&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Download &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/3TUktend3w"&gt;Playable Demo&lt;/a&gt; from our Discord channel, located under -playable-demos&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Read WWII Liberation: &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/15GFarJQnrFBj0UlDT0GBIWS6xswP3kJXnVOzU1083T0/edit?usp=sharing"&gt;Documentation&lt;/a&gt; (Updating)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Check out the complete &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/15GFarJQnrFBj0UlDT0GBIWS6xswP3kJXnVOzU1083T0/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.a4g2uyha17in"&gt;List of assets&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Download &lt;a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UewqVz-EDCz4vRyoCA4EbuUb6dj65HXM/view?usp=sharing"&gt;Config&lt;/a&gt; folder (Optional: to ensure appropriate engine settings)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;World War 2: Liberation&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Introducing &lt;strong&gt;World War 2: Liberation&lt;/strong&gt;, a sprawling wartime environment and the most expansive, customizable WW2 pack on the marketplace. This collection is created for all media usage, such as games, cinematic trailers, movies, and more. The level is optimized with a variety of workflows. It is our biggest and most customizable city pack yet, with over a thousand detailed assets, modular buildings, drivable vehicles, and a ton of useful tools, even for your other projects and environments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Upgrades Roadmap&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We appreciate your reviews. They inspire us to create even more ambitious content.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5 Reviews:&lt;/strong&gt; Bullet Decals&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;25 Reviews:&lt;/strong&gt; Drivable French WWII Plane&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;45 Reviews:&lt;/strong&gt; Cafe Props&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;These features will be developed as a bonus to encourage community feedback if the pack is well received. Your reviews help shape the future of this pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Want more details?&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/15GFarJQnrFBj0UlDT0GBIWS6xswP3kJXnVOzU1083T0/edit?usp=sharing"&gt;Read the documentation here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Asset Pack Manager&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Full control of the level, lights, wind, optimization functions, and sound with a robust system to manage your pack.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Made for Unreal Engine 5 + Exclusive on Fab&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Built from the ground up for optimal performance&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Nanite enabled&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lumen enabled&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Levels and Maps&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;1 Showcase Map: Paris / European City&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Day, war fog, and midnight lighting&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;3 Overview Levels&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Assets Palette&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Master Material Guide&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Powerline Generator Tutorial&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Gritty Visuals&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;We bring you back to the 1940s with custom visuals, post-processing, filmic color grading, and many more atmospheric touches.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;6 Rigged Drivable Vehicles&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;1940s Car Types 1, 2, and 3&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Damaged versions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Truck&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Field Car&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tank (not drivable)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;880 War-Torn Assets&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Building architecture assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Props such as chairs, light poles, debris, curtains, desks, and other warzone elements&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Foliage with damaged trees, plant pots, grass, and more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Prefabs&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Assembled city buildings&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Assembled residential buildings&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Church&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Meshingun Master Material (New Update)&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Built-in powerful all-in-one shader&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Supports wetness/rain and snow&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Ultimate Glass Shader (New)&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Built-in powerful all-in-one glass shader&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Glass shards&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Windows&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fake interiors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Building Customization&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Adjust the color of walls, bricks, doors, windows, shops, and more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Uses a new optimized workflow&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Adjust glass types per instance, including broken, fake interior, translucent, and more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Blueprints&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Updated Powerline Generator&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pole Sign&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Light Poles&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Road Tool&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Simple Splines: Fence, Canal, Tram Track&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Niagara Systems&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Papers flying&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Leaves flying&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Plane war formation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Parachute soldiers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Bird flock system&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;And many more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Burning Cloth (New)&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;New addition to our Master Material&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Can be applied to any mesh&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Uses vertex color as a mask&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Burning Decal (New)&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Can be applied for an aerial burning effect&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Adjust the emissive, black mask, and more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Disclaimer&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Some of the bullet impact effects, explosions, and soldier characters shown in the cinematic trailer are not included in the pack. They are accessible from the Fab marketplace.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Social&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/meshingun.studio"&gt;Instagram&lt;/a&gt; |&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/meshingunstudio"&gt;YouTube&lt;/a&gt; |&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.facebook.com/meshingun.studio"&gt;Facebook&lt;/a&gt; |&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/meshingun-studio/"&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; |&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.artstation.com/meshingun-studio"&gt;ArtStation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="meridian1988_14widowstreet_modularenvironmentvol31"&gt;&lt;a id="meridian1988_14widowstreet_modularenvironmentvol31"&gt;Meridian 1988: 14 Widow Street - Modular Environment (VOL 31)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/40bf866bf43b577d0bdf12d61a3ad209e91f6fde.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1a94e3f934b52340f6c42fe3c195ce91"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This project includes everything pictured, with all assets, maps, and&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    materials created in Unreal Engine. Each asset was created for realistic&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    AAA-quality visuals, style, and budget.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Documentation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://dekogon.notion.site/Town-Buildings-Meridian-1988-f9387634a8bd42909e7d8062fa1adc0d?source=copy_link"&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Town Buildings - Meridian 1988 Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;589 meshes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes the full scene pictured here.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes both day and nighttime lighting.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes a complex landscape material with auto meshing.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality 4K texture sets.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Master material setup controlling the majority of props and models.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional controls for roughness, albedo, normals, and more.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Channel-packed Roughness, Metalness, and Ambient Occlusion.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Realistic post-process and look-up table.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Optimized for games.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tintable painted areas.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Free of legal issues, with all branding and labels custom-made by the studio.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully detailed models.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Supports Lumen for Unreal Engine 5.0+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://docs.unrealengine.com/5.0/en-US/lumen-global-illumination-and-reflections-in-unreal-engine/"&gt;&lt;p&gt;            Unreal Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Supports Nanite for Unreal Engine 5.0+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/nanite-virtualized-geometry-in-unreal-engine?application_version=5.0"&gt;&lt;p&gt;            Unreal Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Notes&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Textures are generally 4K in the package but have been set to use max size.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        You can edit this to return them to the original 4K size.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The full level is included and precompiled into a level to be used and placed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The full project is 21 GB.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Art created by Dekogon Studios artists.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;About the Meridian Project&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        A storm has cut Meridian, USA off from the mainland, but it is not the&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        weather that keeps people from leaving.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        The fog has settled. The streets are silent. The townsfolk are acting&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        strange. At night, church bells drift across the harbor, and uneasy&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        gatherings take place behind shuttered windows.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Meridian 1988 is a collection of eerie, story-rich environments inspired&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        by the coastal towns of East Coast America, including empty homes,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        dimly lit chapels, quiet main streets, and weathered seaside structures.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Explore the remnants of the town of Meridian. You may discover something&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        far more sinister.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="lighthouse_meshingun"&gt;&lt;a id="lighthouse_meshingun" href="https://youtu.be/TJGPPeMylDc"&gt;THE LIGHTHOUSE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/3TUktend3w"&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Join our Discord&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        to get the latest updates and news about our products, get support,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        participate in our contests and win exciting prizes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.artstation.com/artwork/Ez0oze"&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Detailed Images And Videos Here&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Coming to Unity Soon&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;     Watch&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/TJGPPeMylDc"&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;THE LIGHTHOUSE - UE5 Island Level | Playable Open World + Full Interior&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;     Watch &lt;strong&gt;Walkthrough Video&lt;/strong&gt; (Coming Soon)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;     Download&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/3TUktend3w"&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Playable Demo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    from our Discord channel (located under -playable-demos)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;     Read THE LIGHTHOUSE:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XK1oVww_EF-G4cdkECHsZRDuVsmNKjcyJ380P87J4kk/edit?usp=sharing"&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Documentation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    (Updating)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;     Check out the complete&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XK1oVww_EF-G4cdkECHsZRDuVsmNKjcyJ380P87J4kk/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.a4g2uyha17in"&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;List of Assets&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;     Download&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UewqVz-EDCz4vRyoCA4EbuUb6dj65HXM/view?usp=sharing"&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Config Folder&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    (Optional: to ensure appropriate engine settings)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;p&gt;    Introducing &lt;strong&gt;THE LIGHTHOUSE&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    Lighthouses always carry a kind of magic. There is a calm beauty in the way&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    they rise against the sea, guiding travelers through the dark, but they also&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    hold a quiet mystery that makes them perfect for horror.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    That contrast is what inspired us to create this pack, and we hope you enjoy&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    building your own worlds with it.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Upgrade Roadmap&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;15 Reviews:&lt;/strong&gt; Sunset Lighting Scenario&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;25 Reviews:&lt;/strong&gt; Full-Control Flyable Helicopter&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;    These features will be developed as a bonus to encourage community feedback&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    if the pack is well received. Your reviews help shape the future of the lighthouse.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Want more details?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XK1oVww_EF-G4cdkECHsZRDuVsmNKjcyJ380P87J4kk/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.gjdgxs"&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Read the Full Roadmap and Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Made for Unreal Engine 5&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Built from the ground up for optimal performance&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Nanite Enabled&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modular / Extendable&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;HLODs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;World Partition Level&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lumen Enabled&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Lowpoly Baked Workflow&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Usable for VR, Mobile, and lower-end systems&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Showcase Map&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Island Environment&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Daylight Lighting&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dynamic Lighting&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Night Lighting&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Overview Level&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Asset Palette&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Atmospheric Visuals&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        A striking lighthouse island with custom visuals,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        post-processing, filmic color grading, and atmospheric effects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;4 Customizable Vehicles&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Motorboat&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Inflatable Boat&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Helicopter&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lift Machine&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;350+ Detailed Assets&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Building Architecture&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Environmental Props&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Foliage Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Damaged Trees&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Grass and Vegetation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Prefabs&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Assembled Foliage Blocks&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Assembled Lighthouse&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Assembled House&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Master Material&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Built In-House&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Powerful All-in-One Shader&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;PCG Biome&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Automatic Vegetation Variations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Road System&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Dynamic Day &amp;amp; Night&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Automatically transitions between day and night with customizable settings.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Blueprints&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;LITE Powerline Generator&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Vehicles&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lighthouse Fresnel Lens God Rays&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fence Splines&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Niagara Systems&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Flying Leaves&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Smoke Effects&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Bird Flock System&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional Effects&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Social&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/meshingun.studio"&gt;Instagram&lt;/a&gt; |&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/meshingunstudio"&gt;YouTube&lt;/a&gt; |&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.facebook.com/meshingun.studio"&gt;Facebook&lt;/a&gt; |&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/meshingun-studio/"&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; |&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.artstation.com/meshingun-studio"&gt;ArtStation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="meridian1988_55elmstreet_modularenvironmentvol21"&gt;&lt;a id="meridian1988_55elmstreet_modularenvironmentvol21"&gt;Meridian 1988: 55 Elm Street - Modular Environment (VOL 21)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e4595e2ccf42bb985fe00b44b7ab7f495b536a12.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0c587abc323aef043cd29a2564baca3a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This project includes everything pictured, with all assets, maps, and&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    materials created in Unreal Engine. Each asset was created for realistic&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    AAA-quality visuals, style, and budget.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Documentation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://dekogon.notion.site/Town-Buildings-Meridian-1988-f9387634a8bd42909e7d8062fa1adc0d?source=copy_link"&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Town Buildings - Meridian 1988 Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;668 meshes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes the full scene pictured here.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes both day and nighttime lighting.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes a complex landscape material with auto meshing.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality 4K texture sets.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Master material setup controlling the majority of props and models.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional controls for roughness, albedo, normals, and more.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Channel-packed Roughness, Metalness, and Ambient Occlusion.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Realistic post-process and look-up table.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes a fully modeled 1980s police car.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Optimized for games.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tintable painted areas.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Free of legal issues, with all branding and labels custom-made by the studio.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully detailed models.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Supports Lumen for Unreal Engine 5.0+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://docs.unrealengine.com/5.0/en-US/lumen-global-illumination-and-reflections-in-unreal-engine/"&gt;&lt;p&gt;            Unreal Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Supports Nanite for Unreal Engine 5.0+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/nanite-virtualized-geometry-in-unreal-engine?application_version=5.0"&gt;&lt;p&gt;            Unreal Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Notes&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Textures are generally 4K in the package but have been set to use max size.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        You can edit this to return them to the original 4K size.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The full level is included and precompiled into a level to be used and placed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The full project is 17 GB.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Art created by Dekogon Studios artists.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;About the Meridian Project&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        A storm has cut Meridian, USA off from the mainland, but it is not the&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        weather that keeps people from leaving.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        The fog has settled. The streets are silent. The townsfolk are acting&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        strange. At night, church bells drift across the harbor, and uneasy&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        gatherings take place behind shuttered windows.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Meridian 1988 is a collection of eerie, story-rich environments inspired&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        by the coastal towns of East Coast America, including empty homes,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        dimly lit chapels, quiet main streets, and weathered seaside structures.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Explore the remnants of the town of Meridian. You may discover something&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        far more sinister.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="gothicinteriormegapack"&gt;&lt;a id="gothicinteriormegapack" href="https://youtu.be/WSUqPZvVU4I"&gt;Gothic Interior Megapack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Render Pipelines: &lt;strong&gt;HDRP URP BUILT-IN&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Support for &lt;strong&gt;Unity 6, 6.1&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Originally built in &lt;em&gt;Unreal Engine&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;─────────────── LINKS ───────────────&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/3TUktend3w" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join our Discord&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    to get the latest updates and news about our products, get support, participate in our contests, and win exciting prizes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;     Face any issues?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1M-bAAihhJ-IshYcHJ6wS4VYSNeBHAPDTFtzLi5MEWzI/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Read Documentation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;     Also available on &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/c856b256-c060-4337-8156-8b604ce0cadd" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unreal Engine&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;     Get the Book Generator standalone:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.unrealengine.com/marketplace/en-US/product/book-generator-meshingun-studio" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Book Generator (Unreal Engine)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/WSUqPZvVU4I" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gothic Interior&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/IRJ5pZLPWZw" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cathedral/dungeon walkthrough&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    ⭐ &lt;strong&gt;Goes well with our exterior Megapack:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.unrealengine.com/marketplace/en-US/product/gothic-mega-pack-by-meshingun-studio" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Gothic Exterior Megapack&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;───────────── SUMMARY ─────────────&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    Our next Megapack collection for Unity is here — the Gothic Cathedral.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    This is one of the largest Gothic interior libraries available, filled with ornate details, dramatic silhouettes, and carefully crafted architecture.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    It also includes convenient tools, templates, and setup helpers so you can build rich cathedral environments fast and with full artistic control.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="airportsetvol1"&gt;&lt;a id="airportsetvol1"&gt;Airport Set Vol1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9f88603417bc41cc66687fd5103585f492cfa863.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6e8c8e63e43fa5aba58b253e937b8d2e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Join our Discord&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;to get the latest updates and news about our products, get support, participate in our contests, and win exciting prizes.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;hr&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Keywords:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Airport Terminal, Luggage, Suitcase, Carry-on, Seating, Lounge Chair, Security Scanner, X-ray Machine, Metal Detector, Checkpoint, Surveillance Camera, CCTV,&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Payphone, ATM, Clock, Bar Counter, Bar Stool, Vending Machine, Escalator, Baggage Claim, Waiting Area, Information Desk, Ticket Counter, Modular Furniture,&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Transit Hub, Check-in Desk, Public Seating&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="airportsetvol2"&gt;&lt;a id="airportsetvol2"&gt;Airport Set Vol2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/407c5b24315a0c87aaf49e916fbe7d2b9228af56.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7cb7ada499540f4ff719569676e5589a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Join our Discord&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;to get the latest updates and news about our products, get support, participate in our contests, and win exciting prizes.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;hr&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Keywords:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Airport, Airport Interior, Airport Props, Transportation Hub, Terminal Assets, Travel Environment, Public Space, Facility Assets, Commercial Environment,&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Modular Airport Pack, Check-in Area, Security Checkpoint, Waiting Area, Boarding Gate, Baggage Claim, Passenger Terminal, Airport Lounge, Airport Seating,&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Terminal Seats, Queue Barriers, Information Desk, Kiosk, Luggage Cart, Security Scanner, X-Ray Machine, Waste Bin, Trash Can, Trolley, Tray, Monitor Screen,&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Digital Signage, Flight Display Board, FIDS, Advertisement Stand, Banner Display, Office Chair, Wet Floor Sign, Wayfinding Signage&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="airportsetvol3-signage"&gt;&lt;a id="airportsetvol3-signage"&gt;Airport Set Vol3-Signage&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/36c996e61e6888bd2d9fc1b3917be729e7dcde77.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=30d49a75ce40754780b9623262087130"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Join our Discord&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;to get the latest updates and news about our products, get support, participate in our contests, and win exciting prizes.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;All of the signs are designed with modularity and optimization in mind. The bases of the signs can be tinted, allowing you to customize them in any color you choose.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Additionally, the text on the signs consists of mesh decals, which means you can remove, exchange, or even create your own text texture to replace them.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;hr&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Keywords:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Airport, Airport Interior, Airport Props, Transportation Hub, Terminal Assets, Travel Environment, Public Space, Facility Assets, Commercial Environment, Modular Airport Pack,&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Check-in Area, Security Checkpoint, Waiting Area, Boarding Gate, Baggage Claim, Passenger Terminal, Airport Lounge, Airport Seating, Terminal Seats, Queue Barriers,&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Information Desk, Kiosk, Luggage Cart, Security Scanner, X-Ray Machine, Waste Bin, Trash Can, Trolley, Tray, Monitor Screen, Digital Signage, Flight Display Board,&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;FIDS, Advertisement Stand, Banner Display, Office Chair, Wet Floor Sign, Wayfinding Signage&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="nanitefoliagevol1"&gt;&lt;a id="nanitefoliagevol1"&gt;Nanite Foliage Vol1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/312ce30bc9c5357a13baf78bc29d5de3147d82f2.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=299934c18042924537a9783ad4