;p&gt;┗⊱ Sounds ⊰┛&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;┗⊱ Color Customization ⊰┛&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="decay_oildrumsdistrict_rustyindustrialslum"&gt;&lt;a id="decay_oildrumsdistrict_rustyindustrialslum" href="https://youtu.be/wGZzSw9QmnE"&gt;Decay: Oil Drums District - [Rusty Industrial Slum]&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;"&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Links&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;     Already own the pack?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=""&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Join our Discord to get the free Storm Weather DLC&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    receive updates, and get support for your product.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=""&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Playable Demo (Windows 7/8/10/11)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=""&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Playable Demo (Linux)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=""&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Watch the Showcase&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=""&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Decay: Oil Drums District Documentation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;     Static Mesh List:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=""&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;See Documentation (Page 30)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    Review:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    Watch a detailed review from MR3D-DEV&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=""&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;here&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Summary&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Decay: Oil Drums District&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Suitable for everyone from solo developers to large studios.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ideal for storytelling in post-apocalyptic and abandoned environments.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Over 450 static mesh assets.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Advanced smart shader system.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Designed to simplify wasteland environment creation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy to use and highly customizable.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;4 Master Shaders&lt;/strong&gt; – Create realistic weathered surfaces,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        aged metal, rust, dirt, and environmental effects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;280+ Material Instances&lt;/strong&gt; – Extensive customization options&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        for vegetation, terrain, and environmental assets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;457 Textures&lt;/strong&gt; – High-quality texture library with more than&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        115 unique texture variations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;450 Unique Assets&lt;/strong&gt; – Includes props such as plates, cups,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        tires, barrels, modular structures, and 25 pre-assembled buildings.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Blueprint-Based Tools&lt;/strong&gt; – Includes powerline generators and&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        material variation tools for fast and flexible world building.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;"&lt;h3 id="ancientmayanruins"&gt;&lt;a id="ancientmayanruins" href="https://youtu.be/gJd0DrlwrKU"&gt;Ancient Mayan Ruins&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;─────────────── LINKS ───────────────&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/3TUktend3w" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Join our Discord&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;  to get the latest updates and news about our products, get support, participate in our contests, and win exciting prizes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;┏━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┓&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Watch the &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/gJd0DrlwrKU" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ancient Mayan Ruins&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;  trailer&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Check out the complete &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IDqESySYVo-WBSYD_M8vHihLSEkslY4uWKnYDwNaEro/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;List of assets&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;┗━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┛&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;───────────── SUMMARY ─────────────&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;  Our “Ancient Mayan Ruins” environment captures the look and feel of Mayan architecture with detailed and realistic assets. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;  While it’s not a large level, it’s designed to be flexible and easy to scale for your needs. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;  Perfect for adding a rich, atmospheric touch to any historical or adventure project!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="fafnirskeep"&gt;&lt;a id="fafnirskeep" href="https://youtu.be/-CVa25sLV3g"&gt;Fafnir's Keep&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/07b79241c3c10b27bfa6d14047b218944b003ada.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3709104df4b396f9f7e58d9f746283df"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;───────────── SUMMARY ─────────────&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Enter the world of Fafnir's Keep, a stunning fantasy environment pack filled with detailed, medieval-inspired architecture and atmospheric lighting. This pack is perfect for adding a touch of grandeur and mystery to your game or project.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;───────────── FEATURES ──────────────&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Showcase Map:&lt;/strong&gt; Fafnir’s Keep includes a fully laid-out map, allowing you to quickly immerse players in a glossy and beautiful medieval fantasy setting.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Architecture Sets:&lt;/strong&gt; Set of architecture pieces (walls, gates, doors, pillars, banisters) to help you develop and expand the environment as you like&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unique Meshes:&lt;/strong&gt; Featuring &lt;strong&gt;118 detailed meshes&lt;/strong&gt; that bring life to the keep, including architecture, props, and set dressing elements.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Blueprints:&lt;/strong&gt; 23 blueprints for easy integration and customization within your project, saving you time and effort.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Materials and Instances:&lt;/strong&gt; Includes &lt;strong&gt;37 materials&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;158 material instances&lt;/strong&gt; for extensive customization options, allowing you to create a variety of looks and styles for your environment.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Textures:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;239 high-quality textures&lt;/strong&gt; in various resolutions, including:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collision:&lt;/strong&gt; Fully set up collision for interactive gameplay elements.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LOD Support:&lt;/strong&gt; Using Nanite for Unreal Engine 5.3+, no LODs required for optimized performance.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;─────────── Installation Notes ────────────&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ol&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;Enable "Niagara Fluids" built-in plugin for particles to work properly (Follow image guideline)&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ol&gt; &lt;p&gt;Credit:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Environment Artist: &lt;strong&gt;Kristofer Lalinde&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;─────────────── LINKS ───────────────&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://discord.gg/3TUktend3w" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join our Discord&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to get the latest updates and news about our products, get support, participate in our contests and win exciting prizes.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coming to Unity Store&lt;/strong&gt; TBA&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://youtu.be/-CVa25sLV3g" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Watch Showcase&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Read Asset Pack Documentation:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1jjIHnrREeaZO6DCv_zdR7AATMkkSeoqXeRlZttA-rfA/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Documentation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1jjIHnrREeaZO6DCv_zdR7AATMkkSeoqXeRlZttA-rfA/edit#heading=h.u5bhvyn4c4qm" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Check out the complete List of assets&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="feudaljapanmegapackextrapack"&gt;&lt;a id="feudaljapanmegapackextrapack" href="https://youtu.be/1ykMzp4cVeA"&gt;Feudal Japan Megapack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Supported Render Pipelines:&lt;/strong&gt; HDRP, URP&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Support for &lt;strong&gt;Unity 6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/blockquote&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Attention !!!&lt;/strong&gt; This pack supports two render pipelines: HDRP and URP.   &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Due to the large project size (textures and static meshes), we lowered the default texture sizes, but we provide download links for the full high-quality textures for each pipeline.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;─────────────── LINKS ───────────────&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/3TUktend3w" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join our Discord&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    to get the latest updates, support, contest access, and prize opportunities. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://meshingun-studio.com/404" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Contact us if you require High Quality textures&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reviews:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Review from &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/VtqcIYFgSQA" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JSFILMZ&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Watch&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fr3GJ9m0290&amp;amp;pp=ygUSZmV1ZGFsIGphcGFuIHVuaXR5" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Showcase&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Also available on&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.unrealengine.com/marketplace/en-US/product/feudal-japan-megapack" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unreal Engine&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;    Introducing our new Megapack collection for Unity, inspired by Feudal Japan.   &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    The pack features high-quality, customizable assets with modular designs that make assembly easy.   &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    All textures, models, shaders, and tools have been optimized and tested in real-time to ensure strong performance. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;    The theme draws from the architecture and daily life of Feudal Japan – temples, merchant stalls, wooden structures, vegetation, and environment details crafted to match the era. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;With more than 400 assets and prefabs, this is one of the largest libraries of high-end Japanese-themed assets.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Showcase and Overview Map&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;5 Shaders and 251 Materials&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;        400 Assets and Prefabs &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;62 Unique and Modular Assets&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Modular Architecture Pieces such as Walls, Railings, Roofs, etc.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Foliage such as Trees, Bushes, Vines, etc.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Variety of decals → Leak, Dust, etc.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;        615 High-Quality Textures, including Tillable and Trim sheets &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Unique textures&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Decal textures&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="meridian1988_genieservicestation_modularenvironmentvol16"&gt;&lt;a id="meridian1988_genieservicestation_modularenvironmentvol16"&gt;Meridian 1988: Genie Service Station - Modular Environment (VOL 16)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/006e88b278cead6b0507cf098ed21cdce0ca30bb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1212fa4e330ce8110bd813c4d55ce881"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A comprehensive modular environment featuring a realistic AAA-quality 1980s service station and police car, optimized for Unreal Engine with Nanite and Lumen support.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="meridian1988_mickeysrepairshop_modularenvironmentvol38"&gt;&lt;a id="meridian1988_mickeysrepairshop_modularenvironmentvol38"&gt;Meridian 1988: Mickey's Repair Shop - Modular Environment (VOL 38)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/58a95e4fb99a231da8a8a0e6b49802d99df13c9b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=08ea8bf6157e6ccb23a51ff699b3df2c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This project includes everything pictured, with all assets, maps, and&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    materials created in Unreal Engine. Each asset was created for realistic&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    AAA-quality visuals, style, and budget.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Documentation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://dekogon.notion.site/Town-Buildings-Meridian-1988-f9387634a8bd42909e7d8062fa1adc0d?source=copy_link"&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Town Buildings - Meridian 1988 Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;667 meshes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes the full scene pictured here.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes both day and nighttime lighting.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes a complex landscape material with auto meshing.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality 4K texture sets.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Master material setup controlling the majority of props and models.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional controls for roughness, albedo, normals, and more.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Channel-packed Roughness, Metalness, and Ambient Occlusion.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Realistic post-process and look-up table.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes a fully modeled 1980s police car.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Optimized for games.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tintable painted areas.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Free of legal issues, with all branding and labels custom-made by the studio.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully detailed models.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Supports Lumen for Unreal Engine 5.0+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://docs.unrealengine.com/5.0/en-US/lumen-global-illumination-and-reflections-in-unreal-engine/"&gt;&lt;p&gt;            Unreal Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Supports Nanite for Unreal Engine 5.0+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/nanite-virtualized-geometry-in-unreal-engine?application_version=5.0"&gt;&lt;p&gt;            Unreal Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Notes&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Textures are generally 4K in the package but have been set to use max size.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        You can edit this to return them to the original 4K size.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The full level is included and precompiled into a level to be used and placed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The full project is 21 GB.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Art created by Dekogon Studios artists.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;About the Meridian Project&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        A storm has cut Meridian, USA off from the mainland, but it is not the&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        weather that keeps people from leaving.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        The fog has settled. The streets are silent. The townsfolk are acting&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        strange. At night, church bells drift across the harbor, and uneasy&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        gatherings take place behind shuttered windows.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Meridian 1988 is a collection of eerie, story-rich environments inspired&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        by the coastal towns of East Coast America, including empty homes,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        dimly lit chapels, quiet main streets, and weathered seaside structures.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Explore the remnants of the town of Meridian. You may discover something&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        far more sinister.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="asiancentralmarket_modularenvironment"&gt;&lt;a id="asiancentralmarket_modularenvironment"&gt;Asian Central Market - Modular Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/483c7c994950e9f3afa80228fcdf5c68d221eb5d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=bb4584831799d88d9b7205edebf3486d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Documentation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://dekogon.notion.site/Asian-Central-Market-3360a126b144807ea191cbdff99a115f?pvs=73"&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Asian Central Market Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    This project includes everything pictured, with all assets, maps, and&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    materials created in Unreal Engine. Each asset was created for realistic&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    AAA-quality visuals, style, and budget.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;1262 meshes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes the full scene pictured here.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality 4K texture sets.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Master material setup controlling the majority of props and models.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional controls for roughness, albedo, normals, and more.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Channel-packed Roughness, Metalness, and Ambient Occlusion.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Realistic post-process and look-up table.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Optimized for games.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Daytime lighting scenes included.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Interior and exterior gameplay space.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Free of legal issues, with all branding and labels custom-made by the studio.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully detailed models.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Supports Lumen for Unreal Engine 5.0+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://docs.unrealengine.com/5.0/en-US/lumen-global-illumination-and-reflections-in-unreal-engine/"&gt;&lt;p&gt;            Unreal Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;p&gt;    Art created by Dekogon Studios artists.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="meridian1988_brookerwarehouse_modularenvironmentvol47"&gt;&lt;a id="meridian1988_brookerwarehouse_modularenvironmentvol47"&gt;Meridian 1988: Brooker Warehouse - Modular Environment (VOL 47)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6957f03e6d2102297bd80d29e5b16930be913614.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=57be9b08dbbb0bb4e930e6fc300f2417"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This project includes everything pictured, with all assets, maps, and&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    materials created in Unreal Engine. Each asset was created for realistic&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    AAA-quality visuals, style, and budget.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Documentation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://dekogon.notion.site/Town-Buildings-Meridian-1988-f9387634a8bd42909e7d8062fa1adc0d?source=copy_link"&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Town Buildings - Meridian 1988 Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;439 meshes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes the full scene pictured here.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes both day and nighttime lighting.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes a complex landscape material with auto meshing.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality 4K texture sets.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Master material setup controlling the majority of props and models.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional controls for roughness, albedo, normals, and more.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Channel-packed Roughness, Metalness, and Ambient Occlusion.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Realistic post-process and look-up table.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Includes a fully modeled 1980s police car.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Optimized for games.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tintable painted areas.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Free of legal issues, with all branding and labels custom-made by the studio.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully detailed models.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Supports Lumen for Unreal Engine 5.0+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://docs.unrealengine.com/5.0/en-US/lumen-global-illumination-and-reflections-in-unreal-engine/"&gt;&lt;p&gt;            Unreal Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Supports Nanite for Unreal Engine 5.0+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/nanite-virtualized-geometry-in-unreal-engine?application_version=5.0"&gt;&lt;p&gt;            Unreal Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Notes&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Textures are generally 4K in the package but have been set to use max size.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        You can edit this to return them to the original 4K size.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The full level is included and precompiled into a level to be used and placed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The full project is 15 GB.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Art created by Dekogon Studios artists.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;About the Meridian Project&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        A storm has cut Meridian, USA off from the mainland, but it is not the&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        weather that keeps people from leaving.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        The fog has settled. The streets are silent. The townsfolk are acting&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        strange. At night, church bells drift across the harbor, and uneasy&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        gatherings take place behind shuttered windows.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Meridian 1988 is a collection of eerie, story-rich environments inspired&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        by the coastal towns of East Coast America, including empty homes,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        dimly lit chapels, quiet main streets, and weathered seaside structures.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Explore the remnants of the town of Meridian. You may discover something&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        far more sinister.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="meridian1988_communitycenter_modularenvironmentvol10"&gt;&lt;a id="meridian1988_communitycenter_modularenvironmentvol10"&gt;Meridian 1988: Community Center - Modular Environment (VOL 10)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a51e7cedc9591b20348a641fdc27172e38374ab5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6bfe1c4c20777779f5aa2f5b5a10facb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A story-rich modular environment featuring a realistic AAA-quality community center with 962 meshes, 4k textures, and day/night lighting, optimized for Unreal Engine.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="suburbs_vol28_morevendingnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="suburbs_vol28_morevendingnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Suburbs VOL.28 - MORE Vending (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/dea0012d3bd263f41ba3bdf0eae7d5a9646b9dfd.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c7a2f7397c32ca7d36a82780f2fecef7"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A comprehensive collection of highly detailed vending and service-related 3D models and assets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="worldtravel_vol4-asianmarketnanitepluslowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="worldtravel_vol4-asianmarketnanitepluslowpoly"&gt;World Travel VOL.4- Asian Market (Nanite + Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.ne