f each mesh.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Free of legal issues, with all branding and labels custom-made by the studio.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Supports Lumen for Unreal Engine 5.0+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://docs.unrealengine.com/5.0/en-US/lumen-global-illumination-and-reflections-in-unreal-engine/"&gt;&lt;p&gt;            Unreal Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;p&gt;    Art created by Dekogon Studios artists.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="retro80s_vol5_moretoysandgamesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="retro80s_vol5_moretoysandgamesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Retro 80's VOL.5 - MORE Toys &amp; Games (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1472ae2140e6c3495ccb357c96293725261b8466.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1d503ca70e7f765e707d6594b3dec904"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A collection of high-quality retro-themed toy and game 3D models and assets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildings_vol17_rooftopsnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="buildings_vol17_rooftopsnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Buildings VOL.17 - Rooftops (Nanite &amp; Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ba213cbffee63cd956f9e89171a90929a8553373.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0b6139dcb446c6f78093aef463287ed5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Documentation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.notion.so/dekogon/Buildings-99b96370ad3f4ff0a96e0fde60f1695f"&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Buildings Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    This project includes everything pictured, with all assets, maps, and&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    materials created in Unreal Engine. Each asset was created for realistic&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    AAA-quality visuals, style, and budget.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Note: These assets are constructed using Nanite for high-quality&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;        fidelity polycounts and include low-poly versions as well.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;86 meshes, split between Nanite versions and low-poly versions.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-quality 4K texture sets.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Master material setup controlling the majority of props and models.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional controls for roughness, albedo, normals, and more.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Channel-packed Roughness, Metalness, and Ambient Occlusion.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Split meshes to support door interaction, including opening and closing.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Realistic post-process and look-up table.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Optimized for games.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Color-changeable painted parts.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Free of legal issues, with all branding and labels custom-made by the studio.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully detailed models from all sides.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Supports Lumen for Unreal Engine 5.0+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://docs.unrealengine.com/5.0/en-US/lumen-global-illumination-and-reflections-in-unreal-engine/"&gt;&lt;p&gt;            Unreal Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;        Uses Nanite-based geometry for Unreal Engine 5.0+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://docs.unrealengine.com/5.0/en-US/nanite-virtualized-geometry-in-unreal-engine"&gt;&lt;p&gt;            Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;&lt;p&gt;    Art created by Dekogon Studios artists.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="rocks_vol4_snowwetnessmossnanite"&gt;&lt;a id="rocks_vol4_snowwetnessmossnanite"&gt;Rocks VOL.4 - Snow, Wetness, Moss (Nanite)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/62cbe463cdb49b195bc72c346b7cda9c5e62720e.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c67cee11ace894c34c6743f5be534f45"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Documentation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.