      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7d4e36074ec9e12313d00fbfa1afd18966d22f27.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=6d71b031d7e6ee8c826e2926a364f5a5"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/55c1f644eb84cf51f718f9755e9077c44a2e9e39.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=1eaf7fb4116b18a290162bf68f83adcd"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Bloody-good creature &amp; monster assets&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bring monstrosities, blood-dripping creatures, and ghastly ghouls to life with a curated bundle of assets designed to get your players’ hearts pumping! Pay what you want for hundreds of specialized asset packs that work seamlessly with your preferred creation platforms, such as VDM Blender and ZBrush, including &lt;em&gt;Faceit: Facial Expressions and Performance Capture&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;Base Mesh Mega Pack 3D Models - Human, Anime &amp; Cartoon Animals&lt;/em&gt;. Plus, your purchase includes 44 ears, 44 teeth, 44 noses, and much, much more. Create amazing monsters before it’s too late, and help support Save the Children with your purchase! &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ef9741;"&gt;Keys expire. Please redeem your keys before October 31, 2026. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#conceptcreatingcharacterconceptartwithblenderandgreasepencil"&gt;CONCEPT | Creating Character Concept Art with Blender and Grease Pencil&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#basemeshcreatestylizedcharactersquicklywithblender"&gt;BASEMESH | Create Stylized Characters Quickly with Blender&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#retopoflow4"&gt;Retopoflow 4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtoretopologywiththeretopoflowadd-on"&gt;Intro to Retopology with the Retopoflow Add-on&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#realisticmaleandfemalecharactercreatorbundle_rigged280plusblendsha"&gt;Realistic Male &amp; Female Character Creator Bundle - Rigged | 280+ Blendshapes | Arkit 52 | Blender Add-On&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#pothead_ablenderhardsurfacecharactercreationcourse"&gt;Pothead - A Blender Hard Surface Character Creation Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#globalskin_ultimateskinshader"&gt;GlobalSkin - Ultimate Skin Shader&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#figaro_fastbasemeshes"&gt;Figaro - Fast Base Meshes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#ultra-realisticgum_8kpbrgame-readyfullyriggedblender"&gt;Ultra-Realistic Gum - 8K PBR | Game-Ready | Fully Rigged | Blender&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#customisablemaleplusfemalebasemeshbundle_blender50plus"&gt;Customisable Male + Female Basemesh Bundle - Blender 5.0+&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt30"&gt;Pay $30 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#basemeshescharacterstarterkitplusrig"&gt;Base Meshes Character Starter Kit + Rig&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#blazepuppeteer"&gt;Blaze Puppeteer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#faceit_facialexpressionsandperformancecapture"&gt;Faceit : Facial Expressions and Performance Capture&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#charactergenerator_access2billioncombinationsof3dcharacters"&gt;Character generator - Access 2 billion combinations of 3D characters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#44teeth_highdetailedteethforcreatures_blenderassetslibraryimmzbrus"&gt;44 TEETH - High Detailed Teeth For Creatures - Blender Assets Library, IMM Zbrush&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#44ears_highdetailedearsforcreatures"&gt;44 Ears - High Detailed Ears For Creatures - VDM Blender, Zbrush + Bonus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#44noses_highdetailednosesforcreatures"&gt;44 Noses - High Detailed Noses For Creatures&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#44eyes_highdetailedeyesforcreatures_vdmzburshvdmblender"&gt;44 EYES - High Detailed Eyes For Creatures - VDM Zbursh, VDM Blender&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#strandkitthehairfuranddynamicslibrary"&gt;StrandKit | The Hair, Fur &amp; Dynamics Library&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#gumsvol1"&gt;Gums Vol 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#gumsvol2"&gt;Gums Vol 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bodytypegeneratorpro-smartanatomymarkersplusshapekeysblender4x"&gt;Body Type Generator Pro- Smart Anatomy Markers + Shape Keys | Blender 4.X&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#basemeshmegapack3dmodels_humananimeandcartoonanimals"&gt;Base Mesh Mega Pack 3D Models - Human, Anime &amp; Cartoon Animals&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vonnbots"&gt;Vonnbots&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="conceptcreatingcharacterconceptartwithblenderandgreasepencil"&gt;&lt;a id="conceptcreatingcharacterconceptartwithblenderandgreasepencil" href="https://youtu.be/ekQOGfgIDIA"&gt;CONCEPT | Creating Character Concept Art with Blender and Grease Pencil&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A CG Cookie Blender course focused on creating polished character concept art using Grease Pencil. Covers brief interpretation, color theory, thumbnailing, asset creation, and final production across four chapters. Features the character Luna, designed for use alongside the RIG course.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="basemeshcreatestylizedcharactersquicklywithblender"&gt;&lt;a id="basemeshcreatestylizedcharactersquicklywithblender" href="https://youtu.be/yFvIUPR8ay8"&gt;BASEMESH | Create Stylized Characters Quickly with Blender&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A CG Cookie course teaching character creation in Blender starting from a reliable basemesh. Covers 5+ hours of modeling clothing and accessories, texturing with vertex colors and procedurals, setting up materials, studio lighting, and geometry node hair grooming using Blender 4.2's latest tools.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="retopoflow4"&gt;&lt;a id="retopoflow4" href="https://youtu.be/ZE3gcVRR3Dk"&gt;Retopoflow 4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A comprehensive retopology toolkit for Blender featuring sketch-based tools including Contours, PolyStrips, Strokes, PolyPen, Relax, and Tweak. Version 4 is a complete rewrite with deeper Blender integration and major performance improvements. Built by the CG Cookie / Orange Turbine team.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtoretopologywiththeretopoflowadd-on"&gt;&lt;a id="introtoretopologywiththeretopoflowadd-on"&gt;Intro to Retopology with the Retopoflow Add-on&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/54b2ee8f39f6cbbabd84bf33fd6fd00c7f532f6f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a4241a6702a576acd08d5cb79037a510"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A beginner-friendly course covering the complete Retopoflow 4 retopology workflow in Blender. Teaches every major tool — PolyPen, PolyStrips, Strokes, Contours, Tweak, and Relax — finishing with a full character face retopology demonstration. Retopoflow 4 owners can access this course free with coupon code rt4course.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="realisticmaleandfemalecharactercreatorbundle_rigged280plusblendsha"&gt;&lt;a id="realisticmaleandfemalecharactercreatorbundle_rigged280plusblendsha"&gt;Realistic Male &amp; Female Character Creator Bundle - Rigged | 280+ Blendshapes | Arkit 52 | Blender Add-On&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/b4bb1146790f4cf422fe892c8fd844c439bbf1d2.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d8d8748c56e75710b290bdddfd273ac1"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Two fully rigged realistic characters for Blender, built for customization. With 280+ blendshapes across the male and female models, ARKit 52 facial support, and a built-in assistant for generating NPC variations, saving presets, and exporting to FBX or GLB, this is a serious time-saver for anyone building human characters from scratch.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="pothead_ablenderhardsurfacecharactercreationcourse"&gt;&lt;a id="pothead_ablenderhardsurfacecharactercreationcourse" href="https://youtu.be/Oi8EAnQnJCI"&gt;Pothead - A Blender Hard Surface Character Creation Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4bfae7494fe3d151b633912bb71330fd17211ac8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0615dcf3b76be9edf16be7535d00914a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A step-by-step Blender course from CG Cookie guiding you through creating a complete hard surface character. Covers subdivision surface modeling, UV unwrapping, hand-painted and procedural texturing, and final baking into a single texture set. 40 lessons and 17+ hours of content. Intermediate level.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="globalskin_ultimateskinshader"&gt;&lt;a id="globalskin_ultimateskinshader" href="https://youtu.be/nLtwpmkG_sY"&gt;GlobalSkin - Ultimate Skin Shader&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/29bd6f83efd8fa57b16f7a0d413cf1777e7c3b85.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e6edf581d7fdf6c13a2cf5a1fa007d52"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A production-ready skin shader for Blender with advanced subsurface scattering, micro detail controls, and deep customization options. Designed to deliver highly realistic human skin for characters in both Cycles and Eevee. Full details available via interactive product page.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="figaro_fastbasemeshes"&gt;&lt;a id="figaro_fastbasemeshes" href="https://youtu.be/CWLbuGGiDL8"&gt;Figaro - Fast Base Meshes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4d37e5eca14a8fc1defa62bdc4e084cd042e5689.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=81f91e8794c801662527b8e30afbabca"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A Blender add-on for quickly building character and creature base meshes using a stick-figure-style volume system. Features one-click voxelization, a template manager, split-and-pull vertex tools, modifier stack integration, and customizable display options. Compatible with Blender 4.5+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ultra-realisticgum_8kpbrgame-readyfullyriggedblender"&gt;&lt;a id="ultra-realisticgum_8kpbrgame-readyfullyriggedblender"&gt;Ultra-Realistic Gum - 8K PBR | Game-Ready | Fully Rigged | Blender&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4b4c637ac2f85d24fb9f307914015eb988474220.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e25d6370cd7f5e64ef777c61a728a0a0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A production-ready human gum and teeth asset for Blender with 8K/4K PBR textures, full IK/FK rig, shape keys, and a material-based control system for color and surface variation. Works in Cycles and Eevee, exports to Maya, Unreal, and Unity. Includes a Marmoset Toolbag 5 scene.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="customisablemaleplusfemalebasemeshbundle_blender50plus"&gt;&lt;a id="customisablemaleplusfemalebasemeshbundle_blender50plus" href="https://youtu.be/UAvroyOuLfw"&gt;Customisable Male + Female Basemesh Bundle - Blender 5.0+&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A dual-character Blender bundle featuring fully rigged male and female basemeshes with 80+ body and face customization sliders. Includes a custom addon for real-time adjustments to proportions, skin, eyes, clothing, and overlays. Pre-UV-unwrapped with clean topology. Built for Blender 5.0+.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt30"&gt;Pay $30 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="basemeshescharacterstarterkitplusrig"&gt;&lt;a id="basemeshescharacterstarterkitplusrig" href="https://youtu.be/jzOOAszwOEc"&gt;Base Meshes Character Starter Kit + Rig&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;23 pre-rigged character base meshes for Blender, built with clean topology and solid proportions so you can jump straight into modeling characters, custom assets, or original creations. No wrestling with rigging from scratch. Just a solid foundation, ready to sculpt, skin, and export.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="blazepuppeteer"&gt;&lt;a id="blazepuppeteer" href="https://youtu.be/qmQSIPoIXLo"&gt;Blaze Puppeteer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A motion generation addon that works directly on your existing rig, no retargeting or template character required. After a one-time setup, it learns your controller layout and generates inbetweens using anchors, waypoints, and path guides to steer the result. Generation runs locally on your machine, with optional cloud features available. A genuinely different approach to animation that keeps you in control of the output.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="faceit_facialexpressionsandperformancecapture"&gt;&lt;a id="faceit_facialexpressionsandperformancecapture" href="https://youtu.be/f_dQh6-ZZbY"&gt;Faceit : Facial Expressions and Performance Capture&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;An all-in-one facial rigging, motion capture, and animation add-on for Blender. Guides you through semi-automatic, non-destructive creation of facial shape keys for any character type. Includes auto-generated expressions, ARKit and Audio2Face mocap importers, real-time animation recording, a flexible control rig, shape key retargeting, and full compatibility with Rigify body rigs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="charactergenerator_access2billioncombinationsof3dcharacters"&gt;&lt;a id="charactergenerator_access2billioncombinationsof3dcharacters" href="https://youtu.be/-zbynYK7CCA"&gt;Character generator - Access 2 billion combinations of 3D characters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A massive 3D character library offering 2 billion+ combinations of fully rigged male and female characters. Includes hair, clothing, outfits, accessories, facial expressions, lip sync, and ARKit blendshapes. Comes with a Blender generator tool, 67 poses, and 19,000+ pre-rendered PNGs available on request.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="44teeth_highdetailedteethforcreatures_blenderassetslibraryimmzbrus"&gt;&lt;a id="44teeth_highdetailedteethforcreatures_blenderassetslibraryimmzbrus"&gt;44 TEETH - High Detailed Teeth For Creatures - Blender Assets Library, IMM Zbrush&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/fd9d24a47ce9ef41134a5d64d273ec4451389dd2.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=381f089db605a245fcd7b5874f5803f0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A high-detail creature teeth asset pack including 44 sculpted tooth variations in OBJ, FBX, and ZBrush formats. Comes with an IMM brush for ZBrush and an asset library file for seamless use in Blender. Un-textured high-poly sculpts, decimated for performance without sacrificing detail. Roots are fully modeled.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="44ears_highdetailedearsforcreatures"&gt;&lt;a id="44ears_highdetailedearsforcreatures"&gt;44 Ears - High Detailed Ears For Creatures - VDM Blender, Zbrush + Bonus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8d5aac4813ddee826813dffb142d015892a06357.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5c37bb829f00f0e9b86e3f42940f1423"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A creature ear sculpt pack with 44 VDM brushes for Blender and ZBrush, plus OBJ/FBX exports and vector displacement maps. Covers nearly every ear type including sci-fi variations. Compatible with Blender's Asset Library (4.3+) and VDM brush workflow (4.2 and lower). Includes bonus assets and a ZBrush ZTL file.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="44noses_highdetailednosesforcreatures"&gt;&lt;a id="44noses_highdetailednosesforcreatures" href="https://youtu.be/R1Jt13MLHU4"&gt;44 Noses - High Detailed Noses For Creatures&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/868ab0cdcf20bd07d1e0431ae1548270090ce87d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=cdb1e5f5a9fc0f3226882cf14ff7eba6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A high-detail creature nose pack featuring 44 VDM brushes for Blender and ZBrush, with OBJ/FBX files and vector displacement maps. Covers a wide range of nose types sculpted with care from extensive reference research. Supports both Blender 4.3+ Asset Library and older VDM brush workflows.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="44eyes_highdetailedeyesforcreatures_vdmzburshvdmblender"&gt;&lt;a id="44eyes_highdetailedeyesforcreatures_vdmzburshvdmblender"&gt;44 EYES - High Detailed Eyes For Creatures - VDM Zbursh, VDM Blender&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e29341041609910333bf016b451f6d91f53f6b12.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9a20861922c85c62c62cc5267d8f7df9"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A creature eye sculpt pack with 44 VDM brushes for Blender and ZBrush, including OBJ/FBX files and 1025x1025 vector displacement maps. Covers diverse eye types including sci-fi designs. Supports Blender 4.3+ Asset Library method and legacy VDM brush append workflow for older versions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="strandkitthehairfuranddynamicslibrary"&gt;&lt;a id="strandkitthehairfuranddynamicslibrary" href="https://youtu.be/RntD3sAo_00"&gt;StrandKit | The Hair, Fur &amp; Dynamics Library&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A modular Blender asset library for hair and fur featuring 24 hair type systems (1A–4C), 15 fur types, 14 hair card generators, 1,000+ hair cards, edge hair tools, and a physics simulation system. Fully procedural GN-based, works in Cycles and Eevee, and supports game engine export pipelines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="gumsvol1"&gt;&lt;a id="gumsvol1"&gt;Gums Vol 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/fb820e69576c2684f6bf1d72650ce35b292937f1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c4fcb97caa973c329913aad579e05340"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;11 unique gum shapes and 7 tongue models built on shared topology, so they morph between each other non-destructively using layers. Clean UVs, low and high poly ready for baking, included in formats for ZBrush and Blender. A workhorse asset that earns its place in any creature workflow.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="gumsvol2"&gt;&lt;a id="gumsvol2"&gt;Gums Vol 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/673247bfb7b9497a4234890fb9971be550b060e5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=937fdce6cfff6f3bed0294b0609e5a26"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The second volume in the Creature Gums series brings another 11 gum shapes and 7 tongue models with the same shared-topology morphing system, leaning into horror, fantasy, and darker creature design. Same professional-grade topology, UV setup, ZBrush and Blender support. Pick up both volumes and you'll rarely need to build mouth anatomy from scratch again.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="bodytypegeneratorpro-smartanatomymarkersplusshapekeysblender4x"&gt;&lt;a id="bodytypegeneratorpro-smartanatomymarkersplusshapekeysblender4x"&gt;Body Type Generator Pro- Smart Anatomy Markers + Shape Keys | Blender 4.X&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/20177f49b84b37c2224f4df3717be4d847ae658e.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0fb6b6eb9cca304869bc8ddfe2163e15"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Generate humanoid body variations from a single basemesh. Place anatomy markers, choose from 13 presets or dial in 29 sliders, and every result saves as a named Shape Key — original mesh untouched, export-ready whenever you are.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="basemeshmegapack3dmodels_humananimeandcartoonanimals"&gt;&lt;a id="basemeshmegapack3dmodels_humananimeandcartoonanimals"&gt;Base Mesh Mega Pack 3D Models - Human, Anime &amp; Cartoon Animals&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/971e0b6651ae43bcc6bf9303c4bae474738ed39f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=69f14cf41fc30a2a0e700810972bd0b6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;155 base mesh 3D models spanning realistic humans, stylized characters, anime, cartoon animals, and high-poly anatomy sculpts. With 98 rigged models, 42 animated, and file formats covering FBX, OBJ, GLB, BLEND, and more, there's something here for nearly every project and pipeline. A deep library to pull from whenever you need a solid starting point.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vonnbots"&gt;&lt;a id="vonnbots"&gt;Vonnbots&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/85d551df54c5e91eabe0dcff932655a67c7cbfe0.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2487bd9282b18ef55b0b7ef2f4cdcfbd"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A pack of three fully rigged robotic characters from the team at CG Cookie. Each VonnBot comes with stretchy/bendy limbs, a stretchy torso, IK/FK arms and legs, IK parent switching, limited facial controls, and a custom rig UI built right into the properties panel. Professionally modeled, shaded, and rigged — ready to animate straight out of the box.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
