al Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#middleeasterntownunrealengine"&gt;Middle Eastern Town ( Unreal Engine )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#hangar-xunrealengine"&gt;HANGAR-X ( Unreal Engine )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#industrialwarehousenightenvironment_garageunrealengine"&gt;Industrial Warehouse Night Environment - GARAGE ( Unreal Engine )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#containercityunrealengine"&gt;Container City ( Unreal Engine )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#mastermegadirtywallpackmaterial4kunrealengine"&gt;Master Mega Dirty Wall Pack Material 4K ( Unreal Engine )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#fabricbundlematerialunrealengine"&gt;Fabric Bundle Material ( Unreal Engine )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#glassbundlematerialunrealengine"&gt;Glass Bundle Material ( Unreal Engine )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#fireworks_vol1_niagaraunrealengine"&gt;Fireworks Vol. 1 - Niagara (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#toonabilities_vol1_niagaraunrealengine"&gt;Toon Abilities Vol.1 - Niagara (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#lootdrops_vol2_niagaraunrealengine"&gt;Loot Drops Vol.2 - Niagara (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#magicabilities_vol3niagaraunrealengine"&gt;Magic Abilities Vol. 3 Niagara (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#niagaramegapack_vol3unrealengine"&gt;Niagara Mega Pack Vol. 3 (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#uniquemarkersandpings_vol1unity"&gt;Unique Markers &amp; Pings Vol. 1 (Unity)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#uniqueprojectiles_vol4unity"&gt;Unique Projectiles Vol. 4 (Unity)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#uniquelootdrops_vol1unity"&gt;Unique Loot Drops Vol. 1 (Unity)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#steampunkzeppelinstation-victorianairshipterminalmodularenvironmentunrealengine"&gt;Steampunk Zeppelin Station - Victorian Airship Terminal Modular Environment ( Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="japaneseoldshoppingmallinteriorenvironmentunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="japaneseoldshoppingmallinteriorenvironmentunrealengine"&gt;Japanese Old Shopping Mall Interior Environment ( Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7fd5197bf5c013dbbf72c02d4b79417a783c3928.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=321819c8a79fbbeed97d43d0c2e56ffb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Fab Marketplace! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Step into a world of haunting nostalgia with the Japanese Old Shopping Mall environment pack. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This game-ready collection is specifically designed for developers looking to create high-quality&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; post-apocalyptic, survival horror, or urban exploration (Urbex) scenes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you are building a haunted Japanese mall or a derelict commercial district, this pack provides &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;the perfect balance of cinematic realism and technical optimization.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Complete Modular Architecture: Build complex levels in minutes using our modular wall, floor, &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;and ceiling modules. Designed with perfect snapping for a seamless workflow.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 86 Unique High-Detail Meshes: A massive library of AAA-quality props, including weathered store shelves, &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;shattered glass, decayed signage, and traditional Japanese retail elements.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-  Abandoned &amp;amp; Post-Apocalyptic Aesthetic: Expertly crafted materials featuring realistic decay, grime, &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;and dust, perfect for next-gen horror games.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Fast Level Design: Every asset is optimized for fast scene assembly, allowing you to go from a blank &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;map to a cinematic environment instantly.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Professional Optimization: High-fidelity PBR textures and efficient geometry ensure smooth &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;performance in Unreal Engine 5.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cyberpunkbathroom_brutalistunity"&gt;&lt;a id="cyberpunkbathroom_brutalistunity" href="https://youtu.be/RyzgUyZpkoI"&gt;Cyberpunk Bathroom - Brutalist ( Unity )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Unity Asset Store!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Cyberpunk Bathroom Pack by Entroverse Labs delivers a powerful fusion of cyberpunk futurism &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;and brutalist architecture—a perfect balance of high-tech energy and industrial grit. Designed for Unity HDRP, &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;URP, and Built-in Render Pipelines, this pack is fully optimized, modular, and ready to bring cinematic &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;atmosphere to your next game, film, or interactive project.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features :&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Modular Cyberpunk Bathroom Kit&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build complete environments with modular walls, floors, ceilings, and detailed props—perfect for both clean &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;futuristic spaces and worn-down city bathrooms.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- HDRP + URP + Built-in Support&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each material setup is optimized for all three render pipelines, ensuring visual fidelity and flexibility for any &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;type of Unity project.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- High-Resolution Textures &amp;amp; Realistic Materials&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Physically based materials with emissive, roughness, and normal detail bring out the tactile realism of every&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; surface—from reflective mirrors to weathered concrete.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Brutalist–Cyberpunk Fusion Aesthetic&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A signature Entroverse style combining monolithic brutalist geometry with advanced neon lighting and futuristic&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; tech design.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Optimized for Real-Time Performance&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Created for smooth gameplay and efficient rendering, ideal for real-time experiences and cinematic sequences alike.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Customizable Lighting &amp;amp; Materials&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Adjust emissive intensities, change color palettes, or swap fixtures to create unique moods and lighting scenarios.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt20"&gt;Pay $20 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="motelroominteriorenvironmentunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="motelroominteriorenvironmentunrealengine"&gt;Motel Room Interior Environment ( Unreal Engine )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4582924c3d6e75b01a0ff01d2b2114faafbe2033.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=882e6eccd6b8beb9c50ef833bd4789af"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Fab Marketplace! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Step into the nostalgic atmosphere of a classic roadside motel room with this carefully crafted Unreal Engine &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Environment Pack. Warm wood panels, patterned wallpaper, vintage furniture and subtle lighting come together&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; to form a grounded cinematic space that instantly tells a story. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This pack includes 68 unique meshes covering furniture, décor and clutter props, making it ideal for narrative &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;projects, thriller or horror scenes, mystery games and stylized realism.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All assets are fully optimized and game-ready, featuring clean topology, efficient UVs, proper collisions and &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;high-quality materials for believable lighting. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 68 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Modular interior furnishing assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Game-ready and optimized&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- High-quality materials &amp;amp; real-time lighting support&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Fits cinematics, games, trailers and visualization projects&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="retrosci-firesearchcabinenvironmentunity"&gt;&lt;a id="retrosci-firesearchcabinenvironmentunity" href="https://youtu.be/97VTtf7QKJw"&gt;Retro Sci-Fi Research Cabin Environment ( Unity )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Unity Asset Store!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Retro Sci-Fi Research Cabin blends nostalgic design with futuristic functionality, bringing a complete retro-&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;futuristic laboratory and living space to your projects. Featuring 84 unique meshes and an optimized showcase&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; level, this modular environment is designed for building immersive sci-fi interiors filled with research equipment &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;and retro tech details.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The pack includes vintage-style computers, printers, oscillographs, holographic projectors, robotic arms, control&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; panels, and many other prosps that capture the spirit of classic sci-fi engineering. Complemented by modular&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; walls, floors, and furniture pieces, you can easily create anything from a compact research pod to a large-scale&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; base interior.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Demo Map, Overview Map&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 84 Optimized Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Modular Environment&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Detailed Retro Research Equipment&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Customizable Emissive Lamps &amp;amp; Screens&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Channel-packed Metallic/Roughness/AO&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="dungeonruinsunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="dungeonruinsunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/wrBXyKSyH2E"&gt;Dungeon Ruins (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Fab Marketplace! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build ancient underground halls and stone temple remains with the Dungeon Ruins environment pack. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This package features clean modular pieces to design large columns, broken arches, and ruined shrines &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;covered in ivy. It includes a ready-to-use demo map with cinematic lighting. With 167 unique meshes, &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;this package helps game developers build highly detailed and optimized historical locations easily.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Simple modular pieces to build custom ancient temples and ruined stone halls&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Ready-made demo map with highly atmospheric cinematic lighting setup&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Contains 167 unique meshes to decorate outdoor ruins and rocky canyon pathways&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- High-quality textures for realistic weathered stone surfaces, dirt, and moss&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Fully optimized assets with up to 7 levels of LODs for smooth performance&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Includes a specialized pivot wind system blueprint for realistic foliage movement&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Includes 7 master materials and 108 detailed material instances for easy editing&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Automatically generated collisions for quick and safe asset placement&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="megamarblematerial4kunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="megamarblematerial4kunrealengine"&gt;Mega Marble Material 4K ( Unreal Engine )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/de3d229717257ec44e43b86c614b11b58fea3672.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ee787db006896fec84b1e42c3c445ccf"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Fab Marketplace! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features : &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- All materials were carefully created&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Superficially edited and overlay maps created.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Stage optimization is healthy.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Please contact us for contact and information.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- All painting is done with Substance Painter and Designer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="magicprojectiles_vol3_niagaraunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="magicprojectiles_vol3_niagaraunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/uVktk8H60OE"&gt;Magic Projectiles Vol.3 - Niagara (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Fab Marketplace! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;60 Projectiles made with Niagara. This includes Orbs, Spells, Fireballs, Arrows, Magic Spells and more. They &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;are great for all platforms, and for a variety of genres and art styles. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Part of the Magic Projectiles - Mega Pack - Vol.1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;They are easy to scale, change color, and can be used in with several characters.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please contact me if you have any doubts or suggestions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;NOTE: You might need to enable Niagara and Niagara Extras in Edit &amp;gt; Plugins &amp;gt; FX.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vfxgraph_stylizedsmoke_vol1unity"&gt;&lt;a id="vfxgraph_stylizedsmoke_vol1unity" href="https://youtu.be/dPJQuD93-Ks"&gt;VFX Graph - Stylized Smoke - Vol. 1(Unity)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Unity Asset Store!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;33 Stylized Smoke Effects done entirely with Visual Effect Graph&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This package includes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-8 Looping Smokes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-8 Smoke Impacts / Explosions&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-5 Looping Fires&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-12 Smoke Explosions&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Highly Customizable (change direction, radius, rate, force, color, size, etc. in the inspector)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Shaders (2 smoke erosion)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-HDRP and URP only&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Limited Mobile support (high-end mobile devices only)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Documentation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Originally made in URP, adapted to HDRP.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Visual Effect Graph from the Package Manager is required.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="stylizedvfx_water"&gt;&lt;a id="stylizedvfx_water" href="https://youtu.be/LMCV5f9B86k"&gt;Stylized VFX - Water ( Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Fab Marketplace! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;25 Unique Stylized / Cartoon style Water VFX for your games and animations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt30"&gt;Pay $30 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="cappadociaanatoliancavehotelenvironmentunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="cappadociaanatoliancavehotelenvironmentunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/67OYTCj29Hg"&gt;Cappadocia Anatolian Cave Hotel Environment ( Unreal Engine )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Fab Marketplace! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Step into the ancient world with the Cappadocia Anatolian Cave Hotel Environment by Befour Studios.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Inspired by the real-world historical marvels of Anatolia, this highly modular 3D asset pack allows you &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;to build authentic boutique cave hotels, ancient underground cities, and breathtaking ethnic settlements. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;From towering fairy chimneys and soft volcanic rock formations to fully furnished traditional hotel rooms, &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;this pack provides everything you need to create an atmospheric historic village for your games, cinematics, &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;and VR projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features : &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Authentic Anatolian Atmosphere: Perfect for historic games, middle-eastern environments, &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;ancient rock cities, and realistic VR tourism experiences.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 455 Unique High-Quality Meshes: A massive, optimized collection of volcanic rocks, ethnic props, &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;traditional furniture, and modular cave-carved architecture.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Ready-to-Use Interiors &amp;amp; Exteriors: Includes fully dressed hotel rooms, a spa, restaurant, outdoor &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;courtyards, and terraces overlooking the rock formations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Advanced Blueprint Tools: Generate fences, stairs, and background settlements effortlessly to &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;speed up your level design workflow.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Hot Air Balloon Blueprint: Add the signature Cappadocian hot air balloons drifting across your &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;