s.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="magicabilities_vol3niagaraunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="magicabilities_vol3niagaraunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/yLIfmI3ciHM"&gt;Magic Abilities Vol. 3 Niagara (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Fab Marketplace! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;25 Stylized Slashes with customizable scale and colors. Done entirely with Niagara.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="niagaramegapack_vol3unrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="niagaramegapack_vol3unrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/AuDsKV5kW7g"&gt;Niagara Mega Pack Vol. 3 (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Fab Marketplace! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;150+ Niagara Effects such as AoE Vertical Beams, Sword Slashes, Hits and Impacts Vol.2, Muzzle Flashes &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vol.2 and Earthbender done entirely with Niagara and specifically made to be customizable by you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;VERTICAL BEAMS SHOWCASE&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;SWORD SLASHES SHOWCASE&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;HITS AND IMPACTS V2 SHOWCASE&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;MUZZLES FLASHES V2 SHOWCASE&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;EARTHBENDER SHOWCASE&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="uniquemarkersandpings_vol1unity"&gt;&lt;a id="uniquemarkersandpings_vol1unity" href="https://youtu.be/WYFHvPCh_hk"&gt;Unique Markers &amp; Pings Vol. 1 (Unity)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Unity Asset Store!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;21 Unique Area Markers + 11 Unique Pings + 10 Unique HUD Markers&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Part of the Unique VFX Ultra Pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This package contains:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 9 Click Movement;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 10 HUD Icon Markers;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 6 Square Area Markers;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 15 Round Area Markers;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 7 Instant Ground Markers;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 8 Attack Pings (4 linger and 4 instant);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 4 Danger Pings (2 linger and 2 instant);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 8 Help Pings (4 linger and 4 instant);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 8 Question Pings (4 linger and 4 instant);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 8 Direction Pings (4 linger and 4 instant);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 4 Warning Pings (2 linger and 2 instant);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 8 Waypoint Pings (4 linger and 4 instant);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 4 3D Waypoint Pings (loop);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Demo Scene;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Textures &amp;amp; Shaders;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Particle System Controller Script (control color);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- HDRP, URP and BIRP supported&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="uniqueprojectiles_vol4unity"&gt;&lt;a id="uniqueprojectiles_vol4unity" href="https://youtu.be/-xKba_ti6Ew"&gt;Unique Projectiles Vol. 4 (Unity)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Unity Asset Store!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;50 Projectiles including Arrows, Axes, Bullets, Shuriken, Hot Iron Bar, Shards and much more. A fantastic &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;pack for PC and Mobile, and for a variety of genres and art styles.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This package contains:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 50 Projectiles (17 Unique);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 50 Hits/Impacts (17 Unique);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 50 Muzzles (20 Unique);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 3D Shooting Demo;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 2D Shooting Demo;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Textures (Noise, Gradients, Flares, Circles, Galaxies, Impacts, Trails, etc)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Shaders (Distortion, Dissolve, Glow, Fresnel, Heat Distort and Galaxy)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- HDRP, URP and BIRP (built-in);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Combine Projectiles with different Hits/Impacts or with different Muzzles, it's up to your imagination!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="uniquelootdrops_vol1unity"&gt;&lt;a id="uniquelootdrops_vol1unity" href="https://youtu.be/QpCozTTkNr8"&gt;Unique Loot Drops Vol. 1 (Unity)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Unity Asset Store!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;10 Unique Loot Drops with 6 levels of rarity each.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This package contains:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 18 Circular Loot Drops;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 6 Cylinder Loot Drops;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 6 Rift Loot Drops;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 30 Vertical Loot Drops;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Demo Scene;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Textures &amp;amp; Shaders;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Particle System Controller Script (control color);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- HDRP, URP and BIRP supported;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All the effects are fully optimized and work on any platform.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="steampunkzeppelinstation-victorianairshipterminalmodularenvironmentunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="steampunkzeppelinstation-victorianairshipterminalmodularenvironmentunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/kga0k8ieVH8"&gt;Steampunk Zeppelin Station - Victorian Airship Terminal Modular Environment ( Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Professional License redeeming from Fab Marketplace!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Step into a grand, awe-inspiring era of aerial transit with this highly detailed Steampunk Zeppelin Station Victorian Airship Terminal environment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This pack is a seamless fusion of ornate Victorian brass, weathered wood, and powerful, steam-driven machinery. Perfect for creating alternate history narratives, fantasy-adventure games, or immersive cinematic experiences.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Highlights Include:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Modular Station Architecture: Intricately detailed arched copper and weathered wood structural elements, detailed wall panels, multi-level platforms, boarding walkways, and grand terminal interior walls, allowing for flexible custom layouts.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Detailed Steampunk Automatons: Features high-detail, steam-powered humanoid robots with glowing optical sensors, serving as ticket clerks and cargo handlers, bringing life to the terminal.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Baggage &amp;amp; Cargo System: A range of specific props, including a unique, detailed baggage cart (a custom-designed metal and wood wheeled vehicle) and multiple vintage leather trunks and suitcases of various shapes and sizes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Departure/Arrival Board &amp;amp; Ticket Booth: A massive, elaborate, and functional-looking departure board with hand-rendered text and mechanical clockwork details, situated above a richly decorated wooden ticket booth.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Industrial and Steampunk Machinery: A complex network of exposed gears (including massive, moving floor gears), pressure gauges, intricate copper and steel piping, heavy valves, and iron railings.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Docking Infrastructure: Elements of massive zeppelin structures (partial views of the gas envelopes) alongside mooring masts, cranes, and heavy-duty docking platforms with mechanical interfaces.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Atmospheric FX and Textures: Volumetric god rays from distant windows, rich volumetric steam/smoke effects, glowing gaslight textures, soot and oil stain decals, vintage travel posters, and worn surface textures (wood, copper, leather).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Optimized for Performance: Pre-configured for high-quality real-time rendering in Unreal Engine 5 with Nanite and Lumen, maintaining excellent visual fidelity at high frame rates (70+ FPS target on mid-to-high-end hardware).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
