      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5141ef66e67805bf597fcf37a0aeb673adc26fbf.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=4806ff6cec3342425393524736067204"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/672d7a8aecfc259334e213185293b946e6399768.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=3040eeb4b91c3c21d3ab31ab9bee7e3e"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Simplify your development with Synty&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Game developers, rejoice! The pros at Synty Studios are here to help you take your project from baseline to beta with our latest Software Bundle. Build your worlds with professional-quality assets like photorealistic particle effects, prepare for lifelike duels with a fantasy rival pack, and more. Add complex interfaces or simple dungeons—anything you need to help bring your dream game to life. You’ll even get a $10 voucher for the Synty Studios store to keep creating. Pay what you want for AAA-quality assets and help support Code.org with your purchase. &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ef9741;"&gt;Keys expire. All titles should be redeemed before June 31st, 2027.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $30 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#polygon_prototypepack"&gt;POLYGON - Prototype Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#polygon_particlefxpack"&gt;POLYGON - Particle FX Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#polygon_dungeonpack"&gt;POLYGON - Dungeon Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#animation_swordcombat"&gt;ANIMATION - Sword Combat&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#interface_fantasywarriorhud"&gt;INTERFACE - Fantasy Warrior HUD&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#polygon_fantasydungeonmap"&gt;POLYGON - Fantasy Dungeon Map&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#polygon_meadowforest_naturebiome"&gt;POLYGON - Meadow Forest - Nature Biome&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#polygon_fantasyrivalspack"&gt;POLYGON - Fantasy Rivals Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sidekickpack_fantasyknights"&gt;Sidekick Pack - Fantasy Knights&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#10voucher"&gt;$10 Voucher&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $30 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="polygon_prototypepack"&gt;&lt;a id="polygon_prototypepack" href="https://youtu.be/KAiun66iyBA"&gt;POLYGON - Prototype Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Synty® Studios presents: POLYGON - Prototype Pack&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Including characters, buildings, props, and environments, the POLYGON - Prototype Pack provides all the essentials you need to kickstart your game projects. Whether you're crafting a platformer, a shooter, an RPG, or something entirely unique, the modular nature of these assets allows for endless combinations and possibilities. Whether you're a seasoned developer or a newcomer to game design, this pack will help you to prototype and iterate on your game ideas with ease. Includes diagnostic assets for teams to communicate design decisions using notes, markers and more. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- For Unity and Unreal Engine&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 400+ unique assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 10 alternative texture colours&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Synty Polygon and Simple versions of building assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Demo scene included&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Contents may vary between engines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="polygon_particlefxpack"&gt;&lt;a id="polygon_particlefxpack" href="https://youtu.be/Y3az8jkS0FU"&gt;POLYGON - Particle FX Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Synty® Studios presents: POLYGON - Particle FX Pack&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A particle FX asset pack including fire, water, smoke, dust, dirt, blood, nature, weapons, magic and more, to add to your POLYGON or low-poly style project.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Watch Unity and Unreal Engine showcases of the FX included in this pack on YouTube. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- For Unity and Unreal Engine&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 120+ particle FX&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- FX designed to complement the POLYGON asset series&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Lightweight particles to keep performance running smoothly&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Contents may vary between engines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="polygon_dungeonpack"&gt;&lt;a id="polygon_dungeonpack" href="https://youtu.be/ACBH9wTBQbU"&gt;POLYGON - Dungeon Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e8733691b19c5790b0a08b398f436d740d87501d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0ff9c2504d2ea1363be16b6d1e193c78"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Synty® Studios Presents: POLYGON - Dungeon Pack&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A low poly asset pack of characters, props, weapons and environment assets to create a Fantasy themed polygonal style game.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Modular sections are easy to piece together in a variety of combinations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Includes a big demo scene (Character poses indicative only)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-770 unique assets with x4 alternative texture colours.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Modular Interior castle set&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Modular Interior cave set&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Modular Goblin Camp set&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Modular Basement set&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Modular Sewer set&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Multiple Dungeon entrances&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Alternate materials for dust, moss, snow, and lava&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Contents may vary between engines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="animation_swordcombat"&gt;&lt;a id="animation_swordcombat" href="https://youtu.be/5YKHq8vAQ50"&gt;ANIMATION - Sword Combat&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Synty® Studios presents: ANIMATION - Sword Combat&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This pack is brimming with essential animations for sword combat – including light and heavy attacks, fabulous flourishes, dramatic deaths, lively leaps and more. Each with multiple animations and smooth transitions so your characters will move with ease. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 100+ Animation clips as separate files allow you to to only import the animations you need into your project&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Demo scene to test the animations&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Gallery scene with all the animations laid out&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="interface_fantasywarriorhud"&gt;&lt;a id="interface_fantasywarriorhud" href="https://youtu.be/a03NRuznQGI"&gt;INTERFACE - Fantasy Warrior HUD&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Synty® Studios Presents: INTERFACE - Fantasy Warrior HUD&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Quickly build out your game HUD with dozens of pre-built HUD elements! Action bars, minimaps, compasses, weapon wheels, HP bars, damage FX, crosshairs - we’ve added everything we could think of to help you quickly assemble a quality-looking, responsive HUD. Each component can be visually customized to suit your game’s needs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- For Unity and Unreal Engine&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 1,100+ sprites and icons assembled into over 150 prefabs (with animations!)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Comprehensive range of input icons for controller types including PC, Xbox, PS, Switch and Steam.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Text and numeric buttons can be tinted, localised and customised&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;*The UI elements contained in this pack are 2D and intended to work with 2D systems. No 3D models are included.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Contents may vary between engines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="polygon_fantasydungeonmap"&gt;&lt;a id="polygon_fantasydungeonmap"&gt;POLYGON - Fantasy Dungeon Map&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0ce087286b1963ae806735d473d1d4dc9b2b4d4c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ce03f03d5a0bb1a4bd1f752f806e8670"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Synty® Studios presents: POLYGON - Fantasy Dungeon Map&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This map pack is an expansion add-on for POLYGON Dungeon Pack, featuring a new demo scene and a few new assets designed for the new areas. Synty map packs are designed to help inspire you with level design, and save you time with pre-dressed areas ready to place into your project!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In this Dungeons Map pack you will find a grand library, an ominous crypt, a hallowed shrine, a royal hallway, a dizzying vertical labyrinth and more. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-57 prefabs / blueprints &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-New dungeon areas, rooms and demo scene &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Contents may vary between engines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="polygon_meadowforest_naturebiome"&gt;&lt;a id="polygon_meadowforest_naturebiome" href="https://youtu.be/PbUTzpZfEV0"&gt;POLYGON - Meadow Forest - Nature Biome&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Synty® Studios presents: POLYGON - Meadow Forest - Nature Biome&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Come and fly away to the magical meadow forest and immerse yourself in this idyllic landscape surrounded by natural beauty. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;POLYGON - Meadow Forest holds the essence of serenity. From layered hills with grassy fields to a wide variety of flowers, trees, and plants. Butterflies are fluttering throughout the air, and birds nesting in the trees. What better way to fly your kite and experience the sunset? &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;But, with so much bliss, what could you find when going off the beaten track? Are there secrets lurking in the spaces between the trees? Come find out for yourself. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Contents may vary between engines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="polygon_fantasyrivalspack"&gt;&lt;a id="polygon_fantasyrivalspack"&gt;POLYGON - Fantasy Rivals Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/288f3ee3b73e776517a5440ea79896f9ed35c002.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3cae537e11f788635a00c8da79835083"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Synty® Studios Presents - POLYGON - Fantasy Rivals Pack&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A low poly asset pack of characters, weapons, prop and FX assets to create a fantasy based polygonal style game.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Includes a new big rig for massive monsters&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-20+ unique characters, from giant ogres, to enchanted golems&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-20+ weapons that match each character perfectly&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-A wide variety of additional props and FX&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Contents may vary between engines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sidekickpack_fantasyknights"&gt;&lt;a id="sidekickpack_fantasyknights"&gt;Sidekick Pack - Fantasy Knights&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3a264e03b90a84fed1f8f945ad98268d83f3c8ef.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=515ae33452cc1a5dfa0339259a974db8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Synty Studios presents: Fantasy Knights – Sidekick Modular Characters&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create and kit out a calvary of brave Fantasy Knights, utilising 100+ new parts including including broadswords, elaborate helmets, crowns, armour and more, designed to deliver just the noble knights your project needs! Unleash your creativity or utilise our expert presets. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're building a full in-game character creator, or just changing outfits on the fly, the Sidekick Runtime API makes it easy. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-100+ modular, rigged Modern Civilian parts (clothing, hair and more)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-90+ modular, rigged human base species parts (torsos, legs, hands, feet etc.)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Fully rigged to the Unity Humanoid skeleton (Mecanim compatible)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Dynamic joints allow you to add realistic motion to capes, hair, beards etc.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Facial blend shapes for expressions and lipsync (works with ARKit)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Body blend shapes to adjust body type and proportions&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Designed to cohesively match Synty POLYGON environments&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-Designed to work seamlessly with Synty ANIMATION packs&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sidekick Character Creator Tool (Editor Extension) Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Customise material colours directly in the editor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Expert presets to enable rapid character creation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Bake completed characters into a single optimised prefab, combining all skinned mesh renderers into one for performance friendly deployment&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Runtime API for in-game character customisation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;*Contents may vary between engines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="10voucher"&gt;&lt;a id="10voucher"&gt;$10 Voucher&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4fe270c6b4127d2882b2d7b609200b22fbe14806.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f1e82b9fd36f58eeb0e8c8ea099e0133"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;US$10 voucher to use on the Synty Store checkout.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
