ener"&gt;296 Melancholic LoFi Samples "Fading LoFi"&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Fading LoFi is a royalty-free lo-fi production toolkit built around three complete song ideas, melodic loops, drum loops, one-shots and FX. It also includes 100+ original foley recordings, shakers and organic textures, giving producers a warm, melancholic palette for chilled lo-fi hip hop, beats and atmospheric productions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="darktrapdrumkit"&gt;&lt;a id="darktrapdrumkit"&gt;Dark Trap Drum Kit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6664687b1ef1ee0d4e733e0685fc419709a818c1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d24097278673af10e63fee92e966d169"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="100%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/soundcloud%253Atracks%253A1245874456&amp;amp;color=%2376d7ce&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comments=true&amp;amp;show_user=true&amp;amp;show_reposts=false&amp;amp;show_teaser=true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; line-break: anywhere; word-break: normal; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering" title="BVKER.COM" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;BVKER.COM&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering/dark-trap-sample-pack" title="Dark Trap Sample Pack Inspired by Suicideboys, Ghostmane etc." target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;Dark Trap Sample Pack Inspired by Suicideboys, Ghostmane etc.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;Dark Trap Drum Kit focuses on the gloomy side of hip hop and trap, with sounds inspired by darker underground rap aesthetics. The pack combines unique drum one-shots, punchy hits, pads, keys and FX designed to cut through a mix while keeping a gritty, moody character for dark beats and modern trap productions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="lofihiphopfantasy"&gt;&lt;a id="lofihiphopfantasy"&gt;Lofi Hip Hop Fantasy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6959a48cd4f5f83ef30fe881bbb2d4fb7734c6ef.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=269f1d605ae3480dc83d2ae19f6521ab"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="100%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/soundcloud%253Atracks%253A861924724&amp;amp;color=%2376d7ce&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comments=true&amp;amp;show_user=true&amp;amp;show_reposts=false&amp;amp;show_teaser=true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; line-break: anywhere; word-break: normal; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/w-a-production" title="W. A. Production®" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;W. A. Production®&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/w-a-production/lofi-hip-hop-fantasy" title="Lofi Hip Hop Fantasy | 380 Lofi Sounds, Presets &amp;amp; Melodies" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;Lofi Hip Hop Fantasy | 380 Lofi Sounds, Presets &amp;amp; Melodies&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;Kick back. Study. Relax. Soothe your soul with What About: LoFi Hip Hop Fantasy from W. A. Production. This pack is loaded with loops, one-shots, MIDI sequences, and presets. Choose from melodic chords, sensual bass lines, entrancing hi-hat, and percussion patterns.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="melodictrapspecies"&gt;&lt;a id="melodictrapspecies" href="https://youtu.be/JFGLJp_aaZE"&gt;Melodic Trap Species&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2cef62299cce6373582801907200c1b9f74a93e8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4f2ab178b787783ef53bf9d5409b8a64"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Melodic Trap Species is a royalty-free trap production toolkit built for modern beats, heavy 808s and energetic arrangements. It brings together drums, bass elements, loops, one-shots, FX and musical inspiration so producers can move quickly from beat idea to finished track.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="lofiillusion"&gt;&lt;a id="lofiillusion"&gt;Lofi Illusion&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8991f947accd4dbdeb1555e94c2e7d31cbb6d59c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=03de1169530a5726866a436f53accab8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="100%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/soundcloud%253Atracks%253A782401759&amp;amp;color=%2376d7ce&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comments=true&amp;amp;show_user=true&amp;amp;show_reposts=false&amp;amp;show_teaser=true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; line-break: anywhere; word-break: normal; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/w-a-production" title="W. A. Production®" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;W. A. Production®&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/w-a-production/lofi-illusion" title="Lofi Melodies, Drum Shots &amp;amp; Serum Presets | Lofi Illusion Sample Pack" target="_blank" s