755762e29876809b816eb16bcf40b3ef"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="100%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/soundcloud%253Atracks%253A1739482875&amp;amp;color=%2376d7ce&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comments=true&amp;amp;show_user=true&amp;amp;show_reposts=false&amp;amp;show_teaser=true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; line-break: anywhere; word-break: normal; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/w-a-production" title="W. A. Production®" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;W. A. Production®&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/w-a-production/hip-hop-drip" title="Hip Hop Drip | Kendrick Lamar / Travis Scott Style Sounds, Presets &amp;amp; MIDI" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;Hip Hop Drip | Kendrick Lamar / Travis Scott Style Sounds, Presets &amp;amp; MIDI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;Drop a Beat: The name of the Soundpool is the game. With a total of 1,236 samples, true hip hop bangers are a sure thing. From basses and guitars to keys and strings to drum kits and vocals – this sound collection will get you in the flow!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Package contains 1236 Loops* in 90 BPM.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;180 bass loops (30 loops in 6 pitches) 42 drumkits with variations 12 FX loops (2 loops in 6 pitches) 18 FX loops (in universal pitch) 132 guitar loops (22 loops in 6 pitches) 1 guitar loop (in universal pitch) 210 keys loops (35 loops in 6 pitches) 12 pad loops (2 loops in 6 pitches) 96 strings loops (16 loops in 6 pitches) 150 synth loops (25 loops in 6 pitches) 210 synth Bass loops (35 loops in 6 pitches) 60 vocals loops (10 loops in 6 pitches) 21 vocals loops (in universal pitch)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="heavyhittinghiphop"&gt;&lt;a id="heavyhittinghiphop"&gt;Heavy Hitting Hip Hop&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7248c8eca7916f146d75d1c4b02ac915bbc4d476.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2f11227fa1933c77ea49bed05fc4386d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="100%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/soundcloud%253Atracks%253A1653460449&amp;amp;color=%2376d7ce&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comments=true&amp;amp;show_user=true&amp;amp;show_reposts=false&amp;amp;show_teaser=true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; line-break: anywhere; word-break: normal; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/w-a-production" title="W. A. Production®" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;W. A. Production®&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/w-a-production/heavy-hitting-hip-hop" title="Heavy Hitting Hip Hop | Murda Beatz / Hit-Boy Style Sounds, Serum Presets &amp;amp; MIDI" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;Heavy Hitting Hip Hop | Murda Beatz / Hit-Boy Style Sounds, Serum Presets &amp;amp; MIDI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;Heavy Hitting Hip Hop is a royalty-free pack designed for powerful modern hip hop and hybrid trap production. It includes booming 808s, gritty beats, haunting melodies, synths, one-shots, loops, MIDI files and Serum presets to help producers create tracks with raw energy and polished impact.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="moombahtoncaliente"&gt;&lt;a id="moombahtoncaliente"&gt;Moombahton Caliente&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8e996a6bf6fa3debe51816b689162ce69113cd85.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=378c3809cd7189a01cc096c94d76759b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="100%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/soundcloud%253Atracks%253A1161883678&amp;amp;color=%2376d7ce&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comments=true&amp;amp;show_user=true&amp;amp;show_reposts=false&amp;amp;show_teaser=true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; line-break: anywhere; word-break: normal; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/w-a-production" title="W. A. Production®" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;W. A. Production®&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/w-a-production/moombahton-caliente" title="Major Lazer / Dillon Francis Style Kits, Melodies, Drums &amp;amp; Presets | Moombahton Caliente" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;Major Lazer / Dillon Francis Style Kits, Melodies, Drums &amp;amp; Presets | Moombahton Caliente&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;Moombahton Caliente brings a Latin mid-tempo bounce inspired by Major Lazer and Dillon Francis. The pack includes construction kits, melody loops with MIDI, drum loops, Serum presets, synth shots, FX and percussion, giving producers a versatile toolkit for moombahton, EDM and trap productions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="urbandreams"&gt;&lt;a id="urbandreams"&gt;Urban DREAMS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/862bc5047b8b64640e2c85e7efa16c9ba1c77eb5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=81c2562288325df713cc841254c59ab0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Urban DREAMS is a royalty-free sound pack for modern producers, offering production-ready loops, samples, one-shots and creative audio material for hip hop, trap and electronic music. It is designed to speed up workflow, spark ideas and help build polished tracks with high-quality source material.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt30"&gt;Pay $30 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="afterlifelofidrumkit"&gt;&lt;a id="afterlifelofidrumkit"&gt;Afterlife LoFi Drum Kit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c2442a900033a8bdcd02d947448e1b79d8e02c66.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d8fba4c4233a05acdb1df464c16f5e09"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="100%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/soundcloud%253Atracks%253A907598494&amp;amp;color=%2376d7ce&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comments=true&amp;amp;show_user=true&amp;amp;show_reposts=false&amp;amp;show_teaser=true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; line-break: anywhere; word-break: normal; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering" title="BVKER.COM" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;BVKER.COM&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering/afterlife" title="Lo-Fi Hip Hop Sample Pack &amp;quot;Afterlife&amp;quot;" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;Lo-Fi Hip Hop Sample Pack "Afterlife"&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;Afterlife LoFi Drum Kit is a royalty-free lo-fi drum and bonus content library for lo-fi hip hop production. It includes hundreds of drum shots, drum loops, ambiences, atmospheric pads, sweep effects, melodic loops, MIDI loops, tonal one-shots and construction kits for nostalgic, textured beats.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="artifactsboombapsamples"&gt;&lt;a id="artifactsboombapsamples"&gt;Artifacts Boom Bap Samples&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/709e9f801191fcc8c2c0758ba2e021f6252aea81.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=81e509d21bfde05f642ed8f8799871b7"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="100%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/soundcloud%253Atracks%253A1029812470&amp;amp;color=%2376d7ce&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comments=true&amp;amp;show_user=true&amp;amp;show_reposts=false&amp;amp;show_teaser=true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; line-break: anywhere; word-break: normal; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering" title="BVKER.COM" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;BVKER.COM&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering/boom-bap-sample-pack" title="Royalty-free Boom Bap Sample Pack &amp;quot;Artifacts&amp;quot;" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;Royalty-free Boom Bap Sample Pack "Artifacts"&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;Artifacts Boom Bap Samples is a large royalty-free boom bap library with dusty drums, melancholic melodies, MIDI files and construction kits. The sounds are processed for a vintage character with tape-style warmth, subtle distortion and noise, giving producers an old-school hip hop palette with modern workflow organization.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="delusiontrapmelodies"&gt;&lt;a id="delusiontrapmelodies"&gt;Delusion Trap Melodies&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/dfad93ed29abdd2bfcc6c5f6efd06f2b85c7fa74.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2834f28f051c34af11188e6a0ece180b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="100%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/soundcloud%253Atracks%253A882799975&amp;amp;color=%2376d7ce&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comments=true&amp;amp;show_user=true&amp;amp;show_reposts=false&amp;amp;show_teaser=true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; line-break: anywhere; word-break: normal; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering" title="BVKER.COM" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;BVKER.COM&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering/hip-hop-melodies" title="100+ Hip Hop Melodies &amp;quot;Delusion&amp;quot;" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;100+ Hip Hop Melodies "Delusion"&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;Delusion Trap Melodies is a melody-focused trap pack with mix-ready loops that can be dragged straight into a project. Each loop is BPM and key labeled and comes with a matching MIDI file, plus chopped melody versions, making it easy to build new trap, hip hop and urban beats quickly.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="disputeddrillsamplepack"&gt;&lt;a id="disputeddrillsamplepack"&gt;Disputed Drill Sample Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3da450c9b13e472faee23e2ec937c56cf0d901cb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=516997e4d801f2d7e0b9f0eddd7896bf"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="100%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/soundcloud%253Atracks%253A1268702857&amp;amp;color=%2376d7ce&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comments=true&amp;amp;show_user=true&amp;amp;show_reposts=false&amp;amp;show_teaser=true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; line-break: anywhere; word-break: normal; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering" title="BVKER.COM" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;BVKER.COM&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering/disputed-drill-sample-pack" title="NY &amp;amp; UK Drill Sample Pack &amp;quot;Disputed&amp;quot;" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;NY &amp;amp; UK Drill Sample Pack "Disputed"&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;Disputed Drill Sample Pack is built for fresh drill production with new drum hits, cymbals, drum loops, closed hat MIDI patterns, long booming 808s, drill slides, melodic loops, MIDI files and FX. It provides the core ingredients needed for hard NY/UK drill beats in WAV and MIDI formats.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="808vip_serum808presets"&gt;&lt;a id="808vip_serum808presets"&gt;808 VIP: Serum 808 Presets&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9dfedf3d14f14d27eb9be6d5eab56d5864a8bbcb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d8e22fbd199a4eab38b9e3036e813292"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="100%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/soundcloud%253Atracks%253A738735439&amp;amp;color=%2376d7ce&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comments=true&amp;amp;show_user=true&amp;amp;show_reposts=false&amp;amp;show_teaser=true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; line-break: anywhere; word-break: normal; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering" title="BVKER.COM" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;BVKER.COM&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering/bvker-808-vip" title="808 VIP // Samples, Loops, MIDIs &amp;amp; Presets" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;808 VIP // Samples, Loops, MIDIs &amp;amp; Presets&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;808 VIP is a complete 808 toolkit centered around Serum presets and sound design flexibility. It includes Serum 808 presets with macro controls, wavetables, multi-sampled 808 one-shots, 808 loops, MIDI files and matching kick loops/one-shots, making it easy to craft customized trap and hip hop basslines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="oxygenforhybridtrap"&gt;&lt;a id="oxygenforhybridtrap"&gt;Oxygen for Hybrid Trap&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1751bdd8f97da2855863c52aff19026baa2d6499.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ad19dc183132aed35c090a2b02558840"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Oxygen for Hybrid Trap is a royalty-free trap production toolkit built for modern beats, heavy 808s and energetic arrangements. It brings together drums, bass elements, loops, one-shots, FX and musical inspiration so producers can move quickly from beat idea to finished track.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="trappresetsforserum_vol2"&gt;&lt;a id="trappresetsforserum_vol2"&gt;Trap Presets For Serum Vol. 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/aceb038ed89048f4aa316dad9603d43f7e4db300.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2c0514d4ead537a0510487f929ea5149"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Trap Presets For Serum Vol. 2 delivers 120 Serum presets inspired by modern trap and hip hop trends. Each preset includes custom macro controls for quick shaping, with additional loops and MIDI content to help producers create basses, leads, synths, plucks and chords for contemporary trap productions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="trapforserum_vol1"&gt;&lt;a id="trapforserum_vol1"&gt;Trap For Serum Vol. 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c7ff982a6982b76daf806df5a4199062dbe8a24d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=fc15a1cd401adb9e1b2f7ac153fa2a61"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="100%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/soundcloud%253Atracks%253A540652239&amp;amp;color=%2376d7ce&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comments=true&amp;amp;show_user=true&amp;amp;show_reposts=false&amp;amp;show_teaser=true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; line-break: anywhere; word-break: normal; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering" title="BVKER.COM" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;BVKER.COM&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering/trap-for-serum" title="Trap For Serum Vol.1 // Serum Presets, Loops, MIDIs" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;Trap For Serum Vol.1 // Serum Presets, Loops, MIDIs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;Trap For Serum Vol. 1 is a Serum preset collection inspired by current hip hop and trap chart sounds. It includes 80 presets with macro controls, Serum wavetables, audio loops and MIDI loops, giving producers a practical soundbank for basses, leads, chords and modern trap melodies.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="latenightlofi"&gt;&lt;a id="latenightlofi"&gt;Late Night LoFi&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/26371dc5d2bba7e64ade1dcfaadfb83cccedbe55.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=734f3acf485f616615516253fb1a133f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="100%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/soundcloud%253Atracks%253A816918364&amp;amp;color=%2376d7ce&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comments=true&amp;amp;show_user=true&amp;amp;show_reposts=false&amp;amp;show_teaser=true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; line-break: anywhere; word-break: normal; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering" title="BVKER.COM" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;BVKER.COM&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/amazr-mastering/trap-for-serum-2" title="Trap For Serum Vol. 2 // Serum Presets, Loops, MIDI Files" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;Trap For Serum Vol. 2 // Serum Presets, Loops, MIDI Files&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;Late Night LoFi is a royalty-free lofi production pack built for chilled beats, study music and warm hip hop textures. It focuses on relaxed melodies, dusty drums, atmospheric loops, organic one-shots and musical ideas that help producers create mellow, nostalgic tracks with a smooth workflow.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="organictrapdrums"&gt;&lt;a id="organictrapdrums" href="https://youtu.be/XCP5u6BMvJ0"&gt;Organic Trap Drums&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/bcee4609fd6c41c6fcf4ff9a70b1ec9d91e205a9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9615c8cda0d21cf1abef61d2e3d8e568"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Organic Trap Drums is a royalty-free trap production toolkit built for modern beats, heavy 808s and energetic arrangements. It brings together drums, bass elements, loops, one-shots, FX and musical inspiration so producers can move quickly from beat idea to finished track.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="bangin808s"&gt;&lt;a id="bangin808s" href="https://youtu.be/1_LAthTNYJs"&gt;Bangin 808s&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8b5dc38036fd5929cb68655cacfab87455f33606.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4b701e779170e14b33115c2348abbb6e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bangin 808s is an 808 bass pack covering clean, heavy and distorted low-end sounds for trap and hip hop. It includes key-labeled 808 one-shots, audio loops and MIDI loops so producers can quickly build basslines and create hard-hitting beats with wall-shaking low end.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ambientrimshots"&gt;&lt;a id="ambientrimshots" href="https://youtu.be/ZrMNFWe4C3s"&gt;Ambient Rimshots&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9d73e0399c9cfab3e554143eb4dedfbf0ccb799a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=30d557f34562758359b62e195f8201ec"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ambient Rimshots is a royalty-free sound pack for modern producers, offering production-ready loops, samples, one-shots and creative audio material for hip hop, trap and electronic music. It is designed to speed up workflow, spark ideas and help build polished tracks with high-quality source material.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="essentialtrapdrums"&gt;&lt;a id="essentialtrapdrums" href="https://youtu.be/EnpUncgs6VA"&gt;Essential Trap Drums&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/74e2f4f07454f27f87ae423c4e443b5509e530e6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4a315c5e3f40a1e629c3f9257b227ddf"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Essential Trap Drums is a royalty-free trap production toolkit built for modern beats, heavy 808s and energetic arrangements. It brings together drums, bass elements, loops, one-shots, FX and musical inspiration so producers can move quickly from beat idea to finished track.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="icedouttrap"&gt;&lt;a id="icedouttrap" href="https://youtu.be/k95-u-5ZwTE"&gt;Iced Out Trap&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f800cb3fb58b975e4ac70fac088deb0314e3a895.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=cdad0deaaecb6bda94b5c2bf441e3366"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Iced Out Trap is a royalty-free trap production toolkit built for modern beats, heavy 808s and energetic arrangements. It brings together drums, bass elements, loops, one-shots, FX and musical inspiration so producers can move quickly from beat idea to finished track.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="trapitup"&gt;&lt;a id="trapitup" href="https://youtu.be/LBFc1RTlPWQ"&gt;Trap It Up&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/b59ee17f41203c04a1f4b0d7f98fdedae5a488dc.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=700da67163b5d70a1db1de509656ca02"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Trap It Up is a complete trap production pack with loops, MIDI, one-shots and Massive presets. Built for producers crafting hip hop and trap beats, it focuses on punchy 808s, crisp snares and claps, infectious melodies and ready-to-use sound design tools for fast beat creation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="lofihiphopcoast"&gt;&lt;a id="lofihiphopcoast" href="https://youtu.be/ZkZ_94oNuCU"&gt;Lofi Hip Hop Coast&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0a78796e97410f4e27e0878285d61fa987fcac20.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=92e9d4a5aaff1e01bf03b167aa3c6b58"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lofi Hip Hop Coast is a relaxed lofi hip hop production pack with loops, MIDI, Serum presets and one-shots. It focuses on grooving rhythms, chilled melodies and genre-specific drum and synth sounds, helping producers create warm study-beat, chill and coastal lofi hip hop tracks.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="lofichill"&gt;&lt;a id="lofichill" href="https://youtu.be/_rK400Svris"&gt;Lofi Chill&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/816527c8814147353b616b595d32df9c26509c4d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=60426c114d40433c410d1b09a7f1e608"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lofi Chill is a relaxed lofi production pack built around five construction kits plus melody loops, drum loops, drum shots and synth shots. It provides a laid-back toolkit for producers looking to create chilled beats, atmospheric lofi hip hop and mellow background music with a warm, easygoing vibe.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="lofihiphopbreeze"&gt;&lt;a id="lofihiphopbreeze" href="https://youtu.be/d_98kpsA7Ts"&gt;Lofi Hip Hop Breeze&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/94e7379c47372831419383012953233c66ac146d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=78695c630f94af8105bda412a53ed15f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lofi Hip Hop Breeze contains classic lofi hip hop sounds for chilled beatmaking, including melody loops with MIDI, drum loops, Serum presets, synth shots, percussion and FX. It is designed around relaxing chords, vintage textures and laid-back rhythms for smooth lofi productions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="spicyvocaltrap"&gt;&lt;a id="spicyvocaltrap" href="https://youtu.be/IXduPqP80L8"&gt;Spicy Vocal Trap&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6072c1e258c87371535f3cc5303696156c26462f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9c71a701dfb5f38c9851047fae7c9964"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Spicy Vocal Trap is a trap and vocal production pack with vocal kits, vocal loops, melody loops, drum loops, drum samples, presets and FX. It gives producers a broad set of ingredients for building full trap tracks from start to finish, with vocals and sound design elements ready for modern arrangements.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="lofiillusion2"&gt;&lt;a id="lofiillusion2" href="https://youtu.be/T79y_vaVOxE"&gt;Lofi Illusion 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/25f478303008f7a9a85d751961bf4c4ce21a3751.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2375df3eb68ccb975089e7f4aa2a7161"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lofi Illusion 2 expands the original Lofi Illusion concept with lounge-style lofi samples, textures, pads, keys, piano riffs, chords, flutes, trumpets, saxophones, organs, guitar, bass, bells and chimes. It includes melody loops, MIDI, Serum presets, drums and FX for dreamy lofi production.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="loficinematicandmoviesounds"&gt;&lt;a id="loficinematicandmoviesounds" href="https://youtu.be/Le6mka7LB98"&gt;Lofi Cinematic &amp; Movie Sounds&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4120003f680a9ba394cfac6ab0706029ff9fb753.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7bfb418648030844bf402458aba284b9"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lofi Cinematic &amp;amp; Movie Sounds combines lofi hip hop textures with cinematic and film-inspired sound design. The pack includes loops, MIDI, Serum presets, drums, pads, percussion and strings to help producers create dramatic lofi beats, background music, film cues, game audio or chilled cinematic atmospheres.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="lofihiphopdaydream"&gt;&lt;a id="lofihiphopdaydream" href="https://youtu.be/SSlQH-758AA"&gt;Lofi Hip Hop Daydream&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/