 allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/soundcloud%253Atracks%253A124559291&amp;amp;color=%2376d7ce&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comments=true&amp;amp;show_user=true&amp;amp;show_reposts=false&amp;amp;show_teaser=true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; line-break: anywhere; word-break: normal; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif; font-weight: 100;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/w-a-production" title="W. A. Production®" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;W. A. Production®&lt;/a&gt; · &lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/w-a-production/w-a-production-what-about" title="W. A. Production - What About EDM And URBAN Vocal SHOUTS Demo" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;" rel="noopener"&gt;W. A. Production - What About EDM And URBAN Vocal SHOUTS Demo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;EDM &amp;amp; Urban Vocal Shouts is a royalty-free vocal toolkit for EDM, trap, hip hop and urban productions. It provides vocal shouts, phrases, hooks, loops and supporting production elements that can add energy, movement and human character to drops, build-ups, beats and full arrangements.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
