      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7f5ff654930263b148b0dc7b358dc3c94fb1d2e7.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=e445ec3115951c93d9662b57f0dc1a48"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ccf11b38442f0558f83818cfaab83ef5065212b8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=6e5c1f243d88f6e9aa19608018e89e3e"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Discover what’s possible with Unity AI&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Pay what you want to learn how to use Unity AI, the ultimate AI assistant from the pros at Mammoth Club. Unity AI is your agentic assistant—editor-integrated, project-aware, and designed to streamline your workflows. It’s also your AI gateway, connecting directly to your models and tools to maximize performance, security, and control, while serving as your bridge to Unity from your IDE or preferred application. Highlighted by lessons like &lt;em&gt;Build a TikTok LIVE Game with Unity AI - Interactive Chat-Controlled Game&lt;/em&gt;, this curated collection offers everything you need to become an AI mastermind. Save time, money, and reduce operational friction with the Complete Unity AI Bundle before it’s gone! &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ef9741;"&gt;Keys expire. Please redeem your keys before July 07, 2027. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unitygamedevelopmentforabsolutebeginnersandallages"&gt;Unity Game Development for Absolute Beginners and All Ages&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildyourfirstcgameinunity"&gt;Build Your First C# Game in Unity&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#agenticassistant_build3dfirst-personshooterwithunityaifirst-timeex"&gt;Agentic Assistant - Build 3D First-Person Shooter with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildatiktoklivegamewithunityai_interactivechat-controlledgamefirs"&gt;Build a TikTok LIVE Game with Unity AI - Interactive Chat-Controlled Game &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#aigateway_builda2dasteroidshootergamewithunityfirst-timeexclusiveh"&gt;AI Gateway - Build a 2D Asteroid Shooter Game with Unity &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#mcpserver_buildafirstpersonpuzzlegamewithunityaifirst-timeexclusiv"&gt;MCP Server - Build a First Person Puzzle Game with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildacardbattlegameusingunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumblebundlerel"&gt;Build a Card Battle Game Using Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#builda3dlifesimulatorwithdialogueandsavesystemsinunityaifirst-time"&gt;Build a 3D Life Simulator with Dialogue in Unity AI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildatiktokminigamewithunityaiassistantfirst-timeexclusivehumbleb"&gt;Build a TikTok Mini Game with Unity AI Assistant &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#builda3dinventorysystemwithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumblebundler"&gt;Build a 3D Inventory System with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unityaiessentials_buildafruitcuttinggamefirst-timeexclusivehumbleb"&gt;Unity AI Essentials: Build a Fruit Cutting Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildassetswithunityaigeneratorsfirst-timeexclusivehumblebundlerel"&gt;Build Assets with Unity AI Generators &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildatop-downactionrpgwithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumblebundler"&gt;Build a Top-Down Action RPG with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildaproceduraldungeongeneratorwithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumb"&gt;Build a Procedural Dungeon Generator with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildatowerdefensegamewithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumblebundlere"&gt;Build a Tower Defense Game with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildaturn-basedrpgcombatsystemwithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumbl"&gt;Build a Turn-Based RPG Combat System with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#automatewithunityaiassistantandgenerators_builda3dbubbleshootergam"&gt;Automate with Unity AI Assistant and Generators - Build a 3D Bubble Shooter Game &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#builda3dplatformerwithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumblebundlereleas"&gt;Build a 3D Platformer with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#builda2dslidingpuzzlenumbermergegamewithunityaifirst-timeexclusive"&gt;Build a 2D Sliding Puzzle Number Merge Game with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#build-a-2d-snake-game-with-unity-ai"&gt;Build a 2D Snake Game with Unity AI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#build-a-3d-endless-road-crossing-game-with-unity-ai-first-time-exclusive-humble-bundle-release"&gt;Build a 3D Endless Road Crossing Game with Unity AI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unityandaiassistantfoundationsforabsolutebeginnersfirst-timeexclus"&gt;Unity and AI Assistant Foundations for Absolute Beginners &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#revolutionizegamedevelopment_guidetounitydotsecs"&gt;Revolutionize Game Development: Guide to Unity DOTS ECS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildingimmersivegameplay_collisionsandtriggersinunityecs"&gt;Building Immersive Gameplay: Collisions and Triggers in Unity ECS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#optimizingperformance_buildaunitycjobsysteminecs"&gt;Optimizing Performance: Build a Unity C# Job System in ECS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="unitygamedevelopmentforabsolutebeginnersandallages"&gt;&lt;a id="unitygamedevelopmentforabsolutebeginnersandallages"&gt;Unity Game Development for Absolute Beginners and All Ages&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7cbcc624a068c4593ff0d2a732b62942fe4abe42.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3f1068d0d1f6e2d4ade17b8fc99972f2"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Never opened Unity before? That's exactly who this is for.    This video course is built for complete beginners of any age who want to get started with game development.     You'll learn through simple, clear steps with no assumption of prior experience.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Get familiar with the Unity interface  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Understand the basics of game objects and scenes  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build simple interactive projects from scratch  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Gain the confidence to keep learning on your own  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Game development is for everyone. This course proves it.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Open Unity for the first time and take it from there.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildyourfirstcgameinunity"&gt;&lt;a id="buildyourfirstcgameinunity"&gt;Build Your First C# Game in Unity&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ae96f2969f42fe06f1fdc3faf313e6abc703fee5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f908808777408f31da4f012d93e381e6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Every Unity developer started somewhere. This is a great place to begin.    You'll write real C# code and build an actual game in Unity, learning the fundamentals in a way that sticks because you're applying them as you go.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Learn C# basics in the context of game development  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Understand core Unity concepts hands-on  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Write scripts that control real game behavior  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Finish the course with a complete playable game  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;No prior experience needed, just a willingness to learn by doing.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Your first Unity game is closer than you think. Start here.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="agenticassistant_build3dfirst-personshooterwithunityaifirst-timeex"&gt;&lt;a id="agenticassistant_build3dfirst-personshooterwithunityaifirst-timeex"&gt;Agentic Assistant - Build 3D First-Person Shooter with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d7b71fa34765d756e11047fecc7c214b4b0534d9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=47e9378a357957e034cec62de91f64bc"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Igor Aherne returns with a brand-new exclusive launch video course! You've probably spent hours writing scripts from scratch. What if Unity's AI assistant could handle the heavy lifting while you focus on building the game?    Dive into building a complete 3D first-person shooter, using Unity's AI tools at every step of the way.     Here's what you'll cover:  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Set up Unity and enable its AI assistant  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Generate a 3D gun from an image and a move-script  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build levels and enemies with AI assistant  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Create 3D characters using Nano Banana and Unity AI  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Animate characters and generate sounds via AI  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Design and script UI using Unity AI tools  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Apply materials and lightmapping with AI support  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;By the end, you'll have a working 3D shooter and a repeatable workflow for using AI inside Unity on your next project.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Put the AI to work and start building.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildatiktoklivegamewithunityai_interactivechat-controlledgamefirs"&gt;&lt;a id="buildatiktoklivegamewithunityai_interactivechat-controlledgamefirs"&gt;Build a TikTok LIVE Game with Unity AI - Interactive Chat-Controlled Game &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c5eaa74cb153a22a0cfbf653b2c1574e95acd21f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=bb7e3fa34f57ba8a8e6637f96e96c620"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;What if your viewers weren't just watching, they were playing?     This video course walks you through building a TikTok LIVE game where chat interaction drives the gameplay.    Using Unity AI as your assistant, you'll connect Unity to TikTok LIVE and build a system that responds to real viewer input in real time.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Connect Unity to TikTok LIVE chat  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build gameplay systems driven by viewer messages  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Use Unity AI to assist throughout the build  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Deliver an interactive experience for live audiences  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A hands-on course for developers ready to build something outside the usual game format.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Give your audience something to do besides watch.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="aigateway_builda2dasteroidshootergamewithunityfirst-timeexclusiveh"&gt;&lt;a id="aigateway_builda2dasteroidshootergamewithunityfirst-timeexclusiveh"&gt;AI Gateway - Build a 2D Asteroid Shooter Game with Unity &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0584d28cf5d98944dfcd87c42e50f3ba1885b091.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d2a5566a560835452822fca29ce2dae8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;You've heard about AI-assisted development. This video course shows you what it actually looks like in practice, from the first sprite to a finished game.    You'll set up the AI Gateway, learn how to write prompts that get useful results, and build a complete game step by step.     The lessons also cover the honest stuff, like what to do when AI gets it wrong and what it simply can't do.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Set up AI Gateway and write effective prompts  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Generate game sprites and set up your project with AI  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build player movement, shooting, and an arena  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Add asteroids, a fuel system, sound effects, and UI  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Handle score, game over, and AI limitations honestly  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You'll walk away with a finished game and a realistic sense of where AI fits into your workflow.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Don't wait! Enroll now while spots remain.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="mcpserver_buildafirstpersonpuzzlegamewithunityaifirst-timeexclusiv"&gt;&lt;a id="mcpserver_buildafirstpersonpuzzlegamewithunityaifirst-timeexclusiv"&gt;MCP Server - Build a First Person Puzzle Game with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/bd367e41f83bcb0ee695213d2cedd92dd8a76459.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=48441aa540223864024edf6924da5494"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;MCP Server integration opens up a different way of working with Unity AI. This video course shows you exactly how.    You'll build a game while learning how to connect and use an MCP Server alongside Unity's AI assistant, giving you a broader set of tools to work with.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Understand MCP Server and its role in Unity AI  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Connect MCP Server to your Unity workflow  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build a game project using this expanded toolset  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you want to go beyond the basics of Unity AI, this course points you in the right direction.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Start building with more tools at your disposal.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildacardbattlegameusingunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumblebundlerel"&gt;&lt;a id="buildacardbattlegameusingunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumblebundlerel"&gt;Build a Card Battle Game Using Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a64f5f791c3371b737dad2dd4a4c9c18858cbfe4.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=42f390a7295013d0cb93e5ca9e1cee65"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Igor Aherne returns with a new first-time release course! Card games require careful thinking about game state, turn flow, and player interaction.     This video course walks you through building one from the ground up with Unity AI helping at every stage.    You'll design the grid, implement totem movement, build a deck system, handle card UI, and finish with visual effects that bring the game to life.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Set up the project and Unity AI assistant  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Design the grid with totems and movement logic  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Implement turn-based gameplay with AI-assisted scripts  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build the card and deck system  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Add camera navigation, card dragging, UI, and VFX  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A focused build that covers game logic, UI, and polish in one project.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shuffle the deck and start building.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="builda3dlifesimulatorwithdialogueandsavesystemsinunityaifirst-time"&gt;&lt;a id="builda3dlifesimulatorwithdialogueandsavesystemsinunityaifirst-time"&gt;Build a 3D Life Simulator with Dialogue in Unity AI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e37f10a748816c58f2a87e4197623b14e9a29ed0.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=839e992d05da3c482cf595062090512e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Life simulators are rich with systems, conversations, progression, and persistent data.     This video course covers building one in Unity with AI assistance, touching on dialogue systems and save functionality along the way.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build a 3D life simulator environment in Unity  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Implement a dialogue system for character interactions  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Use Unity AI throughout the development process  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A project-based course for developers who want to tackle one of the more complex game genres.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Start building the world your players will live in.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildatiktokminigamewithunityaiassistantfirst-timeexclusivehumbleb"&gt;&lt;a id="buildatiktokminigamewithunityaiassistantfirst-timeexclusivehumbleb"&gt;Build a TikTok Mini Game with Unity AI Assistant &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a4a9459738de65935b816a05f79453b4412de4cc.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=bcd6c6fbe3e1f529713b462afc0ee5dc"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ever wanted to build a game that runs inside TikTok? This video course takes you through the full process, from setting up Unity AI to getting your game live in the TikTok app.    You'll connect to the TikTok SDK, build the required features, set up a server to host credentials, and configure your WebGL build files so everything runs the way it should.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Set up Unity AI Assistant for the project  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Connect Unity to the TikTok SDK  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build and configure required TikTok game features  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Set up a server to host TikTok credentials  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Configure WebGL build files and test in TikTok preview  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A practical course for developers who want to ship a game on a platform people are actually using.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Set it up and get your game in the app.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="builda3dinventorysystemwithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumblebundler"&gt;&lt;a id="builda3dinventorysystemwithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumblebundler"&gt;Build a 3D Inventory System with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/bb6c279e87182608a19dca3f0413dd2ea1dd42e7.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1127c33e87aeff69408ab965c919a469"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Inventory systems are one of those features that show up in almost every game. This video course walks you through building a complete one in Unity, from core mechanics to saving and loading data. You'll cover everything from drag-and-drop management and item equipping to crafting, storage containers, and using Unity AI to optimize and extend the system.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;► Build a core inventory system with AI assistance&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;► Implement drag-and-drop and world item pickup&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;► Add item descriptions, equipping, and consumption&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;► Build a crafting system and storage containers&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;► Save and load inventory data, then optimize with Unity AI&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;A thorough project that covers one of the most reusable systems in game development.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Build it once and use it in every project after.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="unityaiessentials_buildafruitcuttinggamefirst-timeexclusivehumbleb"&gt;&lt;a id="unityaiessentials_buildafruitcuttinggamefirst-timeexclusivehumbleb"&gt;Unity AI Essentials: Build a Fruit Cutting Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9f900e547aa0022cbe8bc3ff3830ce5f74d547a0.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=296c2bae6746ef4cdd355fbfd9ce649b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A fun, focused vide course for getting hands-on with Unity AI.     You'll build a fruit cutting game while learning how Unity's AI tools fit into a real development workflow.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build a complete fruit cutting game in Unity  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Use Unity AI throughout the development process  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Learn practical AI-assisted workflows on a real project  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► A manageable project scope, great for building confidence  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A lighthearted project with real skills behind it.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Pick it up and start cutting.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildassetswithunityaigeneratorsfirst-timeexclusivehumblebundlerel"&gt;&lt;a id="buildassetswithunityaigeneratorsfirst-timeexclusivehumblebundlerel"&gt;Build Assets with Unity AI Generators &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0fcf708bd181decf6e68ae9f045b2f025e3f32e9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a71c8195674658ea6d2fd1c3912a5a1f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Creating game assets usually takes time.     This video course focuses on using Unity's AI Generators to speed that process up and see what's actually possible.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Use Unity AI Generators to create game assets  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Explore what asset types can be generated with AI  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Learn how to apply generated assets inside Unity  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A straightforward look at Unity's generation tools and where they fit in your workflow.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;See what Unity AI can build for you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildatop-downactionrpgwithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumblebundler"&gt;&lt;a id="buildatop-downactionrpgwithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumblebundler"&gt;Build a Top-Down Action RPG with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8d24e64f121b04a7cff8b8e646084a9685086a3d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=04c86f82c9feb84c54d2262057fc0451"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Setting up Unity AI is only the beginning. This video course gets you through the full process, from installation to a working top-down RPG with real gameplay mechanics.    You'll start by getting the AI assistant running properly, then use it to generate characters from 2D images, build a game world, and add interactive elements like destructible crates.     Along the way, you'll also fix the kind of small issues that come up in any real project.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Install and configure the Unity AI Assistant  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Generate 3D character meshes from 2D images  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build a top-down world with core mechanics  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Add destructible crates with score bonuses  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Apply textures and refine gameplay feel  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A hands-on video course that takes you from setup to a playable RPG using Unity's AI tools throughout.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ready to build? Start with lesson one.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildaproceduraldungeongeneratorwithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumb"&gt;&lt;a id="buildaproceduraldungeongeneratorwithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumb"&gt;Build a Procedural Dungeon Generator with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/83f01c7b8dab16aabf2eaf8c21dd60a6e8c773dc.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ec1164d0757c5fbcf96258c9dee92b40"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Procedural generation is one of those skills that makes your games feel alive. Every run is different, every dungeon is new.     This video course teaches you how to build that system in Unity with AI, covering everything from textures to enemies to the finishing touches that make it feel like a real game.    You'll go from generating the dungeon itself all the way to a polished experience with sound and a game over screen.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build a procedural dungeon generator from scratch  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Generating dungeon textures procedurally  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Spawning enemies inside your dungeon  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Improving enemy behavior and game feel  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Adding a game over widget and sounds  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Use Unity AI to assist throughout the build  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;By the end you'll have a working dungeon generator and a much clearer understanding of how procedural systems actually come together in Unity.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build something that plays differently every time.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildatowerdefensegamewithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumblebundlere"&gt;&lt;a id="buildatowerdefensegamewithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumblebundlere"&gt;Build a Tower Defense Game with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6a3a394455c8cc1d69652c9b772759ccb91eed82.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=89218dfea0bbff658a54cd37f46d8ad2"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tower defense is one of the best genres for learning core game systems, waves, pathing, targeting, upgrades. This video course covers all of it.    You'll build a tower defense game in Unity while using AI tools to help design, script, and iterate throughout the process.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Set up wave and enemy spawning systems  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build tower placement and targeting mechanics  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Use Unity AI to speed up design and scripting  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Bring all systems together into a complete game  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're sharpening your Unity skills or exploring AI-assisted development, this project gives you both.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Pick it up and start placing towers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildaturn-basedrpgcombatsystemwithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumbl"&gt;&lt;a id="buildaturn-basedrpgcombatsystemwithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumbl"&gt;Build a Turn-Based RPG Combat System with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7d18983a86f5d29dfb456a7a35e3b15f79a9b07a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=12eed52cfc3b8cee4e1306e352289deb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Turn-based combat systems have a lot of moving parts.     This video course walks you through building one in Unity using AI tools to help along the way.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Design and build a turn-based combat system  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Handle game states, turns, and combat logic  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Use Unity AI to assist with development  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Finish with a working RPG combat foundation  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A practical course for developers who want to understand how turn-based systems are actually built.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Start building your combat system today.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="automatewithunityaiassistantandgenerators_builda3dbubbleshootergam"&gt;&lt;a id="automatewithunityaiassistantandgenerators_builda3dbubbleshootergam"&gt;Automate with Unity AI Assistant and Generators - Build a 3D Bubble Shooter Game &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/cd9857c9488b7af684f782f04c9d6e7e6ff4a9ea.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ddde0f57d50f16a809bf725878d28ce6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Anyone can generate a game. This video course shows you how to do it properly using Unity's AI tools to build a complete 3D Bubble Shooter from start to finish.    You'll install Unity AI and work through its core modes, Ask, Plan, and Agent, then use Unity's AI-powered generators to create the scripts, icons, 3D models, materials, and assets your game needs.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Explore Ask, Plan, and Agent modes in Unity AI  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Generate textures, materials, sprites and 3D models with Unity AI  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Generate all scripts and game features with Unity AI  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes prompts and source files so you can revisit every step and reuse assets in your own projects.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Start building your 3D Bubble Shooter with Unity AI today.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="builda3dplatformerwithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumblebundlereleas"&gt;&lt;a id="builda3dplatformerwithunityaifirst-timeexclusivehumblebundlereleas"&gt;Build a 3D Platformer with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/517288e195bfbccbc7c2f63579a8a6f3543f81df.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c611a12b4f8093d00c8132edfe3bf30a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Platformers are a classic for a reason.     This video course takes you through building a 3D platformer in Unity with Unity AI as your assistant throughout the process.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build a 3D platformer from the ground up  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Set up movement, jumping, and level interactions  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Use Unity AI to speed up your development process  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Finish with a complete, playable 3D platformer  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A hands-on project that covers the fundamentals of 3D game development in Unity.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Jump in and start building.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="builda2dslidingpuzzlenumbermergegamewithunityaifirst-timeexclusive"&gt;&lt;a id="builda2dslidingpuzzlenumbermergegamewithunityaifirst-timeexclusive"&gt;Build a 2D Sliding Puzzle Number Merge Game with Unity AI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f357d95c8c8fad3bb7aabec3fa92f872ace9b614.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9e0f65e46905271c9fd780297032c9a2"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Puzzle games are all about tight logic and satisfying feedback.     This video course walks you through building a 2D sliding number merge game in Unity with AI assistance at every stage of the build.    You'll go from scene setup and grid creation all the way through tile logic, player input, movement, and a complete UI with score and game over handling.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Set up the scene layout and game grid  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Bring tiles to life with logic and behavior  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Implement input handling and smooth movement  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build score tracking, UI, and game over flow  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Use Unity AI throughout the entire project  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A focused, complete build that covers the core systems behind any good puzzle game.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Set up your grid and start sliding.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="build-a-2d-snake-game-with-unity-ai"&gt;&lt;a id="build-a-2d-snake-game-with-unity-ai"&gt;Build a 2D Snake Game with Unity AI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1ee897a659fd57bdd98a0c98086fcd74d3a9af9b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2ad717f1b4b8aec5c94a15be8101e72a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Snake games are a great way to learn core gameplay programming and AI-assisted development.    This video course walks you through building a complete 2D Snake game in Unity with AI assistance at every stage of the project.    You'll go from scene setup and player movement all the way through food spawning, score tracking, game over handling, and polishing the overall experience.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Set up the game board and scene layout  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Create the snake movement and growth system  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Implement food spawning and collision detection  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build score tracking, UI, and game over screens  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Use Unity AI throughout the entire development process  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A focused, complete project that covers many of the fundamental systems used in arcade-style games.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Start building your own Snake game with Unity AI.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="build-a-3d-endless-road-crossing-game-with-unity-ai-first-time-exclusive-humble-bundle-release"&gt;&lt;a id="build-a-3d-endless-road-crossing-game-with-unity-ai-first-time-exclusive-humble-bundle-release"&gt;Build a 3D Endless Road Crossing Game with Unity AI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/49e8938b0e8388ffd8b1871c6df35a04d3a0dee4.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=861e606da0d0c4a0cc4b028ef3911bed"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Road crossing games are a great way to learn movement systems, obstacle spawning, and game state management.    This video course walks you through building a complete 2D road crossing game in Unity with AI assistance at every stage of the project.    You'll go from scene setup and player movement all the way through traffic systems, collision handling, scoring, and game over logic.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Set up the game world and lane system  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Create player movement and controls  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build vehicle spawning and traffic behavior  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Implement scoring, UI, and game over handling  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Use Unity AI throughout the entire development process  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A focused, complete project that covers many of the core systems behind endless arcade-style games.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Start building your own road crossing game with Unity AI.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="unityandaiassistantfoundationsforabsolutebeginnersfirst-timeexclus"&gt;&lt;a id="unityandaiassistantfoundationsforabsolutebeginnersfirst-timeexclus"&gt;Unity and AI Assistant Foundations for Absolute Beginners &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2399111e87d9863e9e5011f6fd8d4352031c0153.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=14f8c8657b671f6fdc799952f177ef8f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Before you build anything in Unity, you need to understand how it actually works.     This video course gives you that foundation, covering the Unity editor, its core architecture, and how Unity's AI Assistant fits into the picture.    The modules takes you from the big picture of what Unity is, through the editor windows and tools, into how Unity builds a world, and finally into what Unity AI actually is and how it works under the hood.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Understand Unity's place in the industry and Unity 6  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Navigate the editor, scene view, hierarchy, and inspector  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Learn GameObjects, components, prefabs, and scenes  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Understand the difference between a chatbot and an agent  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Explore all three Unity AI tools and how the assistant works internally  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;No assumptions, no skipped steps. Just a clear explanation of Unity and its AI tools from the ground up.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Start here and know exactly what you're working with.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="revolutionizegamedevelopment_guidetounitydotsecs"&gt;&lt;a id="revolutionizegamedevelopment_guidetounitydotsecs"&gt;Revolutionize Game Development: Guide to Unity DOTS ECS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e30cacff29772142ba3603b26a3f9b0ce1de9926.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=61dbe8291e745bb5f382f681d31c62da"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;If your Unity games are hitting performance walls, DOTS and the Entity Component System are worth your time.    This video course walks you through Unity's DOTS ECS architecture, covering what it is, why it matters, and how to start using it in your projects.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Understand the core concepts behind DOTS ECS  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Learn how ECS differs from traditional Unity workflows  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Apply DOTS to improve game performance  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Build a foundation for writing high-performance Unity code  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For developers who want to understand what's under the hood and write Unity code that scales.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Take the step toward high-performance Unity development.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildingimmersivegameplay_collisionsandtriggersinunityecs"&gt;&lt;a id="buildingimmersivegameplay_collisionsandtriggersinunityecs"&gt;Building Immersive Gameplay: Collisions and Triggers in Unity ECS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3e0ace967ab50bae3c536364f54c6a1b8c26f1da.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ff20e3174cdc6aefda19d3b080b349a1"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collisions and triggers are at the heart of almost every gameplay mechanic. Getting them right inside ECS requires a different way of thinking.    This video course focuses specifically on handling collisions and triggers within Unity's ECS framework, giving you the practical knowledge to implement them cleanly.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Understand how collisions work in Unity ECS  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Set up and respond to trigger events in ECS  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Apply collision logic to real gameplay scenarios  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Write clean, performant ECS-based interaction code  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A focused video course for developers already working in Unity ECS who want to handle interactions the right way.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Start building more responsive gameplay today.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="optimizingperformance_buildaunitycjobsysteminecs"&gt;&lt;a id="optimizingperformance_buildaunitycjobsysteminecs"&gt;Optimizing Performance: Build a Unity C# Job System in ECS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/154e28f86e99304356b9552187456d0c78de4902.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5c4f83bf25fd2b5e02d2a3858740e7ac"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Slow frame rates and stuttering gameplay are fixable problems. The Unity C# Job System is one of the best tools for solving them.    This video course teaches you how to use the C# Job System within Unity ECS to write multithreaded, high-performance code for your games.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Learn the fundamentals of the Unity C# Job System  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Write multithreaded code safely within ECS  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Identify and address common performance bottlenecks  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;► Apply job-based patterns to real game scenarios  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For developers serious about squeezing real performance out of their Unity projects.  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ Lifetime access to all modules  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;✅ All source files included  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If performance matters to you, this one belongs in your toolkit.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
