      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/52ff29a54e96055f0e8ee16e91ff51a563f7c96e.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=5a27b748d4c3c6b7551c49472431c913"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ac60be04cdcb053636c1dd9c8c7814d4c17a39ac.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=09c4eb75822ddd9cba83ad4e9650ff86"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Master Unreal Engine with ease&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Harness the power of Unreal Engine with our latest Software Learning Bundle by Zenva. This expert-led collection contains specialized courses designed to help you build any genre of game: integrate strategy and base building into your next project with &lt;em&gt;Build a Tower Defense Game in Unreal Engine&lt;/em&gt;, scare the pants off players with &lt;em&gt;Make a Horror Game in Unreal Engine&lt;/em&gt;, or add a splash of retro fun with &lt;em&gt;Develop a Classic Shoot 'em Up with Unreal Engine&lt;/em&gt;. Get serious about game design for a price you choose and help support Girls Who Code with your purchase!  &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ef9741;"&gt;Keys Expire. Please redeem before June 18th, 2027. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unrealenginemini-projects2025edition"&gt;Unreal Engine Mini-Projects&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#learn3dmodelingwithblenderfromscratchnewedition2024"&gt;Learn 3D Modeling with Blender from Scratch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#createaracinggameinunrealengine"&gt;Create a Racing Game in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#uiuxforgamedesign"&gt;UI/UX for Game Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#first-personexplorationgameinunrealengine2026edition"&gt;First-Person Exploration Game in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildacompletestealthgamewithunrealengine"&gt;Build a Complete Stealth Game with Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtomultiplayerinunrealengine"&gt;Intro to Multiplayer in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#developaclassicshootemupwithunrealengine"&gt;Develop a Classic Shoot 'em up with Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#makeahorrorgameinunrealengine"&gt;Make a Horror Game in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#createafully-fledgedbullethellinunrealengine"&gt;Create a Fully-Fledged Bullet Hell in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildatowerdefensegameinunrealengine"&gt;Build a Tower Defense Game in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#developacompleteinfiniterunnerinunrealengine"&gt;Develop a Complete Infinite Runner in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#makeafully-fledged3dplatformerwithunrealengine"&gt;Make a Fully-Fledged 3D Platformer with Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#developa2dplatformerinunrealengine"&gt;Develop a 2D Platformer in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#makeaplanearcadegameinunrealengine"&gt;Make a Plane Arcade Game in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildanrtsgamewithunrealengine"&gt;Build an RTS Game with Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#makeamini-survivalgameinunrealengine"&gt;Make a Mini-Survival Game in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#builda25dfarmingrpgwithunrealengine"&gt;Build a 2.5D Farming RPG with Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#createaturn-basedminirpginunrealengine"&gt;Create a Turn-Based Mini RPG in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtounrealenginegamedevelopment"&gt;Intro to Unreal Engine Game Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#discovergameaudioforunrealengine"&gt;Discover Game Audio for Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#completeunrealenginecpluspluscourse_buildanfps"&gt;The Complete Unreal Engine C++ Course - Build an FPS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtogamedesign"&gt;Intro to Game Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#explorestorytellingforgames"&gt;Explore Storytelling for Games&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtoriggingmodelsinblender"&gt;Intro to Rigging Models in Blender&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="unrealenginemini-projects2025edition"&gt;&lt;a id="unrealenginemini-projects2025edition" href="https://youtu.be/J2cgZ1psueY"&gt;Unreal Engine Mini-Projects&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build four beginner-friendly Unreal Engine mini-games!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Unreal Engine empowers creators to bring imaginative ideas to life, making it a cornerstone tool across all genres. In this course, you’ll build a set of four mini-projects exploring concepts like UIs, physics, and core programming tenets with real-world techniques that strengthen your grasp of the editor. The practical skills you gain will give you the confidence to take the next step in your Unreal Engine journey - whether you want to build RPGs, walking simulators, FPS games, or something else.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manipulate actor properties with scripting&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Utilize loops for mass object spawning&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Build a game based on physics&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Develop an interactive UI&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Connect player input to game mechanics&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Apply Unreal best practices throughout&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="learn3dmodelingwithblenderfromscratchnewedition2024"&gt;&lt;a id="learn3dmodelingwithblenderfromscratchnewedition2024" href="https://youtu.be/LKgbxcx0xIc"&gt;Learn 3D Modeling with Blender from Scratch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master the foundations of Blender and 3D modeling!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;3D modeling, the process of creating digital 3D objects, is a robust field of study with real-world applications for animation, game development, and more. In this course, you'll explore the free and open-source Blender software and learn the fundamental techniques for manipulating meshes and creating custom assets. These skills will form the basis for expanding your 3D modeling skills and open up opportunities to create unique assets for your projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Understand how 3D objects work&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Move, rotate, and scale objects&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Edit vertices, edges, and faces&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Work with Blender's modifiers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Apply materials to meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Export models for other programs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="createaracinggameinunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="createaracinggameinunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/Is4wgmFW9OQ"&gt;Create a Racing Game in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Make an arcade-style racing game in Unreal Engine!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether stylized or hyper-realistic, racing games are a popular genre due to their all-ages nature and easy-to-understand mechanics. In this course, you'll build a racing game while learning how to set up a car and a track that can manage laps. These techniques will give you the foundations to expand any sort of racing game and gain a deeper understanding of Blueprints techniques for vehicles in general.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Implement a race track environment&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add inputs suited to vehicles&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set up a race car&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Detect racing progress&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Control UIs and win conditions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rig additional cars in Blender&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="uiuxforgamedesign"&gt;&lt;a id="uiuxforgamedesign" href="https://youtu.be/f0tBF6qfoMc"&gt;UI/UX for Game Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Discover UI and UX design principles for games!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The user interface (UI) and user experience (UX) play a critical role in communicating information to players and creating smooth, interactive gameplay. In this course, you'll build a UI/UX mockup for a mobile game while exploring design methodologies and wireframing techniques. These techniques will provide you new ways to approach UI/UX game design and to meaningfully apply iterative design to optimize your game's experience.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Understand users with user stories&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create definitive design criteria&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Utilize wireframes for mockups&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Apply common design conventions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Test and iterate design choices&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Recognize design processes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="first-personexplorationgameinunrealengine2026edition"&gt;&lt;a id="first-personexplorationgameinunrealengine2026edition" href="https://youtu.be/5qPwFmXwG8Y"&gt;First-Person Exploration Game in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build a fully-fledged first-person exploration game using Unreal Engine!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;First-person exploration games captivate players by immersing them in interactive worlds, where storytelling and discovery are at the core of the experience. In this course, you’ll develop a modular first-person exploration game inside Unreal Engine, mastering key systems that empower you to craft compelling puzzles, environments, and interactive stories. By the end, you’ll possess reusable tools and in-depth techniques to bring a wide range of first-person games to life.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set up a first-person controller&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Develop versatile interaction systems&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create dynamic door and object logic&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Display info boxes for storytelling&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Implement Blueprints for rapid iteration&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Integrate assets for immersive worlds&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildacompletestealthgamewithunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="buildacompletestealthgamewithunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/jEVMwL6zCh4"&gt;Build a Complete Stealth Game with Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create a fully-fledged 3D stealth game!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Stealth gameplay is a cornerstone of modern action and adventure games, known for its tense strategies and immersive experiences. In this course, you'll build a complete stealth combat game in Unreal Engine, focusing on advanced enemy AI and dynamic stealth mechanics. With these skills, you'll be ready to specialize further in AI-driven design and tackle complex, real-world Unreal Engine projects in multiple genres.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Design advanced enemy patrol systems&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement field of view mechanics&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Integrate real-time sound detection&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Build stealth and combat gameplay&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up character and enemy animations&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Construct game levels efficiently&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtomultiplayerinunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="introtomultiplayerinunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/y6V-63fOM1U"&gt;Intro to Multiplayer in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Discover how to add multiplayer to your Unreal Engine games!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Multiplayer is a highly in-demand feature that can greatly enhance player experiences or completely define the gameplay. In this course, you'll create a multiplayer point-collecting game while exploring the fundamentals of how multiplayer works in Unreal Engine - which can be applied to any Unreal project.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Understand basic networking &amp;amp; RPCs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Explore Unreal settings for multiplayer&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Control inputs and players per device&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Render player states across computers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Manage one-time pickups&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Update UIs across players&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="developaclassicshootemupwithunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="developaclassicshootemupwithunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/x4PjGp_WGsQ"&gt;Develop a Classic Shoot 'em up with Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build a 3D arcade shooter from start to finish in Unreal Engine!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Shoot ‘em ups are a timeless genre that has vastly influenced and shaped the landscape of action games. In this course, you’ll create your own shoot ‘em up in Unreal Engine while learning player controls, dynamic enemy spawning, collision systems, and interactive UI development. These practical, multifaceted skills can be used not just for building shoot 'em ups, but also for exploring new game genres with Unreal.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Build player movement and shooting logic&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Design modular enemy-spawning systems&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement precise collision detection&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Integrate dynamic audio and SFX&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create visual polish with particles&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Develop a real-time game UI&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="makeahorrorgameinunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="makeahorrorgameinunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/a08sixMfD3M"&gt;Make a Horror Game in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn how to make fully-fledged horror games in Unreal Engine!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Horror games are a flexible genre that offers developers unique opportunities to explore spooky aesthetics and atmospheres. Through this course, you'll build a horror game where the player must avoid a monster and collect items - all while managing their flashlight's battery power. The techniques featured here will allow you to unlock level design suitable for the horror game genre that can easily be applied to any project.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Design horror levels and lighting&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement a flashlight object&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create a player-chasing monster&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up collectables&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Control gameplay flow &amp;amp; UIs&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Enhance games with SFX&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="createafully-fledgedbullethellinunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="createafully-fledgedbullethellinunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/qNTdx7J4yNk"&gt;Create a Fully-Fledged Bullet Hell in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build a bullet hell game from start to finish in Unreal Engine!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bursting across screens with relentless action, bullet hell games are a thrilling staple of game development that push technical and creative boundaries. In this course, you’ll create a fully-fledged 3D bullet hell, mastering real-world techniques essential for managing enemies, optimizing gameplay, and delivering an engaging experience. By the end, you’ll have a robust project to showcase your Unreal Engine skills and the confidence to create action-oriented titles of your own.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set up Unreal’s Enhanced Input System&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Design player and enemy characters&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Implement advanced enemy state machines&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Control spawning algorithms&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Apply dynamic VFX and lighting&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Build responsive UI systems&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildatowerdefensegameinunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="buildatowerdefensegameinunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/SjuCFNM_hZY"&gt;Build a Tower Defense Game in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create a complete tower defense game in Unreal Engine!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Tower defense games combine the best of strategy and creativity, making them a favorite among gamers. In this course, you’ll build a tower defense game while exploring character blueprints, animations, tile maps, and scalable game mechanics to develop a polished project that demonstrates the power of 2.5D gameplay. Mastering these skills will help you create modular tower defense games and expand into more advanced Unreal Engine projects.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create modular character blueprints&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up animations for all states&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Design and decorate game levels&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement tower defense behavior and logic&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Develop a point system for strategic decisions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Combine 2D and 3D gameplay features&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="developacompleteinfiniterunnerinunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="developacompleteinfiniterunnerinunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/nUPHfVHd8BY"&gt;Develop a Complete Infinite Runner in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build a fully-fledged, 2.5D infinite runner for Unreal Engine!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Infinite runners are a cornerstone genre, offering endless replay value and a deep dive into modular, dynamic gameplay systems. In this course, you'll develop a complete infinite runner game from start to finish, mastering core foundations in animation, level generation, and more. These skills will not only give you essential skills for infinite runners, but provide you with fundamentals that can easily be applied to roguelikes, platformers, and many other genres.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create moveable actors&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Animate player characters with multiple states&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Place enemies and collectibles programmatically&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Build modular, expandable level scenarios&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manage scoring systems and game overs&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Combine 2D sprites with 3D environments&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="makeafully-fledged3dplatformerwithunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="makeafully-fledged3dplatformerwithunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/oIwwn5bl2ek"&gt;Make a Fully-Fledged 3D Platformer with Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bring your own 3D platformer to life with Unreal Engine from start to finish!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;3D platformers stand as classics of the gaming world, celebrated for their dynamic movement and multi-layered levels. Through this course, you’ll craft a fully-fledged 3D platformer from the ground up, building core features like animated players, collectibles, enemies, and seamless level progression. These skills will not only deepen your understanding of Unreal Engine, but give you the confidence to design original platforming experiences or evolve existing ones.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set up a 3D player controller&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Implement movement, jumping, and animations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create interconnected, multi-stage levels&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add collectibles that track player progress&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Design enemy behavior and obstacles&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Develop in-game menus and UI&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="developa2dplatformerinunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="developa2dplatformerinunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/R9pV5UdXNm0"&gt;Develop a 2D Platformer in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn how to make 2D games using Unreal Engine!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;2D remains an immensely popular art style for games and can be found across a multitude of genres - especially platformers. In this course, you'll build a 2D platformer while learning how to work with tilemaps, players, enemies, and more using Unreal Engine and a 2D art style. These skills will allow you to unlock Unreal Engine's capabilities for 2D games and give you the foundations to work with any kind of platformer project.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create multiple platforming levels&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up player &amp;amp; enemy movement&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement collectible coins&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Work with UI systems&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Control game overs &amp;amp; progression&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Enhance aesthetics with art &amp;amp; audio&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="makeaplanearcadegameinunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="makeaplanearcadegameinunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/S5ObvZS12U4"&gt;Make a Plane Arcade Game in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Make a plane flying game in Unreal Engine!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Planes are a popular subject matter for many genres thanks to their unique and inspiring ability to fly in real life. You'll learn to build an arcade-style game where players must fly through rings to increase their score. These techniques will provide you with new structures for tracking scores, implementing movement, and more for your Unreal projects.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Process inputs&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Script pitch, roll, and yaw&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Control plane acceleration&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Build a ring-based course&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Track scoring with UI&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create 3D environments with Quixel&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildanrtsgamewithunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="buildanrtsgamewithunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/c1baBELiWTY"&gt;Build an RTS Game with Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master the fundamentals for RTS games in Unreal Engine!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Real-time strategy games combine the best of quick action and thought-provoking decisions - making them very popular. You'll explore core strategy mechanics including unit movement, basic combat, and more while building a small RTS project in Unreal. The techniques here will provide you with base mechanics that can be expanded or used in other strategy-style games!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Make playable units&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement simple combat&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Navigate with Nav Mesh&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Provide UI-feedback for input&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create RTS-appropriate cameras&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Improve level aesthetics&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="makeamini-survivalgameinunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="makeamini-survivalgameinunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/fG-Jy6bghy0"&gt;Make a Mini-Survival Game in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create a mini-survival game using Unreal Engine!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Survival games are a staple of the industry with a unique ability to work in just about any setting. Through this course, you'll explore the most fundamental of survival game player mechanics, as well as how to set up environments for those players. These techniques will allow you to adapt any project for the survival game genre with universal concepts that can easily be expanded to suit your needs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Craft terrain with Quixel&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Deal with user inputs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Implement player movement&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Control player "needs"&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Construct companion UIs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Make day-night cycles&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="builda25dfarmingrpgwithunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="builda25dfarmingrpgwithunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/3lDdT_b7CuE"&gt;Build a 2.5D Farming RPG with Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build a farming simulation game using Unreal Engine!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Farming simulation games offer players the chance to create, grow, and manage their own virtual farms, combining strategic planning with RPG-like gameplay to create an immersive experience. In this course, you’ll develop a 2.5D farming simulation from scratch – covering core features like player controls, farming mechanics, and a basic economic system. These skills will give you the tools you need to create more complex farming games and expand into other genres with Unreal Engine.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set up player movement and inputs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add interactive farming mechanics&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create a grid-based map with Blueprints&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Implement simple game currency systems&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Develop skip-time logic for crop growth&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add SFX and game feel polishing&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="createaturn-basedminirpginunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="createaturn-basedminirpginunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/8uAc2Jd4LBA"&gt;Create a Turn-Based Mini RPG in Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build a turn-based mini RPG from start to finish in Unreal Engine!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Turn-based battle systems offer strategic depth for creating immersive and engaging RPG experiences. In this course, you'll construct a 2.5D, turn-based RPG featuring magic spells, healing, and more - all with simple UI controls. These skills will empower you to expand into more sophisticated RPG development and master class construction using Unreal's Blueprints.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create dynamic player/enemy classes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Develop turn-based game logic&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Use UI for character control&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Build a 2.5D game world&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Work with projectiles and healing&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add game juice with SFX&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtounrealenginegamedevelopment"&gt;&lt;a id="introtounrealenginegamedevelopment" href="https://youtu.be/HS7pQuF5tbA"&gt;Intro to Unreal Engine Game Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Take your first step into Unreal Engine game development!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Unreal Engine stands at the forefront of professional game development, powering everything from breakout indie hits to AAA blockbusters. Through this course, you’ll get hands-on with the Unreal Editor, master core mechanics, and build simple interactive examples using the Blueprints Visual Scripting system. With these skills, you'll unlock the foundation to craft immersive experiences and pursue more advanced Unreal Engine projects.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Navigate the Unreal Editor interface&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Work with actors and game objects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up and modify level settings&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement realistic physics and lighting&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Build gameplay with visual scripting&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Handle user interaction&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="discovergameaudioforunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="discovergameaudioforunrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/RdX3VtQKf1I"&gt;Discover Game Audio for Unreal Engine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Explore how to use audio for Unreal Engine projects!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Audio can play a vital role in games by creating atmosphere, providing players with feedback, and giving an immersive sense of presence. Through this course, you'll experiment with playing sounds in Unreal Engine and adjusting available settings to make your audio more dynamic. These skills will allow you to enhance the game feel of your Unreal Engine projects and work with background music, SFX, and more.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Alter sound attenuation&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Play background music&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Make dynamic SFX with randomness&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Give characters footsteps&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Add various types of ambient sounds&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Trigger audio based on actions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="completeunrealenginecpluspluscourse_buildanfps"&gt;&lt;a id="completeunrealenginecpluspluscourse_buildanfps" href="https://youtu.be/SwtkRgvzDvM"&gt;The Complete Unreal Engine C++ Course - Build an FPS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Develop a complete first-person shooter in Unreal Engine using C++ programming!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;First-person shooters are popular for their performance and interactivity, and C++ empowers developers to create them efficiently. In this course, you'll build a fully-fledged FPS survival game with Unreal Engine and C++ while learning to create enemy waves, pickups, and other interactive game elements. These advanced techniques will enable you to leverage more customized FPS features with C++ and approach Unreal Engine development in a whole new way.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create and program enemy classes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Implement wave-based enemy systems&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add various types of pickups&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Manage game environments effectively&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Facilitate cross-class communication&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Code dynamic weapon systems&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtogamedesign"&gt;&lt;a id="introtogamedesign" href="https://youtu.be/FdhFX3SCVOc"&gt;Intro to Game Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Discover how the core concepts of game design can help you to create fun and intuitive games!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Game design is a fundamental process needed when creating any game - from the smallest platformer to the largest MMORPG. In this course, you'll start mastering the foundations of game design by examining each core component and how they apply to real-world games. By the end, you'll understand both why game design is important and, more crucially, how to apply the concepts to your own games and create a stunning portfolio.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Plan a game around a core mechanic or experience&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Engage players by providing tangible goals&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Structure game actions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Guide players through the game&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Understand game feel and its effects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Show players how to play in different ways&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="explorestorytellingforgames"&gt;&lt;a id="explorestorytellingforgames" href="https://youtu.be/s3VT2g0_LCI"&gt;Explore Storytelling for Games&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Discover tips and techniques for designing game narratives! You'll learn by studying real games, and master a variety of methods for telling stories through characters, plots, mechanics, and more.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;No matter what type of games you want to build, the skills you'll learn will help to make your games more immersive and engaging for your players.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Understand technical story design&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create compelling protagonists &amp;amp; antagonists&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Base your story on a three-act structure&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use game-based methods to convey your story&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Incorporate interactive, choice-based storytelling&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Advance the story with quests&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtoriggingmodelsinblender"&gt;&lt;a id="introtoriggingmodelsinblender" href="https://youtu.be/tVccjBYF2Ic"&gt;Intro to Rigging Models in Blender&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Prepare your 3D models for animation by learning the fundamentals of rigging!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Rigging is a key animation technique that involves creating a skeletal armature to manipulate a 3D mesh and streamline the animation process. In this course, you'll discover everything required for rigging - from setting up the "bones" to weight painting and controlling which parts of the mesh are affected by each bone. By the end, you'll have the foundations you'll need to master rigging any kind of 3D model and expand your skills in creating custom assets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create bones to build an armature&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Connect your armature and 3D mesh&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Control affected vertices with weight painting&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Export rigged models&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Apply Mixamo animations to your models&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
