gt;Storyboard Assets Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#mohodebut125"&gt;Moho Debut 12.5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $25 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="clipstudiopaintproversion50_12monthlicense"&gt;&lt;a id="clipstudiopaintproversion50_12monthlicense" href="https://youtu.be/AheoJI0UEnM"&gt;Clip Studio Paint Pro Version 5.0 - 12 month license&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;CLIP STUDIO PAINT PRO, the world’s leading Comic and Manga creation software developed by Celsys Inc., delivers powerful art tools for professional artists and graphic illustrators alike. CLIP STUDIO PAINT PRO includes a large suite of familiar tools including pens, pencils, erasers, rulers, pattern brushes and selection tools that are fully customizable. Sketching, inking, coloring and creating graphic illustrations, comics and manga has never been easier or more efficient!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ultimatebrushpack"&gt;&lt;a id="ultimatebrushpack" href="https://youtu.be/7LbDUB0_rJg"&gt;Ultimate Brush Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) &amp;amp; PHOTOSHOP Brush Pack is a professionally designed brush pack, created for use in CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) and PHOTOSHOP.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) &amp;amp; PHOTOSHOP Brush Pack is an amazing pack that includes a variety of brushes for everyone. Whether you're a digital artist, illustrator, comic artist, manga artist, professional or hobbyist, you will love this brush pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For your convenience, we have made these brushes available for both CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) &amp;amp; PHOTOSHOP. That way, you'll never miss a beat regardless of what application you're using.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;There are 200 brushes in the Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) &amp;amp; PHOTOSHOP Brush Pack. The Brush Pack includes 100 CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) brushes and 100 PHOTOSHOP brushes. The CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) brushes and PHOTOSHOP brushes are identical.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get professional results on your terms in either CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) or PHOTOSHOP.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) &amp;amp; PHOTOSHOP Brush Pack Includes the following brushes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 5 cloud - Create your own dreamy horizon with these cloud brushes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 5 crowd - Save time and expedite your backgrounds with these crowd brushes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 5 spray - Create amazing textures with these spray brushes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 5 trees &amp;amp; grass - Maximize your drawing time with tree and grass brushes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 15 inking - Create amazing lines with these natural inking brushes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 15 painterly &amp;amp; watercolor &amp;amp; oil &amp;amp; bristle &amp;amp; acrylic &amp;amp; sponge - Realistic and natural brushes for everyone.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 15 pastel &amp;amp; charcoal - Dry brushes for that organic look and feel.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 15 penciling &amp;amp; sketching - Get started with you masterpiece with these natural brushes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 20 splatter - Add realism to any artwork.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;***************************************************&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;** Installation Instructions ** &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;***************************************************&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) Brushes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please make sure you've installed CLIP STUDIO PAINT PRO or EX (Manga Studio 5 or 5 EX) on your computer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Simply add the brushes (.sut files) to CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) via the Sub Tool Menu &amp;gt; Import Sub Tool&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;---------------------------------------------------&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;PHOTOSHOP Brushes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please make sure you've installed PHOTOSHOP on your computer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Here are 2 ways that you can add brushes directly to PHOTOSHOP:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Drag the brushes (.ABR files) directly into your PHOTOSHOP window&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;or&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Go to Edit &amp;gt; Presets &amp;gt; Preset Manager, select brushes from the dropdown menu, and then add your brushes using the "Load" button&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;***************************************************&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;** System Requirements **&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;***************************************************&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;CLIP STUDIO PAINT PRO (Manga Studio 5) or higher, CLIP STUDIO PAINT EX (Manga Studio 5 EX) or higher.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;PHOTOSHOP CS 5 or higher (not tested on older versions of PHOTOSHOP)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Up to an additional 700 MB of free disk space recommended.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="superherobrushpack"&gt;&lt;a id="superherobrushpack" href="https://youtu.be/kfvGSt7X0LI"&gt;Superhero Brush Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Super Hero CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) &amp;amp; PHOTOSHOP Brush Pack is a professionally designed brush pack, created for use in CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) and PHOTOSHOP.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Super Hero CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) &amp;amp; PHOTOSHOP Brush Pack will help you defeat all evil! Your super hero illustrations will be more powerful than ever! By the way, it's also an absolutely amazing brush pack for all illustrators, digital, comic and manga artists as well. These brushes were created with the professional artist in mind and includes brushes for both CLIP STUDIO PAINT and PHOTOSHOP! You will absolutely love this brush pack!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For your convenience, we have made these brushes available for both CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) &amp;amp; PHOTOSHOP. That way, you'll never miss a beat regardless of what application you're using.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;There are 204 brushes in the Super Hero CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) &amp;amp; PHOTOSHOP Brush Pack. The Brush Pack includes 102 CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) brushes and 102 PHOTOSHOP brushes. The CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) brushes and PHOTOSHOP brushes are identical.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get professional results on your terms in either CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) or PHOTOSHOP.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Super Hero CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) &amp;amp; PHOTOSHOP Brush Pack Includes the following brushes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 8 painterly&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 6 watercolor&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 4 bristle&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 15 pencils&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 11 pastels &amp;amp; chalks&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 11 inks&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 4 crowd patterns&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 6 cloud patterns&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 11 foliage patterns&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 26 splatters&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;***************************************************&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;** Installation Instructions ** &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;***************************************************&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) Brushes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please make sure you've installed CLIP STUDIO PAINT PRO or EX (Manga Studio 5 or 5 EX) on your computer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Simply add the brushes (.sut files) to CLIP STUDIO PAINT (Manga Studio) via the Sub Tool Menu &amp;gt; Import Sub Tool&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;---------------------------------------------------&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;PHOTOSHOP Brushes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please make sure you've installed PHOTOSHOP on your computer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Here are 2 ways that you can add brushes directly to PHOTOSHOP:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Drag the brushes (.ABR files) directly into your PHOTOSHOP window&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;or&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Go to Edit &amp;gt; Presets &amp;gt; Preset Manager, select brushes from the dropdown menu, and then add your brushes using the "Load" button&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;***************************************************&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;** System Requirements **&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;***************************************************&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;CLIP STUDIO PAINT PRO (Manga Studio 5) or higher, CLIP STUDIO PAINT EX (Manga Studio 5 EX) or higher.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;PHOTOSHOP CS 5 or higher (not tested on older versions of PHOTOSHOP)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Up to an additional 400 MB of free disk space recommended.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="comicbrushpack"&gt;&lt;a id="comicbrushpack" href="https://youtu.be/-ioAc9Kx3A0"&gt;Comic Brush Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Comic Brush Pack is a professionally designed brush pack by Ryan Cardinal, created for use in CLIP STUDIO PAINT.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Comic Brush Pack is an amazing pack that includes a variety of Comic Brushes for everyone. Whether you're a digital artist, illustrator, comic artist, manga artist, professional or hobbyist, you will love this brush pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;There are 100 Brushes in the Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Comic Brush Pack. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get professional results on your terms in CLIP STUDIO PAINT.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Comic Brush Pack Includes the following:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 7 Bokeh Brushes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 7 Cityscape Brushes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 7 Crowd Brushes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 7 Dry Brushes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 9 Foliage Brushes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 7 Glitter Brushes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 7 Landscape Brushes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 7 Marker Brushes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 7 Pencil Brushes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 7 Rocks/Rubble/Debris Brushes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 7 Smoke Brushes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 7 Snow/Rain Brushes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 7 Space Brushes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 7 Watercolor Brushes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;***************************************************&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;** Installation Instructions ** &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;***************************************************&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;CLIP STUD