can be used in any other painting program.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT 3D Poses Pack is a professionally designed pack, created for use in CLIP STUDIO PAINT.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT 3D Poses Pack is an amazing pack that includes a variety of 3D Poses for everyone. Whether you're a digital artist, illustrator, comic artist, manga artist, professional or hobbyist, you will love this pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;These are poses that are difficult to sketch from scratch, but with the Ultimate 3D Poses Pack as your reference material, you can sketch your hero or heroine in a wide variety of positions quickly and easily.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;There are 100 3D Poses in the Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT 3D Poses Pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get professional results on your terms in CLIP STUDIO PAINT.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT 3D Poses Pack Includes the following:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;34 Fighting Poses&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;27 Gesture Poses&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;12 Ground or Sitting Poses&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;09 Idle Poses&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;18 Running or Jumping Poses&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;System Requirements:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;CLIP STUDIO PAINT DEBUT, PRO or EX.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Up to an additional 300 MB of free disk space recommended.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="speechbubblespack"&gt;&lt;a id="speechbubblespack" href="https://youtu.be/R3UAjV__wjE"&gt;Speech Bubbles Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ultimate Speech Bubbles Pack for CLIP STUDIO PAINT&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Want unique speech bubbles for your comic artwork? The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Speech Bubbles Pack includes 200 speech bubbles, including frame, multi, polygonal, single, special border special, spiky and though bubbles. Comes as flat transparent image files that can be used anywhere.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Speech Bubbles Pack is a professionally designed speech bubbles pack, created for use in CLIP STUDIO PAINT.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Speech Bubbles Pack is an amazing pack that includes a variety of speech bubbles for everyone. Whether you're a digital artist, illustrator, comic artist, manga artist, professional or hobbyist, you will love this speech bubble pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;There are 200 speech bubbles in the Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Speech Bubbles Pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get professional results on your terms in CLIP STUDIO PAINT.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Speech Bubbles Pack Includes the following bubbles:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;19 Frame Bubbles&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;27 Multi Bubbles&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;22 Polygonal Bubbles&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;41 Single Bubbles&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;20 Special Border Bubbles&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;26 Special Bubbles&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;24 Spiky Bubbles&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;20 Thought Bubbles&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;System Requirements:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;CLIP STUDIO PAINT DEBUT, PRO or EX.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Up to an additional 150 MB of free disk space recommended.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="comicandmangapanelframespack"&gt;&lt;a id="comicandmangapanelframespack" href="https://youtu.be/8N1ULvJhdlw"&gt;Comic &amp; Manga Panel Frames Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ultimate Comic &amp;amp; Manga Panel Frames Pack&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Comic &amp;amp; Manga Panels Pack is a professionally designed panel frames pack, created for use in CLIP STUDIO PAINT.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Comic &amp;amp; Manga Panels Pack is an amazing pack that includes a variety of Comic &amp;amp; Manga Panels for everyone. Whether you're a digital artist, illustrator, comic artist, manga artist, professional or hobbyist, you will love this panel frame pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;There are 100 Comic &amp;amp; Manga Panels in the Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Comic &amp;amp; Manga Panels Pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get professional results on your terms in CLIP STUDIO PAINT.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Comic &amp;amp; Manga Panels Pack Includes the following:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;27 Angle Panel Frames (with and without panel frame gutters)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;6 Blockage Panel Frames (with and without panel frame gutters)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;28 Boxes Panel Frames (with and without panel frame gutters)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;11 Inset Panel Frames (with and without panel frame gutters)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;15 Overlap Panel Frames (with and without panel frame gutters)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;13 Simple Panel Frames (with and without panel frame gutters)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;System Requirements:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;CLIP STUDIO PAINT DEBUT, PRO or EX.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Up to an additional 1 GB of free disk space recommended.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="storyboardassetspack"&gt;&lt;a id="storyboardassetspack" href="https://youtu.be/DV4jb_61o2k"&gt;Storyboard Assets Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ultimate Storyboard Assets Pack For CLIP STUDIO PAINT&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Need to convey a story or concept quickly? The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Story Board Assets Pack includes over 400 drawn out items. The pack includes items such as portraits of people, hand gestures, video game assets, electronics, icons, stationaries, signs, food, animals, etc. Comes as flat transparent PSD files that can be used anywhere.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Storyboard Assets Pack is professionally designed and created for use in CLIP STUDIO PAINT.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Storyboard Assets Pack is an amazing pack that includes a variety of storyboard elements for everyone. Whether you're a digital artist, illustrator, comic artist, manga artist, professional or hobbyist, you will love this pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;There are 400 storyboard elements in the Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Storyboard Assets Pack.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get professional results on your terms in CLIP STUDIO PAINT.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate CLIP STUDIO PAINT Storyboard Assets Pack Includes the following assets:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;14 Portraits&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;17 Gestures&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;21 Hands&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;18 Videogames&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;13 Electronics&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;37 Stationeries&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;27 Icons&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;30 Roadside/Signs&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;20 Japanese Decorations&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;17 Fashion&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;20 Treasures&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;20 Furniture/Appliances&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;22 Food&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;49 Dessert/Snack&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;18 Animals&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;49 Decorations/Toys/Gifts&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;24 Kitchen/Bathroom&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;System Requirements:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;CLIP STUDIO PAINT DEBUT, PRO or EX.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Up to an additional 50 MB of free disk space recommended.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="mohodebut125"&gt;&lt;a id="mohodebut125" href="https://youtu.be/jBPMNm5xc7I"&gt;Moho Debut 12.5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Moho™ Debut is your complete animation program for creating 2D movies, cartoons, stop motion or cut out animations. Create your own desktop animated shorts in the style of Disney Animation Studios, Nickelodeon Animation Studios, Cartoon Network Studios, South Park Studios or use it to produce animations for film, video, commercials or streaming over the web. Get started quickly with the Beginner’s Mode. Create your own custom characters using the built-in Character Wizard and convert your existing paper drawings to ready-to-animate vector images with one click. Draw your own artwork using built-in brushes, import digital photos, add sound and video, and choose from pre-designed characters or create your own and make them talk using integrated lip-synching. The revolutionary bone rigging system makes animating fast and an efficient alternative to tedious traditional animation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Top Bullet Points:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create your own cartoons and animations!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Bone-based Animation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Vector-based Animation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Cut out Animation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Simulate Stop Motion Animation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Key Features&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bone Rigging&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;The revolutionary bone rigging system makes animating fast and an efficient alternative to tedious frame-by-frame animation. You can easily add a skeleton to any image by simple point and click, and then bring it to life, and keep your project organized with the sequencer and timeline in Moho.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enhanced Vector Based Drawing Tools&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;With enhanced vector based drawing tools, including a variety of brush styles and the ability to import scanned drawings and images, you can create your own characters and objects in Moho Debut 12.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Character Wizard&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;The built-in Character Wizard lets you quickly design your own characters complete with walk cycles. Creating your own animations has never been faster or easier.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Beginner’s Mode&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;The Beginner’s Mode guides you through using the key tools in Moho so you can start creating animated videos and shorts right away.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Auto-Freeze Keys&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;With Auto-Freeze Keys turned on, when you move a bone, all other bones in the rig will be keyed. This ensures body parts only move when intended. No more floating bones!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Content Library Included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Choose from a library of content including ready-to-use characters, props, scenes, stock audio and video clips, scatter brushes and more.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Image Vectorizer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;The Image Vectorizer allows you to bring your existing sketches and image files to life by converting them to ready-to-animate vector drawings with the click of a button.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Integrated Audio Recording&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;The integrated audio recording feature lets you record your own sound clips right within Moho and sync them to your animated characters using automatic lip-syncing.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Easier Lip Syncing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;In version 12, Lip syncing and other frame by frame animations are even easier to achieve! All Switch Layers can be viewed and keyed with the Select Switch Window. Having a visual interface speeds up animation tasks!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;New! Pin Bones&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;With Pin Bones add one point bones to alter, move and reshape assets in fun new ways. Combine with traditional bones for more complex animations. Works with both vectors and images!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
