      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 18:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/79875519196c880e9f128e582b428e5ff74802c0.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=ca80c79a9591220a40d1710bff9b8de2"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8757794275aa2cf4cbe2b96f55ea46a27e7547d5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=6fac8b28dee6727cc0cb2f703935e8a6"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Gorgeous vistas created by you&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#landscapegroundpack_naturemanufacture"&gt;Landscape Ground Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#wintergroundpack_naturemanufacture"&gt;Winter ground Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#parkphotoscannedassets_naturemanufacture"&gt;Park Photo Scanned Assets&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#iceworld_naturemanufacture"&gt;Ice World&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#natureset_naturemanufacture"&gt;Nature Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#pbrgraveyardandnatureset20"&gt;PBR Graveyard and Nature Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#environmentset_naturemanufacture"&gt;Environment Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt30"&gt;Pay $30 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#coastanddunes-environmentset"&gt;Coast &amp; Dunes- Environment Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#lavaandvolcanoenvironmentset"&gt;Lava &amp; Volcano Environment Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#mountain_environmentset_naturemanufacture"&gt;Mountain - Environment Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#forest_environmentset_naturemanufacture"&gt;Forest - Environment Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#meadow_environmentset_naturemanufacture"&gt;Meadow - Environment Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="landscapegroundpack_naturemanufacture"&gt;&lt;a id="landscapegroundpack_naturemanufacture"&gt;Landscape Ground Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/88f3843da34c4b1e446a124724c42bcb635cc74b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6a88dc2361cf8a3ea42fbf8fba40dfb1"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Choose between different ground proposals that will give you the right base for your environment. Whether you want to create a swamp area, a green forest, or a rocky mountain terrain, various propositions from our library of landscape ground will provide you with the necessary materials to choose from. Pack contains 163 ground/floor textures in 43 materials. In the pack, you will also find 4 example landscapes 4x4km in size. Tilled textures are useful for every ground shader. High resolution 2048x2048 guarantees good quality, textures look good at lower resolutions too and are perfect for advanced ground shaders with a height blending feature. They work at HDRP, URP and Built-in render, at terrain and mesh.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="wintergroundpack_naturemanufacture"&gt;&lt;a id="wintergroundpack_naturemanufacture"&gt;Winter ground Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/58763260e324afd77c7bb28f3310500716f28c07.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=830e0dc1bf56aac92087e2494f53de85"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Enjoy the winter landscape that you can easily shape in your design thanks to our materials. Different options of snow cover allow you to create a variety of interpretations of the area - from covering all terrain snow layers to light cover on the grass. In the winter ground pack, you will find textures such as mud, snow, rocks, stones, dirty ground, grass, path, road, and dirty snow. Everything is in PBR and physically accurate. In this textures pack, you will find ground textures, that are perfect for terrain shader. All materials contain height maps for advanced tessellation or parallax shading, so you will get a better effect if you need it. Maskmaps with: metallic, ambient occlusion, height, and smoothness textures give great results in PBR rendering.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="parkphotoscannedassets_naturemanufacture"&gt;&lt;a id="parkphotoscannedassets_naturemanufacture" href="https://youtu.be/bhth2BBHuK4"&gt;Park Photo Scanned Assets&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a355b5286a679619e27212a02b06b0b76b2285c2.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9e409162e5eaca758119c96a8ba6e5a8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create a park that will become an oasis of greenery and nature in a city landscape or other urbanized environment. Wooden benches, decorative lamps, fences, or an artistic fountain - these and many more necessary park elements can be found in our pack. Materials in various variants of use will create a charming composition of the recreational area. This pack contains carefully optimized, modular, atlased photo-scanned and sculpted assets. LOD's are highly optimized - triangles range from 7/4k to even 8 triangles which makes them very cheap to render. Pack contains 68 modular prefabs, 47 models with 4-5 LOD's ( almost 200 meshes), 18 texture atlases (68 textures - Albedo, Smoothness, AO, Metalic, Normal), and 12 ground texture sets (60 maps).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="iceworld_naturemanufacture"&gt;&lt;a id="iceworld_naturemanufacture" href="https://youtu.be/C2-YVWzJ2Rc"&gt;Ice World&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Compose a terrain based on the motive of ice that will allow you to recreate an environment of frozen land, perfectly creating the atmosphere of winter and icy areas like frozen lakes or rivers. The pack is also a huge library of ice textures and shader variants. Many options give you the ability to control almost every aspect of ice. Lake and river variants behave like water so you can control water depth, shelf colors, blend with objects, and ice depth. Shader perfectly blends with the terrain. The asset contains: over 180 Ice materials (544 with all variants of shader), 88 Ice textures, tutorial demo scenes, a frozen river demo scene&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="natureset_naturemanufacture"&gt;&lt;a id="natureset_naturemanufacture"&gt;Nature Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/de3c53552182b8e73bb9d69402b8b9ec5b923c80.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c78f6c8c210fc1da872e8d9f26e56d0e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Nature Set is a group of environmental assets. Pack contains grass, trees, rock models, and landscape ground materials such as rock, mud, stone, asphalt, grass, sand, litter, and leaves. All models and textures were made from 10x10k photo material.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-6 tree models; -5 big rocks; -5 small stones; -1 stone wall; -7 grass models; -84 landscape textures (28 sets);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="pbrgraveyardandnatureset20"&gt;&lt;a id="pbrgraveyardandnatureset20" href="https://youtu.be/CkYP2bor7gg"&gt;PBR Graveyard and Nature Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Graveyard asset is dedicated to creating a cemetery environment with interiors, and nature background. Thanks to these assets you can build a mystical and mysterious area full of details that will stand out in any project, giving a landscape a unique character. The content of this pack is a huge amount (over 2000) of modular, PBR, sculpted, and photo-scanned assets. All assets are high-quality optimized and atlased models with 3-4 LODs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Pack contains 350 prefabs (like in overview screenshots), 217 models (646 meshes with LODs), 329 textures (over 1000 maps), wall/ floor shader (a specular and metallic version that supports snow or moss cover).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="environmentset_naturemanufacture"&gt;&lt;a id="environmentset_naturemanufacture" href="https://youtu.be/8PKCdGpZH7I"&gt;Environment Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This pack contains a huge environment library of carefully optimized, atlased foliage assets. In our pack you will find:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• 8 fir trees (with few bark variants) • 7 poplar trees • 12 rocks (with auto-cover, UV-free, and standard variants) • 26 grass models • 47 ground materials: sand, wet ground, grass, moss, rocks, stones, roads, dirt, leaves, litter, grass, pebbles, roots • 2 trunks • 6 roots • Tesselated landscape material with UV mix function • Demo scene from the video&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With our assets, you can create nice-looking and fast forests or meadows. The pack includes normal and auto-covered materials for rocks, giving you the ability to blend them into the landscape.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt30"&gt;Pay $30 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="coastanddunes-environmentset"&gt;&lt;a id="coastanddunes-environmentset"&gt;Coast &amp; Dunes- Environment Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9babe40c19b43028e550286db22165b9c8d797ee.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0442f48eb4d70d6664b5a80000abed6f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Coast, Dunes, Desert, Dry, Beach, Island, Shoreline Environment with 1x1km demo scene, a huge library of 100% scanned assets, carefully optimized, atlases, LOD’ed, all textures are 4096x4096. Our materials and decals will bring better quality and simplify your workflow. Tilled scanned cliffs that are ready for use with splines; Landscape nanite properly, height-blended 8 layers shader; All files from the video are included in the asset&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="lavaandvolcanoenvironmentset"&gt;&lt;a id="lavaandvolcanoenvironmentset"&gt;Lava &amp; Volcano Environment Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/56335a672ff15e6f9f9df71c1a61bec6f5c8d5c6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7e9cdef813f0ee37c49019f20b53bbb1"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This pack is an Epic MegaGrants Recipient. Big lava environment library rocks and lava rivers that support landscape splines and the Unreal water plugin: lakes, rivers, shallow water simulation live and baked. With that pack, you can easily build a volcanic interior or exterior map. It's perfect for dugeons and caves where lava emission can light whole rooms. All meshes are in nanite and non-nanite versions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="mountain_environmentset_naturemanufacture"&gt;&lt;a id="mountain_environmentset_naturemanufacture" href="https://youtu.be/8qS9X1E5ke4"&gt;Mountain - Environment Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Massive 100% photoscanned foliage library, carefully optimized for mountain, forest, and landscape environments. This pack contains:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 448 meshes and blueprints for: trees, grass, plants, rocks, stones, branches, mushrooms, roots, cones, roots, etc - Materials that will bring better quality and simplify your workflow, - Height blended landscape materials (8 layers) with switches for UV mix, color mix, tesselation, highly optimized - Water materials for lakes and rivers with automatic waterfalls based on a surface slope with a tesselation option - Advanced rocks and objects materials with slope cover, planar, triplanar, and mask. - Road material with vertex color support - Splines for the road (with ground snap) and rivers.  - Rocks, slopes, roots with leaves, grass, moss, and sand cover blueprints - Pine trees: plants, small trees, small forest trees, medium, big, forest, and dead. - Map from the video: 800x800m size&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="forest_environmentset_naturemanufacture"&gt;&lt;a id="forest_environmentset_naturemanufacture" href="https://youtu.be/HWh6rxdLt5Y"&gt;Forest - Environment Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Huge foliage library for forest environment, landscape, and mountains optimized, 100% photo-scanned This pack contains:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Group of materials which will bring better quality and simplify your workflow, - Height blended landscape materials (8 layers) with switches for UV mix, color mix, and tesselation, highly optimized. - Advanced rocks and objects materials with automatic slope cover. Everything promised, planar, triplanar and mask, slope covers - Water materials for river/lake and swamp - Maps from the video are included in the asset - Rocks, slopes, and roots with leaves, grass, moss, and sand cover blueprints - In trees, you will find plants, small trees, small forest trees, medium, big standalone, forest, and dead. - Wooden construction set which helps you to build bridges and other wooden objects - Mushroom set to cover landscape and trunks - Set of roots and trunks, branches to make your forest look full of details.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="meadow_environmentset_naturemanufacture"&gt;&lt;a id="meadow_environmentset_naturemanufacture" href="https://youtu.be/OY4GJzkXJqY"&gt;Meadow - Environment Set&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;100% scanned and carefully optimized extensive foliage library. Perfect for meadows, forests, and wetlands. In the pack, you will find grass, rocks, cliffs, trees, trunks, landscape textures, bushes, flowers, swamp water, and a fence.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Foliage: 31 grass/flower types, 8 Bushes, 11 Trees (3 plants, 2 small, 1 medium, 2 big, 2 forests, 1 dead), 3 trunks, and 2 mushrooms - Rocks: 24 cliffs in parts and merged in bigger shapes, 20 rocks from small to big, Rocks and cliffs material contain a cover-by-angle function with a mask option. - Roads: Dirty and path road with a wet ground mix - Water: Swamp material which blends up to 2 detail types with water and clean water material - Landscape: 6 Low poly background landscapes, 9 ground texture sets: leaves, grass x 3, soil, wet soil, sand x2, needles. - Fences: 24 Fence system meshes (span and posts), 13 pre-built fence meshes, 19 fence construction sets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
