      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4e32b4785134697803c77332f14fc828632d19b4.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=703248df8d803d5b9fdc184ac12f57cb"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/574e5fa087943333274f4d55718023ab62f4f6f1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=960abf7224f14c1a5ac40ed82b7318ef"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Build modern developer skills&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn practical programming, cloud, and web development skills with the Professional Developer Pathways Bundle. Build real projects with Python, JavaScript, Rust, C++, C#, React, Next.js, Django, Flask, and more while exploring Git &amp; GitHub workflows, SQL databases, AWS and Azure developer skills, and modern AI-powered coding workflows with Claude Code. Pay what you want for a massive software development bundle from Zenva and support Alzheimer’s Research UK while building practical skills for today’s rapidly evolving developer landscape.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#javascriptprogrammingforbeginners"&gt;JavaScript Programming for Beginners&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtocodingwithpythonturtle"&gt;Intro to Coding with Python Turtle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#createyourfirstresponsivewebsite"&gt;Create Your First Responsive Website&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtosqlanddatabaseswithmysql"&gt;Intro to SQL and Databases with MySQL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#gitandgithub_versioncontrolandcollaboration"&gt;Git and Github - Version Control and Collaboration&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#microsoftazuredeveloperassociateaz-204_prepandpass"&gt;Microsoft Azure Developer Associate (AZ-204): Prep &amp; Pass&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#10practiceexamsformicrosoftazuredeveloperassociateaz-204"&gt;10 Practice Exams for Microsoft Azure Developer Associate (AZ-204)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#awscertifieddeveloperassociatedva-c02-prepypass"&gt;AWS Certified Developer - Associate (DVA-C02): Prep &amp; Pass&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#10practiceexamsforawscertifieddeveloper-associatedva-c02"&gt;10 Practice Exams for AWS Certified Developer - Associate (DVA-C02)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#agenticaiwithclaudecodeandmcp"&gt;Agentic AI with Claude Code &amp; MCP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bestpracticesforai-poweredcodingwithclaudecode"&gt;Best Practices for AI-Powered Coding with Claude Code&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtonextjsforwebappdevelopment"&gt;Intro to Next.js for Web App Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#nextjsproject_ai-poweredexpensetracker"&gt;Next.js Project - AI-Powered Expense Tracker&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildwebappswithreact19"&gt;Build Web Apps with React 19&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#javascriptmini-projects_languagelearninggame"&gt;JavaScript Mini-Projects - Language Learning Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#intermediatejavascript_buildadynamicdatatable"&gt;Intermediate JavaScript - Build a Dynamic Data Table&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#learnrustprogrammingforbeginners"&gt;Learn Rust Programming for Beginners&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#datastructureswithrust"&gt;Data Structures with Rust&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#rustparallelcomputingproject_imageprocessor"&gt;Rust Parallel Computing Project - Image Processor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#practicalrust_clitoolswithclapandindicatif"&gt;Practical Rust - CLI Tools with Clap and Indicatif&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#rustwebappproject_real-timevideobroadcasting"&gt;Rust Web App Project - Real-Time Video Broadcasting&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#completeintroductiontocplusplus"&gt;The Complete Introduction to C++&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtocplusplusdatastructures"&gt;Intro to C++ Data Structures&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#learnobject-orientedcplusplusbybuildingagame"&gt;Learn Object-Oriented C++ by Building a Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#comprehensiveintroductiontocprogramming"&gt;The Comprehensive Introduction to C# Programming&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtocomputergraphics"&gt;Intro to Computer Graphics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtodjangoforpythonwebappdevelopment2025edition"&gt;Intro to Django for Python Web App Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#pythonturtlemini-projects"&gt;Python Turtle Mini-Projects&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#pythondatastructuresforbeginners"&gt;Python Data Structures for Beginners&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#pandasproject_flightdataanalysis"&gt;Pandas Project - Flight Data Analysis&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#pythonimageprocessingwithpillow"&gt;Python Image Processing with Pillow&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#intermediatepython_virtualpetwithpygame"&gt;Intermediate Python - Virtual Pet with Pygame&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtoregularexpressionsinpython"&gt;Intro to Regular Expressions in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtoobject-orientedprogrammingwithpython"&gt;Intro to Object-Oriented Programming with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#pythonprojects_object-orientedgame"&gt;Python Projects - Object-Oriented Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtoalgorithmswithpython"&gt;Intro to Algorithms with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildawebapplicationwithflask"&gt;Build a Web Application with Flask&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtoflaskforwebappdevelopment"&gt;Intro to Flask for Web App Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#htmlfoundations"&gt;HTML Foundations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#cssfoundations"&gt;CSS Foundations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="javascriptprogrammingforbeginners"&gt;&lt;a id="javascriptprogrammingforbeginners" href="https://youtu.be/B4TjvFZbbrs"&gt;JavaScript Programming for Beginners&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/91a24af7ede9bf377860367f730bc0e4182bf17d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=bd6a4c79da6d5a04a8021f42f7fd1cf0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Considered a core pillar of web development and one of the world's most in-demand languages, JavaScript is used for everything from building websites to creating web apps, HTML5 games, mobile and Internet of Things (IoT) apps, and even space exploration technology.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;In this beginner-friendly course, you'll learn the basics of this lightweight, cross-platform scripting language, and master skills that allow you to add dynamic, interactive content to your websites and apps.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Store data as variables and arrays&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manipulate data with operators&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use conditionals to evaluate data for specific actions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Control program logic and flow with functions and loops&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up objects to store complex sets of data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Alter webpages with the DOM API&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtocodingwithpythonturtle"&gt;&lt;a id="introtocodingwithpythonturtle" href="https://youtu.be/YE7X082ZzU8"&gt;Intro to Coding with Python Turtle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Visualize code and master Python basics with Turtle!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Grasping core programming concepts is easier when you can see your code come to life. In this course, you'll explore coding fundamentals using the engaging Python Turtle graphics library, creating algorithms you can see and building a complete project visualizing our solar system. These foundational Python skills will empower you to tackle more complex programming challenges, master other integral coding principles, and discover how to build algorithms from scratch!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Master fundamental Python syntax&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Understand core algorithm concepts&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Draw shapes using Turtle&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Apply colors and fills&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Visualize algorithms on screen&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Build a visual solar system with code&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="createyourfirstresponsivewebsite"&gt;&lt;a id="createyourfirstresponsivewebsite" href="https://youtu.be/bJN0uDEuymc"&gt;Create Your First Responsive Website&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Discover how to build your first responsive website using only basic HTML and CSS!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;You'll learn by creating a company-style website featuring navigation, a banner, and grid-displayed services, and master techniques for automatically altering its appearance based on screen size.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Lay out various webpage sections with HTML&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use Chrome Developer Tools&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create a navigation bar with hover effects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Display widescreen images for a splash banner&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Showcase elements in a grid-style format&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up CSS rules for different screen sizes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtosqlanddatabaseswithmysql"&gt;&lt;a id="introtosqlanddatabaseswithmysql" href="https://youtu.be/ug6DR87bbfk"&gt;Intro to SQL and Databases with MySQL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn the essential skills to manage and query databases using SQL!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Structured Query Language (SQL) is the backbone of modern databases, enabling developers to store, retrieve, and manipulate data efficiently. In this course, you'll gain a solid foundation in relational databases and work with MySQL to explore real-world techniques like filtering data, combining tables, and more. By mastering these skills, you'll unlock the ability to manage data systems for applications, websites, and beyond.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You’ll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Retrieve data with SELECT queries&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Filter, group, and aggregate data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Add new data with various techniques&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Combine data with SQL JOIN operations&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manipulate data with UPDATE and DELETE&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Maintain data integrity in databases&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="gitandgithub_versioncontrolandcollaboration"&gt;&lt;a id="gitandgithub_versioncontrolandcollaboration" href="https://youtu.be/PT0S6sT56CE"&gt;Git and Github - Version Control and Collaboration&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Developing an application takes time, and things often go wrong. From accidentally breaking something that used to work perfectly, to a team member overwriting your working code, fixing mistakes can take valuable time that you don't have to waste.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Discover how to prevent all of this with Git - the version control system that allows you to keep a history of your file changes, and Github - a website where you can store projects, save important information, and collaborate with others on both closed and open source projects.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You'll learn all about: &lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Version control and its uses&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Adding version control to an existing project&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Using Git commands to change a project's ecosystem&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Creating a Github account and using Git commands with Github&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Exploring the Github EcoSystem&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="microsoftazuredeveloperassociateaz-204_prepandpass"&gt;&lt;a id="microsoftazuredeveloperassociateaz-204_prepandpass"&gt;Microsoft Azure Developer Associate (AZ-204): Prep &amp; Pass&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e8d09c294e82e9ada99391346599d26928ba8ec6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2e0ea3c038520f79bb31c99317752e29"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build Azure development skills for certification!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Azure developers need to build, secure, monitor, and connect cloud applications using real platform services. In this course, you'll prepare for Microsoft Azure Developer Associate certification (AZ-204) while learning core Azure development workflows across compute, storage, security, monitoring, integrations, the portal, CLI, and SDKs. These skills will help you approach exam scenarios with confidence and apply Azure development practices from start to finish.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Build Azure compute solutions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manage Azure storage workflows&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Secure cloud applications&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Monitor and troubleshoot apps&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Connect Azure services&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use portal, CLI, SDKs&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="10practiceexamsformicrosoftazuredeveloperassociateaz-204"&gt;&lt;a id="10practiceexamsformicrosoftazuredeveloperassociateaz-204"&gt;10 Practice Exams for Microsoft Azure Developer Associate (AZ-204)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f61b256111d7ab3eb9202cd40d5fc8673a4a1823.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e419fe5f838cc13e21db7ae60110b9bd"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Test your Azure developer readiness!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Microsoft Azure development skills are essential for building secure, scalable cloud solutions across compute, storage, identity, monitoring, and service integration. Through these practice exams, you'll prepare for Microsoft Azure Developer Associate certification with complete AZ-204 coverage reflecting real exam scope, difficulty, and best-fit answer patterns. These skills will help you identify weak developer areas, strengthen real-world Azure knowledge, and approach certification with confidence.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll practice how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Simulate the official AZ-204 format&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Test Azure compute solutions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Validate Azure storage knowledge&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Apply security and identity concepts&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Practice integration scenario questions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Master crucial exam pacing techniques&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="awscertifieddeveloperassociatedva-c02-prepypass"&gt;&lt;a id="awscertifieddeveloperassociatedva-c02-prepypass"&gt;AWS Certified Developer - Associate (DVA-C02): Prep &amp; Pass&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/09b23970f49c8e6a32686b916187217ed98f2995.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=68bf2cd9d3a95cdb75e42508da0071c8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Prepare for AWS developer certification!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;AWS developer skills are essential for building, securing, deploying, and maintaining cloud applications that meet real-world requirements. Through this course, you'll prepare for the AWS Certified Developer - Associate exam (DVA- C02) while practicing service selection, Lambda, data stores, security, CI/CD deployment workflows, troubleshooting, and optimization from start to finish. These skills will help you approach certification questions with confidence and apply AWS developer best practices in real projects.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Develop applications with AWS services&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Build serverless Lambda workflows&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Secure application code and data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Package deployments with CI/CD&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot AWS application issues&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Optimize cloud application performance&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="10practiceexamsforawscertifieddeveloper-associatedva-c02"&gt;&lt;a id="10practiceexamsforawscertifieddeveloper-associatedva-c02"&gt;10 Practice Exams for AWS Certified Developer - Associate (DVA-C02)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/24c565e1c09c481a851e8ffd1eea1e8e0f06d315.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=01d2aa8827062449a720a8a0d758a107"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Validate your AWS developer exam readiness!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Scenario-driven practice is key to passing developer certification exams. These practice exams help you prepare for the AWS Certified Developer - Associate exam (DVA-C02) with ten complete timed tests covering development, security, deployment, troubleshooting, and optimization in the same weighted style as the real exam. You'll learn to spot weak domains, review missed service-selection scenarios, and refine your exam strategy before the live attempt.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll practice how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Simulate full exam sessions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Answer scenario-driven AWS questions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Test all four domains&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Identify weak knowledge areas&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Improve timed exam pacing&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Review best-fit service choices&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="agenticaiwithclaudecodeandmcp"&gt;&lt;a id="agenticaiwithclaudecodeandmcp" href="https://youtu.be/ewqM7ZWw49k"&gt;Agentic AI with Claude Code &amp; MCP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master agentic AI workflows and scale your development with Model Context Protocol (MCP) servers!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Modern software engineering increasingly relies on connecting intelligent AI models to specialized tools to solve complex development challenges. In this course, you'll explore real-world examples that connect AI models to external tools, data, and structured capabilities. These advanced techniques will allow you to design custom, reusable agentic workflows that significantly streamline your professional development pipeline.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Configure Model Context Protocol servers&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Integrate external file system tools&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Automate GitHub issue-to-PR workflows&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Navigate live sites using Playwright&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Define behaviors with agentic configurations&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Package reusable AI-driven skill sets&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="bestpracticesforai-poweredcodingwithclaudecode"&gt;&lt;a id="bestpracticesforai-poweredcodingwithclaudecode" href="https://youtu.be/3w814AaiAFY"&gt;Best Practices for AI-Powered Coding with Claude Code&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock the secrets of AI-powered coding with Claude Code!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;AI is transforming the way software is built, but mastering it means going far beyond simple prompts. In this course, you’ll gain hands-on experience working inside a real-world project - learning how to use Claude Code and tools like it with precision, safety, and confidence from start to finish. As you master structuring, refining, and controlling AI workflows, you’ll be equipped to apply advanced best practices for integrating AI into any production codebase.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Direct AI tools with strong prompts&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Prevent "architectural drift" in projects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Design and implement guardrails effectively&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement safe project modification workflows&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use scratchpads for structured planning&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Expand custom features in live apps&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtonextjsforwebappdevelopment"&gt;&lt;a id="introtonextjsforwebappdevelopment" href="https://youtu.be/uLKY2T7iTjU"&gt;Intro to Next.js for Web App Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master the cutting-edge capabilities of Next.js for high-performance web applications!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Modern web development demands architecture that balances powerful server-side logic with seamless, interactive client experiences. Through this course, you will master the foundations of Next.js 16.2, learning to architect high-performance apps through hands-on technical exercises. These advanced architectural skills will empower you to transition from basic React components to engineering scalable, industry-standard web platforms.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement efficient App Router patterns&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Utilize SSR, SSG, and ISR&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Architect hybrid server-client components&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Develop secure, type-safe server actions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Structure scalable web apps&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manage application state transitions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="nextjsproject_ai-poweredexpensetracker"&gt;&lt;a id="nextjsproject_ai-poweredexpensetracker" href="https://youtu.be/wHgi6gYZOV8"&gt;Next.js Project - AI-Powered Expense Tracker&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build a sophisticated AI-powered financial assistant with Next.js and Gemini!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Modern web development is rapidly shifting toward AI-first architectures that transform static user interfaces into intelligent, conversational experiences. In this course, you will build a complete, real-world project that leverages natural language processing to automate expense tracking. By integrating advanced function calling, you will gain the expertise needed to develop dynamic, data-driven applications that bridge the gap between user intent and database actions.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Architect AI-driven Next.js applications&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement natural language input parsing&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Execute secure database function calls&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Master Drizzle ORM for data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Sync real-time dashboard state updates&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Integrate the Gemini AI SDK&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildwebappswithreact19"&gt;&lt;a id="buildwebappswithreact19" href="https://youtu.be/SCMMpyjww1Y"&gt;Build Web Apps with React 19&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock the power of modern web app development with React!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;React is the cornerstone of interactive web applications, enabling developers to create dynamic user experiences efficiently. In this course, you'll embark on a practical journey to learn the fundamentals of React and how to apply them to create dynamic frontends. These foundational skills will allow you to tackle real-world React projects confidently and start building robust, scalable web apps of all kinds.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Understand the React mental model&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Write and use JSX effectively&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create reusable components effortlessly&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manage dynamic data with state&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Handle events and user interactions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement conditional rendering techniques&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="javascriptmini-projects_languagelearninggame"&gt;&lt;a id="javascriptmini-projects_languagelearninggame" href="https://youtu.be/9n97L2snd3w"&gt;JavaScript Mini-Projects - Language Learning Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/587a3be66c1426c58bc43ee3bb5f025faf3962a4.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=11f0da1957758d574596ce6711d6bd36"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Expand your JavaScript skills by building a browser-based language learning app!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;With no additional frameworks or libraries required, you'll create a quiz-based game while learning how to dynamically integrate JavaScript into webpages, and mastering skills and systems that can be used to create a wide variety of apps and games.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Structure an app with multiple questions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Change the questions and answers the DOM displays&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Detect user input&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Process correct and incorrect answers&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Track and display scores&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Style the app's appearance&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="intermediatejavascript_buildadynamicdatatable"&gt;&lt;a id="intermediatejavascript_buildadynamicdatatable" href="https://youtu.be/xa8KLNRi_Hw"&gt;Intermediate JavaScript - Build a Dynamic Data Table&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/387a88cf607ed108e19920f2ddb3ced94a385753.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=65b10de305f97d16e72588f618d1627c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Expand your JavaScript skills by exploring the concepts of asynchronous programming!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Asynchronous programming lets certain tasks be performed in parallel, which in turn allows us to have fast and efficient websites. Through this course, you'll build a trading card webpage and explore how to utilize async functions to manipulate the DOM dynamically and work with data from a separate JSON file. These concepts will give you the skills to build robust websites, work with API data, create HTML5 games, and gain in-demand web development skills.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Understand promises and async functions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Handle errors in async programming&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use fetch() to retrieve JSON data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Write clean code with arrow functions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Display retrieved data in a table&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Dynamically filter data on the DOM&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="learnrustprogrammingforbeginners"&gt;&lt;a id="learnrustprogrammingforbeginners" href="https://youtu.be/__Fjvbcx_vg"&gt;Learn Rust Programming for Beginners&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dive into the fundamentals of Rust and unlock unparalleled efficiency!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Rust is a general-purpose programming language that’s revolutionizing software development with its emphasis on performance and type-safe coding standards. In this course, you'll journey through Rust's unique features, exploring why developers are increasingly leaning towards it for building real-world applications. By mastering these skills with Rust, you will be equipped to tackle high-performance projects in sectors like web development, systems programming, and more.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up your Rust environment&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Understand basic Rust syntax&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Utilize Rust's ownership system&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement control flow in Rust&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create and use structs and enums&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Leverage crates and modules for efficiency&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="datastructureswithrust"&gt;&lt;a id="datastructureswithrust" href="https://youtu.be/gJyV6sjUgao"&gt;Data Structures with Rust&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock the power of data structures with Rust!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Data structures are the backbone of efficient coding, and mastering them can make the difference between elegant solutions and cumbersome code. In this course, you'll delve into the world of Rust, applying and implementing essential data structures from start to finish. These Rust skills will allow you to select the ideal structure for any situation, streamlining your coding efficiency and preparing you for real-world applications.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Utilize Rust's Vectors effectively&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Work with HashMaps efficiently&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Implement stacks from scratch&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create queues independently&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Handle errors with options&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Use Rust for safe data management&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="rustparallelcomputingproject_imageprocessor"&gt;&lt;a id="rustparallelcomputingproject_imageprocessor" href="https://youtu.be/T7QXGTcwREQ"&gt;Rust Parallel Computing Project - Image Processor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock the power of image processing for Rust applications!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Rust's Image Crate (or library) offers developers a quick and easy way to perform common image manipulations on files - a much-needed skill in today's media-driven world. In this course, you'll learn how to programmatically edit images while also exploring Rust's parallel computing abilities to improve program efficiency. These skills will not only give you greater control over image-based features, but allow you to start using concurrent execution for any Rust-made project.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Resize images&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rotate images&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Crop images&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Blur images&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Work with image ratios&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Process images in bulk&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="practicalrust_clitoolswithclapandindicatif"&gt;&lt;a id="practicalrust_clitoolswithclapandindicatif" href="https://youtu.be/ZxZYsHTttJ4"&gt;Practical Rust - CLI Tools with Clap and Indicatif&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Elevate your Rust skills by building a dynamic CLI application!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In today's fast-paced development world, command-line interfaces (CLIs) are vital for creating efficient and user-friendly applications. In this course, you'll transform a basic image-processing app into a fully-fledged Rust-powered CLI tool. Mastering these skills expands your ability to develop real-world, efficient programs that deliver results using the powerful Rust language.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Parse command-line arguments&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Handle complex subcommand&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add progress bars with Indicatif&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Improve user interaction dynamically&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Execute tasks with CLI efficiency&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create versatile Rust applications&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="rustwebappproject_real-timevideobroadcasting"&gt;&lt;a id="rustwebappproject_real-timevideobroadcasting" href="https://youtu.be/kjRfOV6UwuU"&gt;Rust Web App Project - Real-Time Video Broadcasting&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master real-time video broadcasting with Rust!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Real-time communication is revolutionizing how we interact online, affecting fields from gaming to remote work. Through this course, you'll create a simple video broadcasting system using Rust, WebRTC, and JavaScript - gaining deep insights into real-time communication protocols. These cutting-edge skills will empower you to build fully-fledged applications for live streaming and beyond.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Utilize WebRTC for video streaming&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Establish peer-to-peer connections&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Integrate Rust with JavaScript&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Configure ICE servers effectively&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Apply Session Description Protocol (SDP)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Streamline client-side experiences&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="completeintroductiontocplusplus"&gt;&lt;a id="completeintroductiontocplusplus" href="https://youtu.be/s-d5ywN1fX8"&gt;The Complete Introduction to C++&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ede712dd2f4816a9601a1c638b1e8572bda94bea.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=bec2b41d2f8bd30448f933de133eee4e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn the foundations of C++ programming!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;C++ is the powerhouse behind many advanced tech - including web browsers, operating systems, games, and cloud platforms. Industry leaders like Microsoft, Google, and Apple use C++ to power the innovations that shape our world.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With this beginner-friendly course, you'll learn the basics of working with C++ as you explore techniques for storing and manipulating data - from controlling how your program executes to keeping your code clean.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Handle output and input&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Store various pieces of data with variables&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Manipulate and evaluate data with operators&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Manage flow with conditionals, loops, and more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create reusable blocks of code&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set up a local C++ development environment&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtocplusplusdatastructures"&gt;&lt;a id="introtocplusplusdatastructures" href="https://youtu.be/iXhH2fI-v_k"&gt;Intro to C++ Data Structures&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c82157b393887c18fbcc1273352d298b11b9b2be.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6f51e568f2dff66ee8d59555bfc158ba"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Enhance your knowledge of C++ by exploring data structures.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Knowing how to deal with data structures in C++ is an essential skill for all sorts of C++ programs. Through this course, you'll learn how to store different kinds of data and how you can manipulate and control these data structures in useful ways. These C++ foundations will help prepare you to handle complex data with actionable, problem-solving skills to suit a variety of programming situations.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Store lists of similar data in a single variable&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create entities with multiple variable values&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Reference memory addresses with pointers&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use pointers with operators, arrays, and structs&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Define custom datatypes of limited values (enumerations)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Rename datatypes with Typedef&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="learnobject-orientedcplusplusbybuildingagame"&gt;&lt;a id="learnobject-orientedcplusplusbybuildingagame" href="https://youtu.be/_XXdIgZJzrA"&gt;Learn Object-Oriented C++ by Building a Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/327696aa75f42a281a42a1918a096be38fb8c3e2.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f831a12526d32ca5a265bc7840350920"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Explore object-oriented C++ programming!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Object-oriented programming is a popular paradigm where developers build their programs around "objects" that contain data and functionality related to that object. In this course, you'll explore how to create objects and classes and access their data - all while building a text-based dungeon crawler. This knowledge will provide you with one of the most important skill sets you'll need to create robust C++ programs or even pursue a professional programming career.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create basic classes and objects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Control how data in objects is accessed&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manage OOP principles such as inheritance&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Build text-based dungeons with various rooms&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Deal with player and enemy movement&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Setup interaction systems for combat and items&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="comprehensiveintroductiontocprogramming"&gt;&lt;a id="comprehensiveintroductiontocprogramming" href="https://youtu.be/XIJ_JAR5FpM"&gt;The Comprehensive Introduction to C# Programming&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Jumpstart your programming journey with the C# language!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Developed by Microsoft, C# is a versatile and robust language powering everything from simple applications to complex software systems. In this course, you'll dive deep into C# and explore foundational programming topics - all while cementing your learning with real-world examples and exercises. By the end, you'll have the foundational knowledge to excel in web development, mobile app creation, and even game development using major frameworks like Unity and MonoGame.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up a C# development environment&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Understand C# syntax and execution&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Process and manipulate data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Store data - including with collections&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create efficient code with loops and methods&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Apply fundamentals to real-world examples&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtocomputergraphics"&gt;&lt;a id="introtocomputergraphics" href="https://youtu.be/LONOO13Pm0M"&gt;Intro to Computer Graphics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock the secrets behind computer graphics with hands-on learning!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Computer graphics shape every digital world we experience - from 3D models to blockbuster games. In this course, you’ll dive deep into the essential concepts of how graphics are created and displayed, gaining a clear understanding of the theory and code that power every pixel. By building a mini rendering engine using C# and OpenTK, you’ll truly grasp how images are brought to life in real-world applications and expand your horizons in building custom graphics solutions.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up OpenTK for C# graphics&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Explore the graphics pipeline’s stages&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Transfer geometry to the GPU efficiently&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Write and apply GLSL shaders&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manage graphical data flow&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Render and animate custom graphics&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtodjangoforpythonwebappdevelopment2025edition"&gt;&lt;a id="introtodjangoforpythonwebappdevelopment2025edition" href="https://youtu.be/Wqb_c3eDu-Q"&gt;Intro to Django for Python Web App Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn how to build dynamic web apps with Django, the powerful Python-based framework!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Django is a high-level, open-source framework that simplifies the creation of dynamic and scalable web applications. In this course, you'll build a fully-fledged multi-page website, exploring key concepts such as Django's Model-View-Template (MVT) architecture, dynamic content generation, and project organization. By the end, you'll have the foundational skills needed to create your own complete web app projects and expand into more Django topics.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set up and configure a Django project&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Understand Django's MVT architecture&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create dynamic templates with context data&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Control page navigation with URLs and views&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Work with static files, including CSS&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Build a simple multi-page web app&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="pythonturtlemini-projects"&gt;&lt;a id="pythonturtlemini-projects" href="https://youtu.be/N5wJQHS9bZw"&gt;Python Turtle Mini-Projects&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/020ee3e54fad3b75eb2a50a282c29593c2ad0d61.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a76728e9f32a4e05eb1192090aa0b299"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Expand your Python skills with engaging Turtle projects!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Python Turtle provides a fun, visual way to bring your code to life and create unique and interactive projects with ease. Through this course, you'll build three distinct graphical mini-projects from start to finish, while learning essential Python concepts like variables, loops, and functions. These practical skills will solidify your understanding of programming fundamentals, preparing you to tackle more complex Python applications for the real world.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Work with data, variables, and operators&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement conditional logic&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Optimize code with functions and loops&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use randomization&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Handle user keyboard input&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Structure complete mini-projects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="pythondatastructuresforbeginners"&gt;&lt;a id="pythondatastructuresforbeginners" href="https://youtu.be/7fh-e5Atz8U"&gt;Python Data Structures for Beginners&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ae5ef42fac45fcd45c5030e08ce79ea95bd6a22e.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c12702e3556ddbe34620c8557cdecb75"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn fundamental data structures for Python programming!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Data structures are a tool that allows us to store multiple data values efficiently and maintain specific relationships between those stored values. In this course, you'll explore some of the core Python data structures available, their use cases, and how to practically apply these uses to a text-based RPG battle. These skills will not only give you a foundational element of programming but provide you new methods to organize and manage your program data.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Store multiple values as lists&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Control strings as sequences of data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Work with key-value pairs in dictionaries&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use tuples and sets based on scenario&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manipulate all data structures&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Apply data structures to games&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="pandasproject_flightdataanalysis"&gt;&lt;a id="pandasproject_flightdataanalysis" href="https://youtu.be/wnOINkMZfus"&gt;Pandas Project - Flight Data Analysis&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3b723e8a4680a4a6052b566d00662be7daaf01c8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6862b0a91aa7549aeb2ecefccd5ef3ef"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master Pandas data analysis using real-world flight data!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Data analysis and visualization are critical for almost every industry in making data-backed decisions. Through this course, you'll use Pandas to explore real-world flight data and learn methods for grouping, filtering, and visualizing data in ways applicable to real life. These techniques will unlock new ways you can leverage your data for insights and provide core skills for the entirety of data science.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Load external spreadsheet data&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Explore data structures for analysis&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Filter data for various criteria&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Group data for different analyses&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create different chart types&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Leverage the above for data insights&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="pythonimageprocessingwithpillow"&gt;&lt;a id="pythonimageprocessingwithpillow" href="https://youtu.be/ZYHYB0_W1f8"&gt;Python Image Processing with Pillow&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/476c8a00556eb3a6118a9124bd8ab1c74e242edf.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ae0f85a361bb293d4e45f041b2b2e820"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn how to work with images in Python using Pillow!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Pillow, a fork of the Python Imaging Library (PIL), is a popular tool for manipulating and saving digital images through easy-to-use modules. Through this course, you'll explore basic image operations with Pillow and learn to apply rotation, color changes, filters, and much more. These techniques will allow you to unlock the power of images for your Python apps and give you efficient ways to alter those images to your needs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Display and save images&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Change rotations and image dimensions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Alter image color values&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Enhance contrast, brightness, and more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Use common filters like blurring&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add aspects like borders&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="intermediatepython_virtualpetwithpygame"&gt;&lt;a id="intermediatepython_virtualpetwithpygame" href="https://youtu.be/XzEDiXdG-lk"&gt;Intermediate Python - Virtual Pet with Pygame&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Craft a virtual pet game with Python and Pygame!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Virtual pets are a popular stress-relief genre that allow players to engage with risk-free pet care. You'll work with the Pygame library and create a simple pet game with basic care options and needs system for the pet. These techniques will both enhance your skills with Python and give you new tools to create fun or educational games to play.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Use project management techniques&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create item and pet objects&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Control mouse click interactions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Implement movement and collisions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add "decay" to pet needs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set up end game criteria&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtoregularexpressionsinpython"&gt;&lt;a id="introtoregularexpressionsinpython" href="https://youtu.be/PkTsr1kniDk"&gt;Intro to Regular Expressions in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock new data management techniques in Python with regular expressions!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Regular expressions (RegEx) are a dynamic syntax of characters that provide easy ways to parse, clean, and extract data from text. In this course, you'll explore the foundations of regular expressions and learn a variety of sequences and characters to search your data dynamically. These skills will allow you to apply algorithms to complex data and more quickly find the data you need for your projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create basic patterns using metacharacters&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Refine extracted characters with classes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Anchor searches from specific points&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Define character quantity to extract&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Group patterns for complex searches&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Apply techniques to real-life projects&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtoobject-orientedprogrammingwithpython"&gt;&lt;a id="introtoobject-orientedprogrammingwithpython" href="https://youtu.be/knSfYdQcNBc"&gt;Intro to Object-Oriented Programming with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;With applications in data science, computer vision, and machine learning, Python has been used to automate tasks, create AAA games and effects for blockbuster films, and build cutting-edge technologies like smart cars and facial recognition systems.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;In this beginner-friendly course, you'll learn the basics of Python - including techniques for working with data, program logic, and more. The skills that you'll learn can be applied to building games, apps, and more, and can form the foundations of more advanced programs.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Store simple data values with variables&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manipulate data with operators&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Save sets of data with lists, tuples, and dictionaries&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Control logic flow with conditionals and loops&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up program logic with functions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Work with classes and objects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="pythonprojects_object-orientedgame"&gt;&lt;a id="pythonprojects_object-orientedgame" href="https://youtu.be/sWtQe8a-HuU"&gt;Python Projects - Object-Oriented Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7a444bd8ab64c5468cfc63a39f1f66be14f0f751.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=b830045e28cf312d1c2725063306bf17"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master object-oriented programming techniques for games using Python!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Object-oriented programming (OOP) is one of the most in-demand paradigms, offering developers efficient and intuitive ways to organize their code. In this course, you'll use the Python language to create a text-based escape room while exploring core techniques for working with game "objects" and object-oriented principles. These OOP foundations will prepare you to pursue any number of interactive projects with responsible habits, whether it's games or other software projects!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manage game projects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement different interaction types&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Structure. store, &amp;amp; display item data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Evaluate inputs for specific answers&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Test your games for errors&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Consider various impacts games have&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtoalgorithmswithpython"&gt;&lt;a id="introtoalgorithmswithpython" href="https://youtu.be/FWGbmk3Abnw"&gt;Intro to Algorithms with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/29f967666eabd246f11f98fa21636e772aa24925.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=8b2119b6631f438cb06cda34d1df7922"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn fundamental algorithms for searching and sorting data!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Computer science has many long-standing core algorithms to accomplish specific tasks quickly and efficiently. In this Python course, you'll examine a small sampling of algorithms used every day for searching and sorting data - and discover the pros and cons of each method. These skills will provide you new tools to approach data and give you the foundations needed to scale your projects for large amounts of data.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn all about:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;What algorithms are&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Linear searches&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Binary searches&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Bubble sorting&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Insertion sorting&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Comparing algorithm efficiency&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildawebapplicationwithflask"&gt;&lt;a id="buildawebapplicationwithflask" href="https://youtu.be/8-pzWxPF4IA"&gt;Build a Web Application with Flask&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Make a recipe posting and sharing web app with Flask!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;User interaction has become a core feature of the web app ecosystem, and Flask makes implementing these features easy. In this course, you'll master how to work with routes, forms, and user authentication in Flask while building a site where users can post and share recipes. These skills will allow you to expand your web app skills with Flask and implement user activity for your web app projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create intermediate database models&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Work with forms in Flask&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set up user registration&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Control authorized page access&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Implement user-sharing features&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Build website navigation integrating routes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtoflaskforwebappdevelopment"&gt;&lt;a id="introtoflaskforwebappdevelopment" href="https://youtu.be/BO9aygF8ta0"&gt;Intro to Flask for Web App Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Explore web app development with Flask!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Popularized by its simplicity and flexibility, Flask is a micro web framework that allows you to build web applications using Python. In this course, you'll explore the fundamentals of how Flask works while setting up a dynamic to-do list application - complete with database functionality. These skills will provide you the stepping stones necessary to develop more robust apps with Flask and unlock Python for the web.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set up a Flask project&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create dynamic web routes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Manage pages with templates&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add database CRUD functions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Restructure apps modularly&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Use Flask's built-in debugging&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="htmlfoundations"&gt;&lt;a id="htmlfoundations" href="https://youtu.be/6R4VfKPhrog"&gt;HTML Foundations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/656e61a449bc06ba37a27e349034e9713ebf59bd.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=cbce6ccaa47e5bc6e33052833ca70d83"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build websites, web apps, and more by learning the primary foundation for all web development - HTML.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;HTML (Hypertext Markup Language) is the core pillar of web development that dictates the structure and base appearance of every webpage, and plays a crucial role as you develop your skills further with CSS and JavaScript.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In this course, you will develop a strong set of HTML skills needed to get started on your web development journey, as you learn to structure your page, add specific elements, and even start adding website interactivity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create your first HTML file&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Handle text and its various attributes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Utilize images, links, lists, tables, and more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Work with classes and IDs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Display HTML elements in various ways&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Deal with various user inputs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="cssfoundations"&gt;&lt;a id="cssfoundations" href="https://youtu.be/mxm2NJnYPBo"&gt;CSS Foundations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c74c3fee5698df7b1d0413f7f99cf36772cb92c9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1f65347dee8c6cdf228c886346adc4bf"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master website aesthetics and responsiveness by learning the fundamentals of CSS - a core pillar of web development.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cascading Style Sheets, otherwise known as CSS, is a language geared at altering the appearance of HTML and other markup languages - from page aesthetics, like colors and fonts, to designs that respond to screen size.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course will get you started with the basics of this powerful style sheet language and provide you an in-demand set of skills to enhance the design of your personal and professional web development projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Import CSS into your web project&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Select various HTML elements to alter&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Position and size elements with CSS&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; colors and various stylings&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Alter margins and padding&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Adjust backgrounds, borders, text, and more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
