ile"&gt;HOSTILE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#protocolchaos"&gt;PROTOCOL CHAOS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#cynetic"&gt;CYNETIC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#madness"&gt;MADNESS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#noisealchemy1monthtry_lifetimeaccesscreator"&gt;NOISE ALCHEMY 1 MONTH TRY&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt22"&gt;Pay $22 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#noisealchemylifetimeaccessplusallpacksfromtiers1-2_lifetimeaccesscreator"&gt;NOISE ALCHEMY LIFETIME ACCESS + ALL PACKS FROM TIERS 1-2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="monsterscreams"&gt;&lt;a id="monsterscreams" href="https://youtu.be/RZuFqFqnv2U"&gt;MONSTER SCREAMS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;MONSTER SCREAMS is a collection of 50 monster scream sound effects and variations, created using the SCREAM tool from noisealchemy.com. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Designed for horror, games, and cinematic projects, this pack delivers a wide range of terrifying, aggressive, and unsettling creature screams ready to use.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="book"&gt;&lt;a id="book" href="https://youtu.be/tF3DfVdDdW0"&gt;BOOK&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;BOOK — 42 Sound Effects Created with Noise Alchemy A collection of 42 carefully crafted book sound effects for games, films, apps, and any project that needs authentic paper and binding sounds. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Every sound was designed to capture the natural feel of real books — from the soft rustle of a single page turning to the satisfying thud of a heavy tome closing shut. Multiple variations ensure your project never sounds repetitive, giving you options for every moment and every type of book. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;What's inside : &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;single pages turning slowly, fast page flips, books opening gently, books snapping shut, hardcover and softcover impacts, paper rustles, spine creaks, and natural handling sounds. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perfect for RPG inventory systems, visual novels, puzzle games, interactive storybooks, mobile apps, documentary films, and any scene where books and manuscripts are part of the world. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All sounds are royalty-free&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="dice"&gt;&lt;a id="dice" href="https://youtu.be/cJCFDHPwhAk"&gt;DICE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A collection of 50 high quality dice sound effects designed for tabletop RPG games, board games and any project where authentic dice rolling matters.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cards"&gt;&lt;a id="cards" href="https://youtu.be/M8MbH32kxvI"&gt;CARDS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A collection of 60 high-quality playing card sound effects, perfect for adding realism and tactile detail to your projects. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes: Card shuffles Dealing sounds Flips &amp;amp; picks Card movements and interactions &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Designed for games, UI, casino scenes, and tabletop experiences, these sounds are clean, precise, and ready to use. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bring your card interactions to life with subtle, satisfying audio.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="warhorn"&gt;&lt;a id="warhorn" href="https://youtu.be/TlRGKro1pyI"&gt;WAR HORN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;30 powerful Viking war horn sound effects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ancient. Massive. Cinematic. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perfect for battle scenes, trailers, fantasy films, and Viking games. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unleash the call to war.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="doomnoisealchemy"&gt;&lt;a id="doomnoisealchemy" href="https://youtu.be/bcE08ocFpsI"&gt;DOOM&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unleash pure darkness with DOOM, a collection of 24 powerful dark cinematic impact sounds designed for horror, trailers, and intense sound design. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each impact comes with additional reverse and glitch variations, giving you multiple ways to build tension and create brutal cinematic moments. These sounds feature massive sub-bass punches, distorted impacts, dark braaam-style hits, unsettling reverses, and glitchy textures that add weight and dread to your scenes. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In total, the pack includes 24 original impacts plus their reverse and glitch versions, providing a versatile toolkit for creating dramatic hits, transitions, and dark sonic events. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perfect for:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; Horror films and trailers &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Game sound design &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Dark cinematic transitions &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Sci-fi and dystopian atmospheres &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Trailer impacts and stingers &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;All sounds were designed to deliver maximum intensity, deep low-end power, and immediate usability in professional sound design workflows. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Created by Noise Alchemy – Dark Sound Design for Creators.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="noisealchemy1daytry_lifetimeaccesscreator"&gt;&lt;a id="noisealchemy1daytry_lifetimeaccesscreator" href="https://youtu.be/xLs9rjffu0g"&gt;NOISE ALCHEMY 1 DAY TRY&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get full access to the entire NOISE ALCHEMY library for 24 hours. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This plan is perfect for creators who need professional horror sound effects quickly for a short film, trailer, prototype, YouTube video, or a single production session. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;During your access period, you can explore and download everything available on the platform, including cinematic impacts, creature sounds, ambiences, drones, experimental textures, and sound design tools.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="psychosis"&gt;&lt;a id="psychosis" href="https://youtu.be/4eHqFnjq7jM"&gt;PSYCHOSIS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;PSYCHOSIS – 35 Dark Ambient Loop Sounds Dive into the depths of the human mind with PSYCHOSIS, a collection of 35 dark ambient loop sounds designed to create oppressive and unsettling atmospheres. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This premium pack explores tension, paranoia, and psychological unease through evolving soundscapes. From short disturbing textures to long immersive loops, each sound is crafted to build a sense of discomfort and suspense. Whispering drones, distant echoes, unstable tones, and shifting ambiences blend together to create a deeply haunting sonic experience. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perfect for game developers, filmmakers, and content creators working on horror, thriller, or psychological projects. Ideal for nightmares, abandoned places, liminal spaces, and tense cinematic moments. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All sounds are royalty-free and ready for commercial use. No attribution required. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're designing a horror game, producing a suspenseful scene, or crafting immersive audio environments, PSYCHOSIS provides the perfect foundation for psychological tension.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt9"&gt;Pay $9 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="inventory"&gt;&lt;a id="inventory" href="https://youtu.be/-ZSvrmTBcjQ"&gt;INVENTORY&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;INVENTORY is a collection of 30 sound effects designed specifically for video game inventory systems and user interfaces. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This pack includes a wide range of UI sounds such as item selection, movement, grabbing, equipping, switching, and navigation interactions. Each sound is crafted to be clean, responsive, and easy to integrate, helping you improve user feedback and enhance the overall player experience. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're designing a minimal UI or a more stylized interface, these sounds add clarity and polish to every interaction. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perfect for game developers working on indie games, RPGs, survival games, or any project requiring intuitive and satisfying inventory feedback. All sounds are royalty-free and ready for commercial use.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ancientmechanisms"&gt;&lt;a id="ancientmechanisms" href="https://youtu.be/Fofp6JIczPA"&gt;ANCIENT MECHANISMS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;ANCIENT MECHANISMS – 25 Ancient Mechanical Sound Effects Bring the sound of forgotten machines to life with ANCIENT MECHANISMS, a collection of 25 mechanical sound effects inspired by ancient engineering. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This pack features the creaking, grinding, and heavy movement of wooden and iron mechanisms, perfect for triggering massive gates, secret doors, hidden traps, dungeon systems, and ancient machines. Designed for fantasy games, medieval environments, films, trailers, escape rooms, and immersive sound design, these sounds capture the raw texture of old metal gears, wooden contraptions, and heavy mechanical systems. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're building a mysterious temple, an ancient fortress, or a forgotten underground mechanism, this pack adds the authentic mechanical weight your scenes need. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Included in this pack: 25 Ancient Mechanism Sound Effects Wood and iron mechanical movements Heavy gates, gears and ancient devices Perfect for fantasy, medieval and dungeon environments Ready-to-use high-quality WAV files.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Created with NoiseAlchemy sound design tools.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="horsesteps"&gt;&lt;a id="horsesteps" href="https://youtu.be/FPbWxHjeLzQ"&gt;HORSE STEPS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bring authentic equine movement to your projects with HORSE, a comprehensive collection of 100 high-quality horse footstep sound effects. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This pack captures the natural rhythm and power of horses in motion, featuring a wide variety of hoof impacts, walking, trotting, and galloping variations. Recorded and designed to deliver realistic textures, these sounds are perfect for films, games, trailers, animations, historical scenes, fantasy worlds, and cinematic produc